# <a name="required-diagnostic-data-for-office"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-103">Obvezni diagnostični podatki za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-103">Required diagnostic data for Office</span></span>

> [!IMPORTANT]
> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-104">Informacije v tem članku veljajo za različico 1904 ali novejšo različico sledeče Officeove odjemalske programske opreme, ki je nameščena v računalniku s sistemom Windows:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-104">The information in this article applies to Version 1904 or later of the following Office client software installed on a computer running Windows:</span></span>
> - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-105">Office 365 ProPlus in Office 365 Business</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-105">Office 365 ProPlus and Office 365 Business</span></span>
> - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-106">Office 365 Personal, Office 365 Home ali druge različice Officea, ki so del naročnine na Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-106">Office 365 Personal, Office 365 Home, or other versions of Office that are part of an Office 365 subscription.</span></span>
> - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-107">Project in Visio, ki sta vključena v nekatere naročniške pakete, kot sta paketa Project Online Professional ali Visio Online 2.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-107">Project and Visio that come with some subscription plans, such as the Project Online Professional plan or Visio Online Plan 2.</span></span>
>
> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-108">Informacije veljajo tudi za različico 16.28 ali novejšo od teh aplikacij sistema Office za Mac: Excel, Outlook, OneNote, PowerPoint in Word.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-108">The information also applies to Version 16.28 or later of the following Office for Mac applications: Excel, Outlook, OneNote, PowerPoint, and Word.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-109">Diagnostični podatki so uporabljeni za zaščito, posodobitev ter zaznavanje in odpravljanje težav v Officeu, poleg tega pa tudi za izboljšanje izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-109">Diagnostic data is used to keep Office secure and up-to-date, detect, diagnose and fix problems, and also make product improvements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-110">Ti podatki ne vključujejo uporabniškega imena ali e-poštnega naslova, vsebine datotek uporabnika ali informacij o aplikacijah, ki niso del Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-110">This data does not include a user’s name or email address, the content of the user’s files, or information about apps unrelated to Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-111">Diagnostični podatki o uporabljeni programski opremi odjemalca za Office v računalnikih z nameščenim sistemom Windows so bili zbrani in poslani Microsoftu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-111">This diagnostic data is collected and sent to Microsoft about Office client software being used on computers running Windows.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-112">Nekateri diagnostični podatki so obvezni, medtem ko so drugi izbirni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-112">Some diagnostic data is required, while some diagnostic data is optional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-113">S kontrolniki zasebnosti lahko izbirate, ali nam boste poslali zahtevane ali izbirne diagnostične podatke, kot so na primer nastavitve pravilnikov za organizacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-113">We give you the ability to choose whether to send us required or optional diagnostic data through the use of privacy controls, such as policy settings for organizations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-114">S Pregledovalnikom diagnostičnih podatkov lahko vidite, kateri diagnostični podatki so nam poslani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-114">You can see the diagnostic data being sent to us by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-115">***Obvezni diagnostični podatki*** vključujejo najmanjšo nujno količino podatkov, potrebnih za zagotavljanje varnosti, posodobitev in pričakovanega delovanja Officea v napravi, v kateri je sistem nameščen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-115">***Required diagnostic data*** is the minimum data necessary to help keep Office secure, up-to-date, and performing as expected on the device it’s installed on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-116">Z obveznimi diagnostičnimi podatki prepoznate težave z Officeom, ki so morda povezane z napravo ali konfiguracijo programske opreme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-116">Required diagnostic data helps to identify problems with Office that may be related to a device or software configuration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-117">Z njimi lahko na primer prepoznate pogoste zrušitve novo uvedenih Officeovih funkcij v določeni različici operacijskega sistema oz. onemogočene Officeove funkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-117">For example, it can help determine if an Office feature crashes more frequently on a particular operating system version, with newly introduced features, or when certain Office features are disabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-118">Z obveznimi diagnostičnimi podatki lahko hitreje zaznamo, diagnosticiramo in odpravimo te težave ter tako zmanjšamo njihov vpliv na uporabnike ali organizacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-118">Required diagnostic data helps us detect, diagnose, and fix these problems more quickly so the impact to users or organizations is reduced.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-119">Če želite izvedeti več informacij o diagnostičnih podatkih, preberite te članke:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-119">For more information about diagnostic data, see the following:</span></span>

## <a name="categories-and-data-fields-that-are-common-for-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-171">Skupne kategorije in podatkovna polja za vse dogodke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-171">Categories and data fields that are common for all events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-172">Nekatere informacije o dogodkih so skupne za vse dogodke, ne glede na kategorije ali podatkovne podtipe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-172">There is some information about events that is common to all events, regardless of category or data subtype.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-173">Te skupne informacije, ki jih včasih imenujemo *podatkovne pogodbe*, so organizirane v kategorije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-173">This common information, which is sometimes referred to as *data contracts*, is organized into categories.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-174">Posamezne kategorije vključujejo polja, ta polja pa vsebujejo metapodatke in lastnosti posameznih dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-174">Each category contains fields, and these fields are the metadata and properties of an individual event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-175">Te informacije si lahko ogledate s Pregledovalnikom diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-175">You can view this information by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-176">Kategorije zbranih informacij o dogodkih lahko razdelite v dve skupini:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-176">The categories of information that is collected about events can be divided into two groups:</span></span>

  - [<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-177">Skupne informacije za vse dogodke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-177">Information common to all events</span></span>](#information-common-to-all-events)
  - [<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-178">Informacije, ki posebej podpirajo zbiranje diagnostičnih podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-178">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection</span></span>](#information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection)

### <a name="information-common-to-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-179">*Skupne informacije za vse dogodke*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-179">*Information common to all events*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-180">Informacije, skupne za vse dogodke, so zbrane v teh kategorijah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-180">Information common to all events is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="app"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-181">Aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-181">App</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-182">Informacije o aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-182">Information about the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-183">Vsa polja so nespremenljiva za vse seje določene različice aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-183">All fields are constant for all sessions of a given application version.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-184">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-184">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-185">**Branch** – Veja posamezne graditve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-185">**Branch** - The branch that the given build came from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-186">Omogoča, da določimo vrsto veje posamezne graditve ter tako izberemo ustrezne rešitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-186">Allows us to determine what type of branch a given build came from so that we can correctly target fixes.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-187">**InstallType** – Popisovalnik, ki določa način uporabnikove namestitve aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-187">**InstallType** - An enumerator that identifies how the user installed the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-188">Omogoča prepoznavanje morebitnih težav določenih namestitvenih mehanizmov, ki jih v drugih ni mogoče zaznati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-188">Allows us to determine if specific install mechanisms are creating issues that are not seen in other installation mechanisms.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-189">**Name** – Ime aplikacije, ki ustvarja podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-189">**Name** - The name of the application that is providing the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-190">Omogoča, da določimo, v kateri aplikaciji je prišlo do težave in tako pripravimo ustrezno rešitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-190">Allows us to identify which application is showing an issue so we know how to address it.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-191">**Platform** – Širša klasifikacija platforme, v kateri se izvaja aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-191">**Platform** - The broad classification of the platform on which the app is running.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-192">Omogoča, da določimo, v kateri platformi je prišlo do težav ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-192">Allows us to identify on which platforms an issue may be occurring so that we can correctly prioritize the issue.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-193">**Version** – Različica aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-193">**Version** - The version of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-194">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerih različicah izdelka je prišlo do težave ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-194">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

#### <a name="client"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-195">Odjemalec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-195">Client</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-196">Identifikator, povezan s primerkom sistema Office v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-196">Identifier related to an Office instance on a device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-197">Konstanta za vse seje vseh aplikacij določene različice namestitve za zbirke več aplikacij oz. konstanta za vse seje določene različice aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-197">Constant for all sessions of all apps of a given installation version for multi-app suites, or constant for all sessions of a given application version.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-199">**Id** – Enolični identifikator, ki je dodeljen odjemalcu ob času namestitve Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-199">**Id** - Unique identifier assigned to a client at install time of Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-200">Omogoča, da določimo, ali težave vplivajo na izbran nabor namestitev in koliko uporabnikov je zaznalo te težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-200">Allows us to identify whether issues are impacting a select set of installs and how many users are impacted.</span></span>

#### <a name="consent"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-201">Soglasje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-201">Consent</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-206">**DiagnosticConsentLevel** – Označuje raven soglasja za uporabo diagnostičnih podatkov, ki ga je podelil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-206">**DiagnosticConsentLevel** – Indicates what level of diagnostic data consent the user has given</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-207">**DiagnosticConsentSourceLocation** – Označuje, kako je uporabnik soglašal z uporabo diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-207">**DiagnosticConsentSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user had provided the consent for diagnostic data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-210">**ServiceConnectionState** – Označuje, ali je uporabnik izbral, da želi oz. ne želi uporabljati vse povezane izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-210">**ServiceConnectionState** – Indicates whether the user has chosen to use or not use all connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-211">**ServiceConnectionStateSourceLocation** – Označuje, kako je uporabnik izbral možnost uporabe vseh povezanih izkušenj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-211">**ServiceConnectionStateSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user provided the choice whether to use all connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-212">**ServiceConnectionStateConsentTime** – Označuje, kdaj je uporabnik izbral, ali želi uporabljati vse povezane izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-212">**ServiceConnectionStateConsentTime** – Indicates when the user chose whether to use all connected experiences.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-213">Datum bo prikazan kot človeško berljiv datum ali kot strojno kodiran datum, ki je videti kot veliko število.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-213">The date will appear as either a human readable date or as a machine encoded date that looks like a large number.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-214">**ControllerConnectedServicesState** – Označuje, ali ima uporabnik dostop do izbirnih povezanih izkušenj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-214">**ControllerConnectedServicesState** – Indicates whether the user has access to optional connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-216">**ControllerConnectedServicesStateConsentTime** – Označuje, kdaj je uporabnik izbral stanje izbirnih povezanih izkušenj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-216">**ControllerConnectedServicesStateConsentTime** – Indicates when the user chose the status of optional connected experiences.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-217">Datum bo prikazan kot človeško berljiv datum ali kot strojno kodiran datum, ki je videti kot veliko število.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-217">The date will appear as either a human readable date or as a machine encoded date that looks like a large number.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-218">**UserContentDependentState** – Označuje, ali je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki analizirajo vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-218">**UserContentDependentState** – Indicates whether the user has chosen to enable or disable connected experiences that analyze content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-219">**UserContentDependentStateSourceLocation** – Označuje, kako je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki analizirajo vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-219">**UserContentDependentStateSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user’s choice to enable or disable was made for connected experiences that analyze content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-220">**UserContentDependentStateConsentTime** – Označuje, kdaj je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki analizirajo vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-220">**UserContentDependentStateConsentTime** – Indicates when the user chose to enable or disable connected experiences that analyze content was made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-221">Datum bo prikazan kot človeško berljiv datum ali kot strojno kodiran datum, ki je videti kot veliko število.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-221">The date will appear as either a human readable date or as a machine encoded date that looks like a large number.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-222">**DownloadContentState** – Označuje, ali je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki prenašajo spletno vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-222">**DownloadContentState** – Indicates whether the user has chosen to enable or disable connected experiences that download online content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-223">**DownloadContentStateSourceLocation** – Označuje, kako je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki prenašajo spletno vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-223">**DownloadContentStateSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user made the choice to enable or disable connected experiences that that download online content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-224">**DownloadContentStateConsentTime** – Označuje, kdaj je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki prenašajo spletno vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-224">**DownloadContentStateConsentTime** – Indicates when the user made the choice to enable or disable connected experiences that download online content.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-225">Datum bo prikazan kot človeško berljiv datum ali kot strojno kodiran datum, ki je videti kot veliko število.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-225">The date will appear as either a human readable date or as a machine encoded date that looks like a large number.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-227">Informacije o operacijskem sistemu in graditvi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-227">Information about the operating system and build.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-228">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-228">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-229">**OsBuild** – Številka graditve operacijskega sistema, ki je nameščena v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-229">**OsBuild** - The build number of the operating system installed on the device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-230">Omogoča, da določimo, ali težave različno vplivajo na posamezne servisne pakete oz. različice določenega operacijskega sistema ter jih razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-230">Allows us to identify whether issues are impacting individual service packs or versions of a given operating system differently than others so we can prioritize issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-231">**OsVersion** – Glavna različica operacijskega sistema, ki je nameščena v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-231">**OsVersion** - The major version of the operating system installed on the device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-232">Omogoča, da določimo, ali nekatere težave vplivajo na določeno različico operacijskega sistema bolj kot druge ter jih razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-232">Allows us to determine if issues are impacting a particular operating system version more than other so we can prioritize issues.</span></span>

#### <a name="legacy"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-233">Starejša različica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-233">Legacy</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-234">Vsebuje ID aplikacije in različico operacijskega sistema za združljivost z obstoječimi starejšimi postopki zbiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-234">Provides an App Id and OS version for compatibility with existing legacy collection practices.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-235">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-235">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-236">**AppId** – Vrednost popisovalnika, ki označuje, katera aplikacija posreduje podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-236">**AppId** - An enumerator value representing which application is sending the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-237">Omogoča, da določimo, v kateri aplikaciji je prišlo do težave in tako pripravimo ustrezno rešitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-237">Allows us to identify which application is showing an issue so we know how to address it.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-238">**OsEnv** – Popisovalnik, ki določa, v katerem operacijskem sistemu se izvaja seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-238">**OsEnv** - An enumerator indicating which operating system the session is running on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-239">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerem operacijskem sistemu je prišlo do težav ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-239">Allows us to identify which operating system an issue happening on so we can prioritize issues.</span></span>

#### <a name="release"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-240">Izdaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-240">Release</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-241">Informacije, povezane s kanalom izdaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-241">Information related to the release channel.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-242">Vsa polja so nespremenljiva za vse seje vseh aplikacij določene različice namestitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-242">All fields are constant for all sessions of all apps of a given installation version.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-243">Določa skupino vseh naprav znotraj ene faze cikla izdaje izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-243">Identifies a group of devices all in one phase of a product release cycle.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-244">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-244">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-245">**Audience** – Določa podskupino občinstva določene skupine občinstva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-245">**Audience** - Identifies a sub-audience of a given audience group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-246">Omogoča spremljanje podmnožic skupin občinstva za ocenjevanje razširjenosti in ravni pomembnosti težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-246">Allows us to track subsets of audience groups to evaluate prevalence and prioritization of issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-247">**AudienceGroup** – Določa krog, kjer so ustvarjeni podatki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-247">**AudienceGroup** - Identifies the ring where data is coming from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-248">Omogoča postopno uvajanje funkcij in prepoznavanje morebitnih težav, preden te dosežejo večji del uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-248">Allows us to roll out features in a staged fashion and identify potential issues before they reach most users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-249">**Channel** – Kanal, v katerem je izdan določen izdelek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-249">**Channel** - The channel that the product is being released through.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-250">Omogoča, da prepoznamo, ali določene težave različno vplivajo na kanale za uvajanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-250">Allows us to identify if an issue is impacting one of our rollout channels differently than others.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-251">**Fork** – Določa vejitev izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-251">**Fork** - Identifies the fork of the product.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-252">Omogoča mehanizem za združevanje podatkov v naboru številk graditve za prepoznavanje težav, povezanih z določeno izdajo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-252">Allows a mechanism to aggregate data across a set of build numbers to identify issues related to a given release.</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-253">Seja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-253">Session</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-254">Informacije o seji obdelave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-254">Information about the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-255">Vsa polja so nespremenljiva za to sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-255">All fields are constant for this session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-256">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-256">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-257">**ABConfigs** – Določa nabor pilotnih različic, ki se izvajajo v določeni seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-257">**ABConfigs** - Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-258">Omogoča, da ugotovimo, katere pilotne različice se izvajajo v seji ter tako določimo, ali je pilotna različica izvor uporabnikovih težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-258">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-259">**EcsETag** – Indikator sistema pilotnih različic, ki predstavlja pilotne različice, poslane v računalnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-259">**EcsETag** - An indicator from the flighting system that represents the flights sent to the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-260">Omogoča, da določimo, katere pilotne različice morda vplivajo na določeno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-260">Allows us to identify what flights might be impacting a given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-261">**Flags** – Zastavice za sledenje bitne maske celotne seje, trenutno osredotočene predvsem na možnosti vzorčenja in diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-261">**Flags** - Bitmask tracking flags applicable to an entire session, currently primarily focused on sampling and diagnostic data options.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-262">Omogoča nadziranje načina delovanja določene seje v primerjavi z diagnostičnimi podatki, ki jih ustvari seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-262">Allows us to control how a given session behaves in relation to the diagnostic data that the session generates.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-263">**Id** – Enolično identificira določeno podatkovno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-263">**Id** - Uniquely identifies a given session of data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-264">Omogoča, da določimo vpliv težav tako, da ocenimo število prizadetih sej in prepoznamo morebitne skupne značilnosti teh sej.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-264">Allows us to identify the impact of issues by evaluating the number of sessions that are impacted and if there are common features of those sessions.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-265">**ImpressionId** – Določa nabor pilotnih različic, ki se izvajajo v določeni seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-265">**ImpressionId** - Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-266">Omogoča, da ugotovimo, katere pilotne različice se izvajajo v seji ter tako določimo, ali je pilotna različica izvor uporabnikovih težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-266">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-267">**MeasuresEnabled** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali so podatki trenutne seje vzorčni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-267">**MeasuresEnabled** - Flag indicating if the current sessions data is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-268">Omogoča, da določimo, kako statistično oceniti podatke, zbrane v določeni seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-268">Allows us to determine how to statistically evaluate the data that is gathered from the given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-269">**SamplingClientId** – ID odjemalca, s katerim določimo, ali je del vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-269">**SamplingClientId** - The id of the client used to determine if it is part of sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-270">Omogoča, da določimo, zakaj so bile posamezne seje vključene oz. izključene iz vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-270">Allows us to determine why an individual session was included or excluded from sampling.</span></span>

#### <a name="user"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-271">Uporabnik</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-271">User</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-272">Na voljo so informacije o najemniku za inventarne številke komercialne programske opreme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-272">Provides tenant information for commercial software SKUs.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-273">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-273">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-274">**PrimaryIdentityHash** – Identifikator s psevdonimom, ki označuje trenutnega uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-274">**PrimaryIdentityHash** – A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-275">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** – Vrsta identitete, ki jo vsebuje polje »PrimaryIdentityHash«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-275">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** – The type of identity contained in the PrimaryIdentityHash.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-276">MASCID, OrgIdCID ali UserObjectId.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-276">One of MASCID, OrgIdCID or UserObjectId.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-277">**TenantGroup** – Vrsta najemnika, kamor sodi naročnina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-277">**TenantGroup** - The type of the tenant that the subscription belongs to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-278">Omogoča, da razvrstimo težave in določimo, ali je težava razširjena oz. omejena na določen nabor uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-278">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-279">**TenantId** – Najemnik, s katerim je povezana uporabnikova naročnina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-279">**TenantId** - The tenant that a user’s subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-280">Omogoča, da razvrstimo težave in določimo, ali je težava razširjena ali omejena na določen nabor uporabnikov oz. določenega najemnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-280">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant.</span></span>

### <a name="information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-281">*Informacije, ki posebej podpirajo zbiranje diagnostičnih podatkov*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-281">*Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-282">Informacije, ki posebej podpirajo zbiranje diagnostičnih podatkov, so zbrane v teh kategorijah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-282">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="activity"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-283">Dejavnost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-283">Activity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-284">Informacije, ki omogočajo razumevanje uspešno izvedenega dogodka zbiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-284">Information to understand the success of the collection event itself.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-285">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-285">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-286">**AggMode** – Sporoči sistemu, kako naj združi rezultate dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-286">**AggMode** - Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-287">Omogoča, da zmanjšamo količino prenesenih informacij iz uporabnikovega računalnika tako, da združimo rezultate dejavnosti v en dogodek, ki ga redno pošiljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-287">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user’s machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-288">**Count** – Število izvajanj določene dejavnosti, če skupno število označuje združeni dogodek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-288">**Count** - The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-289">Omogoča, da določimo, kolikokrat je bila dejavnost uspešno oz. neuspešno izvedena glede na način združevanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-289">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-290">**CV** – Vrednost, ki določa odnos med dejavnostmi in poddejavnostmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-290">**CV** - A value that identifies the relationship between activities and sub-activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-291">Omogoča, da lahko znova ustvarimo odnos med ugnezdenimi dejavnostmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-291">Allows us to rebuild the relationship between nested activities.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-292">**Duration** – Trajanje izvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-292">**Duration** - The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-293">Omogoča, da določimo težave z učinkovitostjo delovanja, ki negativno vplivajo na uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-293">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the users experience.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-294">**Result**.**Code** – Koda, ki jo določa aplikacija, za prepoznavanje določenih rezultatov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-294">**Result**.**Code** - An application defined code to identify a given results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-295">Omogoča, da določimo podrobnosti napake, kot je koda napake, s katero lahko razvrstimo težave in jih odpravimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-295">Allows us to determine more specific details of a given failure such as a failure code that can be used to classify and fix issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-296">**Result.Tag** – Oznaka za celo število, ki določa lokacijo v kodi, kjer je bil ustvarjen rezultat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-296">**Result.Tag** - An integer tag that identifies the location in code where the result was generated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-297">Omogoča, da natančno določimo lokacijo v kodi, kjer je bil ustvarjen rezultat, ter tako razvrstimo napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-297">Allows us to distinctly identify the location in code where a result was generated which enables classification of failures.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-298">**Result**.**Type** – Vrsta kode rezultata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-298">**Result**.**Type** - The type of the result code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-299">Določa vrsto poslane kode rezultata, tako da lahko ustrezno obravnavamo vrednost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-299">Identifies what type of result code was sent so that the value can be correctly interpreted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-300">**Success** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bila dejavnost uspešna oz. neuspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-300">**Success** - A flag indicating if the activity succeeded or failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-301">Omogoča, da določimo, ali so bila uporabnikova dejanja v izdelku uspešno oz. neuspešno izvedena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-301">Allows us to determine if actions the user takes in the product are succeeding or failing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-302">Prepoznamo lahko težave, ki vplivajo na uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-302">This allows us to identify issues that are impacting the user.</span></span>

#### <a name="application"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-303">Aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-303">Application</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-304">Informacije o namestitvi aplikacije, kjer se zbirajo dogodki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-304">Information about the installation of the application from which the events are being gathered.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-305">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-305">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-306">**Architecture** – Arhitektura aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-306">**Architecture** - The architecture of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-307">Razvrstimo lahko napake, ki so morda značilne za določeno arhitekturo aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-307">Let’s us classify errors that might be specific to an architecture of the application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-308">**Click2RunPackageVersion** – Številka različice paketa »zagon s klikom«, s katerim ste namestili aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-308">**Click2RunPackageVersion** - The version number of the Click-To-Run package that installed the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-309">Omogoča, da določimo, s katero različico namestitvenega programa je bil nameščen Office ter tako prepoznamo težave, povezane z namestitvijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-309">Allows us to identify which version of the installer was used to install Office so we can identify setup related issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-310">**DistributionChannel** – Kanal, v katerem je bila uvedena aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-310">**DistributionChannel** - The channel where the app was deployed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-311">Omogoča, da razdelimo dohodne podatke na particije ter tako ugotovimo, ali težave vplivajo na občinstvo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-311">Allows us to partition incoming data so we can determine if issues are impacting audiences.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-312">**InstallMethod** – Ali je bila trenutna graditev Officea nadgrajena iz starejše graditve, je bila povrnjena v starejšo graditev oz. gre za novo namestitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-312">**InstallMethod** - Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from an older build, rolled back to an older build, or a fresh install.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-313">**IsClickToRunInstall** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali gre za namestitev »zagon s klikom«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-313">**IsClickToRunInstall** - Flag indicating if install was a click to run install.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-314">Omogoča, da določimo težave, ko so morda značilne za namestitveni mehanizem »zagon s klikom«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-314">Allows us to identify issues that might be specific to the Click-To-Run install mechanism.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-315">**IsDebug** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je to graditev Officea za odpravljanje napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-315">**IsDebug** - Flag indicating if the office build is a Debug build.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-316">Omogoča, da določimo, ali so vir težav graditve za odpravljanje težav, ki lahko delujejo na drugačen način.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-316">Allows us to identify if issues are coming from Debug builds which may behave differently .</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-317">**IsInstalledOnExternalStorage** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil Office nameščen v zunanjo napravo za shranjevanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-317">**IsInstalledOnExternalStorage** - Flag indicating if Office was installed on an external storage device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-318">Določimo lahko, ali je težavam mogoče slediti v mesto zunanje shrambe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-318">Let’s us determine if issues can be traced to an external storage location.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-319">**IsOEMInstalled** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je Office namestil proizvajalec strojne opreme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-319">**IsOEMInstalled** - Flag indicating if Office was installed by an original equipment manufacturer (OEM).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-320">Določimo lahko, ali je aplikacijo namestil proizvajalec strojne opreme ter tako razvrstimo in prepoznamo težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-320">Let’s us determine if the application was installed by an OEM which can help us classify and identify issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-321">**PreviousVersion** – Različica Officea, ki je bila predhodno nameščena v računalniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-321">**PreviousVersion** - The version of Office that was previously installed on the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-322">Omogoča povrnitev na prejšnjo različico, če ima trenutna različica težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-322">Allows us to roll back to a previous version if the current one has an issue.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-323">**ProcessFileName** – Ime datoteke aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-323">**ProcessFileName** - The name of the application filename.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-324">Omogoča določitev imena izvedljive datoteke, ki ustvarja podatke, saj je za isto ime aplikacije lahko na voljo več različnih imen datotek postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-324">Allows us to identify the name of the executable which is generating the data as there may be several different process filenames reporting as the same app name.</span></span>

#### <a name="client"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-325">Odjemalec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-325">Client</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-326">Informacije o odjemalcu za Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-326">Information about the Office client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-327">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-327">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-328">**FirstRunTime** – Prvo izvajanje odjemalca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-328">**FirstRunTime** - The first time the client was run.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-329">Omogoča nam vpogled v podatke o tem, koliko časa ima odjemalec že nameščen Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-329">Allows us to understand how long the client has had Office installed.</span></span>

#### <a name="device"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-330">Naprava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-330">Device</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-331">Informacije o konfiguraciji naprave in zmogljivostih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-331">Information about device configuration and capabilities.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-332">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-332">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-333">**DigitizerInfo** – Informacije o digitalizatorju, ki ga uporablja računalnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-333">**DigitizerInfo** - Information on the digitizer used by the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-334">Omogoča razvrstitev podatkov glede na osrednjo napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-334">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-335">**FormFactor** – Določa dimenzije naprave, ki pošilja podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-335">**FormFactor** - Identifies what form factor the device sending the info is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-336">Omogoča razvrstitev podatkov glede na osrednjo napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-336">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-337">**FormFactorFamily** – Določa dimenzije naprave, ki pošilja podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-337">**FormFactorFamily** - Identifies what form factor the device sending the info is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-338">Omogoča razvrstitev podatkov glede na osrednjo napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-338">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-339">**HorizontalResolution** – Vodoravna ločljivost zaslona naprav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-339">**HorizontalResolution** - The horizontal resolution of the devices screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-340">Omogoča razvrstitev podatkov glede na osrednjo napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-340">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-341">**Id** – Enolični identifikator naprave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-341">**Id** - A unique identifier for the device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-342">Omogoča, da lahko porazdelimo težave v več napravah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-342">Allows us to identify the distribution of issues across a set of devices.</span></span>

#### <a name="event"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-383">Dogodek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-383">Event</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-384">Informacije o dogodku, vključno z enoličnim identifikatorjem seje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-384">Event-specific information, including its unique identifier in the session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-385">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-385">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-386">**Contract** – Seznam morebitnih pogodb, ki jih dogodek uveljavlja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-386">**Contract** - A list of any contracts that the event is implementing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-387">Omogoča, da lahko ocenimo, kateri podatki so del posameznih dogodkov, tako da jih lahko učinkovito obdelamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-387">Allows us to evaluate what data is part of the individual event so that we can process it effectively.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-388">**CV** – Vrednost, s katero lahko identificiramo dogodke, ki so medsebojno povezani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-388">**CV** - A value that allows us to identify events that are related to one another.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-389">Te podatke uporabljamo za diagnostiko, da lahko določimo vzorce povezanega načina delovanja oz. povezanih dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-389">Used for diagnostics to allow us to identify patterns of related behavior or related events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-390">**Flags** – Informacije, s katerimi lahko spremenimo način odzivanja določenega dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-390">**Flags** - Information used to alter how a given event responds.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-391">Omogoča, da lahko upravljamo način obravnavanja določenega dogodka za namene prenašanja podatkov Microsoftu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-391">Used to manage how a given event is treated for the purposes of uploading the data to Microsoft.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-392">**Id** – Enolični identifikator dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-392">**Id** - A unique identifier for the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-393">Omogoča enolično identificiranje prejetih dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-393">Allows us to uniquely identify the events that are being received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-394">**Name** – Ime dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-394">**Name** - The name of the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-395">Omogoča določitev dogodka, ki ga je poslal odjemalec.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-395">Allows to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-396">**Rule** – Identifikator pravila, ki je ustvarilo podatke (če je te ustvarilo pravilo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-396">**Rule** - An identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-397">Omogoča določitev vira dela podatkov, tako da lahko preverimo veljavnost parametrov dogodkov in jih upravljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-397">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-398">**RuleId** – Identifikator pravila, ki je ustvarilo podatke (če je te ustvarilo pravilo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-398">**RuleId** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-399">Omogoča določitev vira dela podatkov, tako da lahko preverimo veljavnost parametrov dogodkov in jih upravljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-399">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-400">**RuleInterfaces** – Vsi vmesniki, ki jih uveljavi določeno pravilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-400">**RuleInterfaces** - Any interfaces that are implemented by the specific rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-401">Omogoča, da razvrstimo in uvozimo podatke glede na njihovo strukturo ter tako poenostavimo obdelavo podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-401">Allows us to classify and import the data based on its structure which simplifies data processing.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-402">**RuleVersion** – Identifikator pravila, ki je ustvarilo podatke (če je te ustvarilo pravilo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-402">**RuleVersion** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-403">Omogoča določitev vira dela podatkov, tako da lahko preverimo veljavnost parametrov dogodkov in jih upravljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-403">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-404">**SampleRate** – Navedba odstotka uporabnikov, ki pošiljajo ta del podatkov. Opravimo lahko statistično analizo podatkov in pogostih podatkovnih točk, ki ne zahtevajo, da jih pošiljajo vsi uporabniki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-404">**SampleRate** - An indication of what percentage of users are sending this piece of data This allows us to do statistical analysis of the data and for very common data points not require that to be sent by all users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-405">**SchemaVersion** – Različica sheme, ki je uporabljena za ustvarjanje diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-405">**SchemaVersion** - The version of the schema used to generate diagnostic data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-406">Zahtevano za upravljanje podatkov, ki jih pošlje odjemalec.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-406">Required to manage data being sent form the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-407">Omogoča, da lahko sčasoma spremenimo vrsto podatkov, ki jih pošilja odjemalec.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-407">This allows changes over time in what data is being sent from each client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-408">**Sequence** – Števec, ki določa vrstni red ustvarjenih dogodkov v odjemalcu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-408">**Sequence** - A counter that identifies the order that an event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-409">Omogoča razvrstitev prejetih podatkov tako, da lahko prepoznamo korake, ki so odjemalce morda privedli do določnih težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-409">Allows the data being received to be ordered so that we can identify what steps may have led to an issue that is impacting clients.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-410">**Source** – Izvorni cevovod, uporabljen za prenos podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-410">**Source** - The source pipeline that was used to upload the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-411">Zahtevano za spremljanje posameznih cevovodov za prenašanje za zagotavljanje ustreznosti stanja sistema in lažje prepoznavanje težav s cevovodom za prenašanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-411">Required to monitor each of our upload pipelines for overall health and to help identify issues with the upload pipeline.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-412">Omogoča spremljanje posameznih cevovodov za prenašanje za zagotavljanje njihove skladnosti s predpisi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-412">This allows us to monitor individual upload pipelines to make sure they remain compliant.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-413">**Time** – Čas, ko je bil dogodek ustvarjen v odjemalcu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-413">**Time** - The time that the event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-414">Omogoča, da lahko sinhroniziramo in preverimo veljavnost vrstnega reda dogodkov, ustvarjenih v odjemalcu, ter izdelamo metriko učinkovitosti delovanja za navodila za uporabnike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-414">Allows us to synchronize and validate the order of events generated on the client as well as establish performance metrics for user instructions.</span></span>
