  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-428">**OsMinorVersion** – Podrazličica operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-428">**OsMinorVersion** - The minor version of the operating system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-429">Omogoča, da določimo, iz katere različice operacijskega sistema izhajajo diagnostični podatki ter tako razvrstimo težave po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-429">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-430">**OsVersionString** – Enolični niz, ki predstavlja številko različice operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-430">**OsVersionString** - A unified string representing the operating system build number.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-431">Omogoča, da določimo, iz katere različice operacijskega sistema izhajajo diagnostični podatki ter tako razvrstimo težave po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-431">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-432">Seja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-432">Session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-433">Informacije o seji obdelave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-433">Information about the process session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-434">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-434">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-435">**ABConfigsDelta** – Spremlja razliko med trenutnimi podatki »ABConfigs« in prejšnjo vrednostjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-435">**ABConfigsDelta** - Tracks the difference between the current ABConfigs data and the previous value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-436">Omogoča spremljanje novih pilotnih različic v računalniku, tako da lahko določite, ali je nova pilotna različica morda kriva za težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-436">Allows us to track what new flights are on the machine to help identify if a new flight is responsible for an issue.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-437">**CollectibleClassification** – Razredi informacij, ki jih lahko zbira seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-437">**CollectibleClassification** - The classes of information the session can collect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-438">Omogoča filtriranje sej glede na razpoložljive podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-438">Allows filtering of sessions based on the data they would have.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-439">**DisableTelemetry** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je ključ »DisableTelemetry« nastavljen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-439">**DisableTelemetry** - Flag indicating if the DisableTelemetry key is set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-440">Omogoča, da si lahko ogledamo, ali je seja poročala le o diagnostičnih podatkih »EssentialServiceMetadata«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-440">Allows us to know if a session was not reporting diagnostic data other than EssentialServiceMetadata.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-441">**SamplingKey** – Ključ, uporabljen za določanje, ali je seja vzorčna ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-441">**SamplingKey** - The key used to determine whether the session is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-442">Omogoča prikaz podatkov, ki določajo, ali je seja vzorčna ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-442">Allows us to understand how individual sessions are making their choice of whether they are sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-443">**SamplingMethod** – Način, uporabljen za določanje pravilnika vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-443">**SamplingMethod** - The method used to determine sampling policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-444">Omogoča razumevanje vrste podatkov, ki jih ustvarja seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-444">Allows us to understand what data is coming from a session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-445">**Sequence** – Enolični številski identifikator seje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-445">**Sequence** - A unique numeric identifier for the session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-446">Omogoča razvrščanje sej za analizo časov pojava težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-446">Allows the ordering of sessions for analysis of then issues might have occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-447">**Start** – Čas zagona seje postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-447">**Start** - The boot time of the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-448">Omogoča določitev časa začetka izvajanja seje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-448">Allows us to establish when the session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-449">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** – Razlika med UTC-jem in lokalnim časom v minutah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-449">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** - The difference in minutes between UTC and the local time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-450">Omogoča normaliziranje časov UTC v lokalne čase.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-450">Allows normalization of UTC times back to the local time.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-451">**SamplingClientIdValue** – Vrednost ključa, s katerim je določeno vzorčenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-451">**SamplingClientIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-452">Omogoča, da lahko prepoznamo razlog za vzorčenje oz. izključitev iz vzorčenja za določeno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-452">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-453">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** – Vrednost ključa, s katerim je določeno vzorčenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-453">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-454">Omogoča, da lahko prepoznamo razlog za vzorčenje oz. izključitev iz vzorčenja za določeno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-454">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-455">**SamplingSessionKValue** – Dodatni metapodatki vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-455">**SamplingSessionKValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-456">Omogoča ocenjevanje statističnega pomena prejetih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-456">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-457">**SamplingSessionNValue** – Dodatni metapodatki vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-457">**SamplingSessionNValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-458">Omogoča ocenjevanje statističnega pomena prejetih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-458">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-459">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** – Vrednost, ki določa, katero raven diagnostičnih podatkov je izbral uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-459">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** - Value indicating what level of diagnostic data the user has opted into.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-460">Omogoča razumevanje ravni diagnostičnih podatkov, ki jih bo ustvarila seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-460">Allows us to understand what level of diagnostic data to expect from a session.</span></span>

## <a name="data-fields-that-are-common-for-onenote-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-461">Podatkovna polja, ki so skupna za dogodke storitve OneNote</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-461">Data fields that are common for OneNote events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-462">Naslednja podatkovna polja so skupna za vse dogodke storitve OneNote za Mac, iOS in Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-462">The following data fields are common for all events for OneNote on Mac, iOS, and Android.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-463">Kadar uporabljate pregledovalnik diagnostičnih podatkov, je prikazano ime »Dejavnost«, »ReportData« ali »Nepričakovano« za dogodke storitve OneNote za Mac, iOS in Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-463">When using the Diagnostic Data Viewer, events for OneNote on Mac, iOS, and Android will appear to have a name of Activity, ReportData, or Unexpected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-464">Če želite najti dejansko ime dogodka, izberite dogodek in si nato oglejte polje »EventName«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-464">To find the actual event name, select the event, and then look at the EventName field.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-465">**Activity_ActivityType** – označuje vrsto tega dogodka dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-465">**Activity_ActivityType** -  Indicates the type of this activity event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-466">Dejavnost je lahko normalna dejavnost ali dejavnost z visoko vrednostjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-466">An activity can be a normal activity or a high value activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-467">**Activity_AggMode** – sporoči sistemu, kako naj združi rezultate dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-467">**Activity_AggMode** -  Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-468">Omogoča, da zmanjšamo količino prenesenih informacij iz uporabnikovega računalnika tako, da združimo rezultate dejavnosti v en dogodek, ki ga redno pošiljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-468">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user’s machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-469">**Activity_Count** – število izvajanj določene dejavnosti, če pridobljeno število označuje združeni dogodek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-469">**Activity_Count** -  The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-470">Omogoča, da določimo, kolikokrat je bila dejavnost uspešno oz. neuspešno izvedena glede na način združevanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-470">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-471">**Activity_CV** – vrednost, ki določa odnos med dejavnostmi in poddejavnostmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-471">**Activity_CV** -  A value that identifies the relationship between activities and sub-activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-472">Omogoča, da lahko znova ustvarimo odnos med ugnezdenimi dejavnostmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-472">Allows us to rebuild the relationship between nested activities.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-473">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** – čas, ko je dejavnost nedejavna in ne izvaja nobenega dejanskega dela, vendar se čas še vedno sešteva za pridobitev skupnega časa dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-473">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time an activity is idle and not doing any real work, but the time is still count towards the total activity's time.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-474">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** – trajanje izvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-474">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-475">Omogoča, da določimo težave z učinkovitostjo delovanja, ki negativno vplivajo na uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-475">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the users experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-476">**Activity_Expiration** – datum v številski obliki označuje, kdaj bo prišlo do ustavitve pošiljanja tega dogodka iz odjemalcev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-476">**Activity_Expiration** -  A date in numerical format indicates when this event will be stop sending from clients</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-477">**Activity_FailCount** – število, ki pokaže, kolikokrat je bila ta dejavnost neuspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-477">**Activity_FailCount** -  A number of times this activity has failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-478">**Activity_Name** – kratko ime dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-478">**Activity_Name** -  A short name of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-479">Omogoča določitev dogodka, ki ga je poslal odjemalec.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-479">Allows to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-480">**Activity_Namespace** – imenski prostor dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-480">**Activity_Namespace** -  A namespace of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-481">Omogoča združevanje dogodkov v skupine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-481">Allows to group the event into groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-482">**Activity_Reason** – niz, ki označuje razlog, zaradi katerega je dejavnost končana z določenim rezultatom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-482">**Activity_Reason** -  A string indicating the reason causing an activity to ends with a particular result.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-483">**Activity_Result** – zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bila dejavnost uspešna, neuspešna ali nepričakovano neuspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-483">**Activity_Result** -  A flag indicating if the activity succeeded, failed, or unexpectedly failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-484">Omogoča, da določimo, ali so bila uporabnikova dejanja v izdelku uspešno oz. neuspešno izvedena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-484">Allows us to determine if actions the user takes in the product are succeeding or failing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-485">Prepoznamo lahko težave, ki vplivajo na uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-485">This allows us to identify issues that are impacting the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-486">**Activity_State** – zastavica označuje, ali je dogodek začetek ali konec dejavnosti uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-486">**Activity_State** -  A flag indicates whether an event is a start of a user activity or an end of a user activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-487">**Activity_SucceedCount** – število, ki pokaže, kolikokrat je bila ta dejavnost uspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-487">**Activity_SucceedCount** -  A number of times this activity is succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-488">**ErrorCode** – označuje kodo napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-488">**ErrorCode** -  Indicates an error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-489">**ErrorCode2** – označuje drugo kodo napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-489">**ErrorCode2** -  Indicates a second error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-490">**ErrorCode3** – označuje tretjo kodo napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-490">**ErrorCode3** -  Indicates a third error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-491">**ErrorTag** – označuje oznako, ki je povezana s kodo napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-491">**ErrorTag** -  Indicates the tag associated in code of an error if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-492">**ErrorType** – označuje vrsto napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-492">**ErrorType** -  Indicates the type of an error if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-493">**EventName** – enolično ime dogodka v aplikaciji OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-493">**EventName** -  A unique name of a OneNote's event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-494">Dogodki v aplikaciji OneNote uporabljajo to polje po meri za določanje enoličnega imena zaradi inženirske omejitve v preteklosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-494">OneNote events use this custom field to specify a unique name due to an engineering limitation in the past.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-495">**ExpFeatures** – označuje, ali je uporabnik vklopil stikalo za preskusne funkcije v aplikaciji OneNote ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-495">**ExpFeatures** -  Indicates whether a user has turn-on an experimental-feature switch in OneNote app or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-496">**ExpirationDate** – datum v številski obliki zapisa označuje, kdaj bo ustavljeno pošiljanje tega dogodka iz odjemalcev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-496">**ExpirationDate** -  A date in numerical format indicates when this event will be stop sending from clients</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-497">**IsConsumer** – označuje, ali je uporabnik potrošnik ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-497">**IsConsumer** -  Indicates whether a user is consumer or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-498">**IsEdu** – označuje, ali ima uporabnik status uporabnika v izobraževalnem najemniku ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-498">**IsEdu** -  Indicates whether a user is a user in education tenant or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-499">**IsIW** – označuje, ali je uporabnik poslovni uporabnik ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-499">**IsIW** -  Indicates whether a user is an enterprise user or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-500">**IsMsftInternal** – označuje, ali je uporabnik zaposleni družbe Microsoft ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-500">**IsMsftInternal** -  Indicates whether a user is a Microsoft employee or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-501">**IsPremiumUser** – označuje, ali ima uporabnik licenco Premium ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-501">**IsPremiumUser** -  Indicates whether a user has premium license or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-502">**Namespace** – imenski prostor dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-502">**Namespace** -  A namespace of the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-503">Omogoča združevanje dogodkov v skupine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-503">Allows to group the event into groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-504">**Release_AppStore** – zastavica označuje, ali je graditev pridobljena v trgovini z aplikacijami ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-504">**Release_AppStore** -  A flag indicates whether a build is coming from an app store or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-505">**Release_Audience** – določa podskupino občinstva za dano skupino občinstva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-505">**Release_Audience** -  Identifies a sub-audience of a given audience group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-506">Omogoča spremljanje podmnožic skupin občinstva za ocenjevanje razširjenosti in ravni pomembnosti težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-506">Allows us to track subsets of audience groups to evaluate prevalence and prioritization of issues.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-507">**AudienceGroup** – določa krog, kjer so ustvarjeni podatki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-507">**Release_AudienceGroup** -  Identifies the ring where data is coming from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-508">Omogoča postopno uvajanje funkcij in prepoznavanje morebitnih težav, preden te dosežejo večji del uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-508">Allows us to roll out features in a staged fashion and identify potential issues before they reach most users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-509">**Release_Channel** – kanal, v katerem je izdelek izdan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-509">**Release_Channel** -  The channel that the product is being released through.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-510">Omogoča, da prepoznamo, ali določene težave različno vplivajo na kanale za uvajanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-510">Allows us to identify if an issue is impacting one of our rollout channels differently than others.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-511">**RunningMode** – označuje način zagona aplikacije, in sicer s strani uporabnika ali sistemskega procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-511">**RunningMode** -  Indicates how the app is launched either by user or by system process.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-512">**SchemaVersion** – prikazuje trenutno različico sheme telemetrije v telemetrijskem prodajnem lijaku v OneNotu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-512">**SchemaVersion** -  Indicates a current telemetry schema version in OneNote's telemetry pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-513">**Session_EcsETag** – indikator sistema pilotnih različic, ki predstavlja pilotne različice, poslane v računalnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-513">**Session_EcsETag** -  An indicator from the flighting system that represents the flights sent to the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-514">Omogoča, da določimo, katere pilotne različice morda vplivajo na določeno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-514">Allows us to identify what flights might be impacting a given session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-515">**Session_ImpressionId** – določa nabor pilotnih različic, ki se izvajajo v dani seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-515">**Session_ImpressionId** -  Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-516">Omogoča, da ugotovimo, katere pilotne različice se izvajajo v seji ter tako določimo, ali je pilotna različica izvor uporabnikovih težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-516">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-517">**SessionCorrelationId** – globalni enolični identifikator za sejo gostitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-517">**SessionCorrelationId** -  The globally unique identifier for the host’s session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-518">**SH_ErrorCode** – označuje kodo napake, če je na voljo ob neuspehu dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-518">**SH_ErrorCode** -  Indicates an error code if available when an activity fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-519">**Tag** – oznaka za celo število, ki določa lokacijo v kodi, kjer je ustvarjen dogodek telemetrije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-519">**Tag** -  An integer tag that identifies the location in code where the telemetry event is generated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-520">**UserInfo_IdType** – niz označuje vrsto uporabniškega računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-520">**UserInfo_IdType** -  A string indicates the type of a user's account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-521">**UserInfo_OMSTenantId** – najemnik, s katerim je povezana uporabnikova naročnina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-521">**UserInfo_OMSTenantId** -  The tenant that a user’s subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-522">Omogoča, da razvrstimo težave in določimo, ali je težava razširjena ali omejena na določen nabor uporabnikov oz. določenega najemnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-522">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-523">**UserInfo_OtherId** – seznam psevdonimnih identifikatorjev, ki niso primarni in predstavljajo uporabniške račune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-523">**UserInfo_OtherId** -  A list of non-primary pseudonymous identifiers representing user's accounts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-524">**UserInfo_OtherIdType** – seznam vrst računov, ki niso primarni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-524">**UserInfo_OtherIdType** -  A list of non-primary account types.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeclicktorunupdatestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-532">Office.ClickToRun.UpdateStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-532">Office.ClickToRun.UpdateStatus</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-540">**status** – Trenutno stanje posodobitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-540">**status** - Current status of the update</span></span>

#### <a name="officecompliancefileformatballotdisplayedonfirstboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-542">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotDisplayedOnFirstBoot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-542">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotDisplayedOnFirstBoot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-543">Označuje, ali je bilo Officeovo pogovorno okno z izbirami oblike zapisa datoteke prikazano uporabniku ob prvem/drugem zagonu aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint v sistemu Win32.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-543">Indicates whether the Office File Format choice dialog box was shown to the user on first/second boot of Word, Excel, PowerPoint on Win32.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-544">Spremlja, ali je prikazano pogovorno okno »Glasovnica za FileFormat« – dogodek je poslan ob prvem/drugem zagonu aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint v sistemu Win32.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-544">Tracks whether the FileFormat Ballot dialog box is displayed - event is sent at the first/second boot of Word, Excel or PPT Win32.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-545">Zbrana so naslednja polja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-545">The following fields are collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-546">**CountryRegion** – nastavitev regije države uporabnika v sistemu Windows</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-546">**CountryRegion** –  The users’ country region setting in Windows system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-547">**FileFormatBallotBoxAppIDBootedOnce** – označuje, v kateri aplikaciji (Word, Excel, PowerPoint) je bila obdelana logika prikaza glasovnice oblike zapisa datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-547">**FileFormatBallotBoxAppIDBootedOnce** –  In which app (Word, Excel, PPT) the file format ballot display logic was processed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-548">**FileFormatBallotBoxDisplayedOnFirstBoot** – označuje, kakšen je rezultat prikaza za glasovnico oblike zapisa datoteke (prikazan/ni prikazan kot nepričakovan/ni prikazan zaradi licence/ni prikazan zaradi lokacije).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-548">**FileFormatBallotBoxDisplayedOnFirstBoot** –  What is the display result for file format ballot (displayed/not displayed as unexpected/not displayed due to license/not displayed due to location).</span></span>

#### <a name="officecompliancefileformatballotoption"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-549">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotOption</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-549">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotOption</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-550">Spremlja, ali je prikazano pogovorno okno »Glasovnica za FileFormat« – dogodek je poslan ob prvem/drugem zagonu aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint v sistemu Win32.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-550">Tracks whether the FileFormat Ballot dialog box is displayed - event is sent at the first/second boot of Word, Excel or PPT Win32.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-551">Označuje, ali je pogovorno okno z izbirami oblike zapisa datoteke prikazano ob prvem ali drugem zagonu aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint v sistemu Win32.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-551">Indicates whether the Office File Format choice dialog box is displayed on first or second boot of Word, Excel, or PowerPoint on Win32.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-552">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-552">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-553">**FileFormatBallotSelectedOption** – določa možnost oblike zapisa datoteke (OOXML/ODF), ki jo je uporabnik izbral v pogovornem oknu glasovnice oblike zapisa datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-553">**FileFormatBallotSelectedOption** – Identifies the file format option (OOXML/ODF) that was selected by the user through the file format ballot dialog box.</span></span>


#### <a name="officecorrelationmetadatautccorrelationmetadata"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-554">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-554">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-555">Zbira metapodatke Officea prek UTC-ja in jih primerja z enakovrednimi podatki, zbranimi prek cevovoda telemetrije sistema Office za preverjanje ustreznosti in celovitosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-555">Collects Office metadata through UTC to compare with equivalent data collected through the Office telemetry pipeline to check correctness and completeness of data.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-556">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-556">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-557">**abConfigs** – Seznam ID-jev funkcij za določanje, katere funkcije so omogočene za odjemalca ali prazne, ko ti podatki niso zbrani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-557">**abConfigs** - A list of feature IDs to identify which features are enabled on the client or empty when this data is not being collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-558">**abFlights** – »NoNL:NoFlights«, ko pilotne različice funkcij niso nastavljene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-558">**abFlights** - "NoNL:NoFlights" when the feature flights aren't set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-559">V nasprotnem primeru je izbrana možnost »holdoutinfo=unknown«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-559">Otherwise "holdoutinfo=unknown".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-560">**AppSessionGuid** – Identifikator določene seje aplikacije, ki se je začela z ustvarjanjem procesa in traja vse do konca procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-560">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-561">Dogodek je oblikovan kot standardni 128-bitni GUID, sestavljen iz 4 delov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-561">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-562">Ti štirje deli v vrstnem redu so (1) 32-bitni ID procesa (2) 16-bitni ID seje (3) 16-bitni ID zagona (4) čas ustvarjanja 64-bitnega procesa v UTC 100ns.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-562">Those four parts in order are (1) 32 bit Process ID (2) 16 bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64 bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-563">**appVersionBuild** – Številka različice graditve aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-563">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-564">**appVersionMajor** – Številka glavne različice aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-564">**appVersionMajor** - The app major version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-565">**appVersionMinor** – Številka podrazličice aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-565">**appVersionMinor** - The app minor version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-566">**appVersionRevision** – Številka različice revizije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-566">**appVersionRevision** - The app revision version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-567">**audienceGroup** – Ime skupine občinstva izdaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-567">**audienceGroup** - The release audience group name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-568">**audienceId** – Ime občinstva izdaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-568">**audienceId** - The release audience name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-569">**channel** – Kanal, prek katerega se distribuira Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-569">**channel** - The channel by which Office was distributed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-570">**deviceClass** – Dimenzije naprave v operacijskem sistemu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-570">**deviceClass** - Device form factor from the OS</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-571">**ecsETag** – Identifikator preskusa za proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-571">**ecsETag** - An experiment identifier for the process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-572">**impressionId** – GUID, ki označuje trenutni nabor funkcij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-572">**impressionId** - A guid indicating the current set of features.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-573">**languageTag** – Trenutna jezikovna oznaka za Office UI IETF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-573">**languageTag** - The current Office UI IETF language tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-574">**officeUserID** – Naključno ustvarjeni GUID za to namestitev Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-574">**officeUserID** - Randomly generated guid for this Office install</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-575">**osArchitecture** – Arhitektura operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-575">**osArchitecture** - Operating system architecture</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-576">**osEnvironment** – Celo število, ki označuje operacijski sistem (Windows, Android, iOS, Mac itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-576">**osEnvironment** - An integer indicating the operating system (Windows, Android, iOS, Mac, etc).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-577">**osVersionString** – Različica operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-577">**osVersionString** - Operating system version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-578">**sessionID** – Naključno ustvarjeni GUID za prepoznavanje seje aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-578">**sessionID** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-579">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** – Logična vrednost konstante.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-579">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Constant boolean value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-580">Vedno ima vrednost true.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-580">Always true.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenotefirstrunfirstrun"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-581">Office.OneNote.FirstRun.FirstRun</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-581">Office.OneNote.FirstRun.FirstRun</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-582">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja, da lahko novi uporabniki prvič uspešno zaženejo in začnejo uporabljati OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-582">The critical signal used to ensure new users can successfully launch and run OneNote for the first time.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-583">Telemetrija se uporablja za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-583">The telemetry is collected to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-584">Če uporabniki prvič ne morejo zagnati aplikacije, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-584">If users can’t launch the app for the first time, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-585">**AfterOneDriveFrozenAccountError** – označuje napako OneDrive, ko je račun zamrznjen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-585">**AfterOneDriveFrozenAccountError** - Indicates an error from OneDrive when an account is frozen.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-586">**Poskus** – kolikokrat je treba izvesti uporabniško izkušnjo prvega zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-586">**Attempt** - The number of times that the first run experience needs to retry.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-587">**IsDefaultNotebookCreated** – označuje, ali je OneNote ustvaril uporabniški privzeti zvezek ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-587">**IsDefaultNotebookCreated** - Indicates whether OneNote has created a user's default notebook or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-588">**IsDelayedSignIn** – označuje, ali je prvi zagon v zakasnitvi pri vpisu, kjer se uporabniku ni treba vpisati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-588">**IsDelayedSignIn** - Indicates whether the first run is in delayed sign-in mode where a user is not required to signed-in.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-589">**IsMSA** – označuje, ali je račun Microsoftov račun ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-589">**IsMSA** - Indicates whether an account is Microsoft account or not.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-591">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja, da lahko novi uporabniki (Microsoftov račun) prvič uspešno zaženejo in začnejo uporabljati OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-591">The critical signal used to ensure new consumer users (Microsoft Account) can successfully launch and use OneNote for the first time.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-596">**Napaka A** – predmet napake označuje napako med napako med prvim zagonom, če pride do nje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-596">**Error A** - OneNote's error object indicates an error during an error during the first run if any.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-597">**FAllowAddingGuide** – označuje, ali bo OneNote omogočil ustvarjanje zvezka za vodenje ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-597">**FAllowAddingGuide** - Indicates whether OneNote will allow creating a guide notebook or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-598">**FrozenOneDriveAccount** – označuje, ali je račun OneDrive zamrznjen ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-598">**FrozenOneDriveAccount** - Indicates whether a OneDrive account is frozen or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-599">**IsDefaultNotebookCreated** – označuje, ali je OneNote ustvaril uporabniški privzeti zvezek ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-599">**IsDefaultNotebookCreated** - Indicates whether OneNote has created a user's default notebook or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-600">**NoInternetConnection** – označuje, ali naprava nima nameščene internetne povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-600">**NoInternetConnection** - Indicates whether a device does not have internet connection.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-601">**ProvisioningFailure** – predmet napake v OneNote, ki označuje napako pri omogočanju uporabe, če pride do nje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-601">**ProvisioningFailure** - A OneNote error object indicating a provisioning error if any.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-602">**ProvisioningFinishedTime** – označuje končni čas, ko OneNote dokonča omogočanje uporabe zvezka med izkušnjo prvega zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-602">**ProvisioningFinishedTime** - Indicates the end time when OneNote finishes provisioning a notebook during first run experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-603">**ProvisioningStartedTime** – označuje začetni čas, ko OneNote začne omogočati uporabo zvezka med izkušnjo prvega zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-603">**ProvisioningStartedTime** - Indicates the start time when OneNote starts provisioning a notebook during first run experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-604">**ShowSuggestedNotebooks** – označuje, ali OneNote prikaže funkcijo predlaganega zvezka ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-604">**ShowSuggestedNotebooks** - Indicates whether OneNote will show a suggested notebook feature or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="officetargetedmessagingensurecached"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-622">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-622">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-623">Spremlja prenos paketa za Dynamic Canvas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-623">Tracks if a package for Dynamic Canvas was downloaded.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-624">Obravnavamo ga kot konfiguracijo programske opreme, ker mora biti paket uspešno prenesen, da odjemalec lahko uporablja ustrezno izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-624">Considered a software configuration because the package must be successfully downloaded to enable the client to render the right experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-625">Še posebej je pomemben pri naročninah za potrošnike, kjer prek platna komuniciramo z uporabnikom, ki mu je potekla licenca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-625">Is especially critical in consumer subscriptions where we use canvas to communicate to the user that the license has expired.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-626">Z njim spremljamo metapodatke paketa dinamične vsebine, prenesene z izdelkom in shranjene v predpomnilnik, ter rezultatov izvedenih postopkov za paket: napake pri prenosu, napake pri razpakiranju, napake pri preverjanju doslednosti, zadetki v predpomnilniku, uporabe paketa, uspešni prenosi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-626">Used to track metadata of a dynamic content package downloaded and cached by the product as well as results of operations performed on the package: download failures, unpacking failures, consistency checks failures, cache hits, package usages, download sources.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-627">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-627">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-628">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated** – Logična zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bila mapa predpomnilnika uspešno ustvarjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-628">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated -** Boolean flag indicating if cache folder creation succeed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-629">**Data\_CdnPath – Izvorni naslov paketa.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-629">**Data\_CdnPath – source address of the package-**</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-630">**Data\_EnsureCached** – Logična zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil paket vsebine shranjen v predpomnilnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-630">**Data\_EnsureCached -** Boolean flag indicating if content package was cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-631">**Data\_ExistsAlready** – Logična zastavica, ki označuje, da je bil paket že prenesen v preteklosti in da je bil zaznan vnovični poskus prenosa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-631">**Data\_ExistsAlready -** Boolean flag indicating that the package was already downloaded before and there was another attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-632">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed** – Izvorni paket ni na voljo v izvorni datoteki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-632">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed -** source package not available in source</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-633">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder** – Težave z lokalnim diskom, zaradi katerih prihaja do napak pri ustvarjanju imenika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-633">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder -** local disk issues causing failure in directory creation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-634">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da je bil paket prenesen, vendar ga odjemalec ne more brati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-634">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed -** flag indicating if package was downloaded, but the client can’t read it</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-635">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess** – Uspešni poskusi branja paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-635">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess -** successful attempts to read the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-636">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess** – Ni zaznanih težav z diskom ali konfiguracijo, ki bi preprečevale branje toka datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-636">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess -** no disk issues nor configuration issues which doesn’t let the file stream to be read</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-637">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed** – Relativna pot ne pripelje do dostopnega mesta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-637">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed -** relative path doesn’t point to accessible location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-638">**Data\_HashActualValue** – Zgoščena vrednost, pridobljena iz imena datoteke, ko je bil paket uporabljen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-638">**Data\_HashActualValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-639">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed** – Napaka z izračunom zgoščene vrednosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-639">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed -** error with calculation of a hash</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-640">**Data\_HashMatchFailed** – Neujemanje zgoščenih vrednosti imena datoteke in predpomnjenih vrednosti registra.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-640">**Data\_HashMatchFailed -** hash mismatch between the package name and registry values cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-641">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess** – Uspešno preverjanje doslednosti zgoščene vrednosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-641">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess -** hash consistency check success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-642">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed** – Paketa ni mogoče prenesti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-642">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed -** can’t download the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-643">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData** – Preneseni paket ne vsebuje nobenih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-643">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData -** downloaded package contains no data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-644">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess** – Uspešen prenos paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-644">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess -** successful download of a package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-645">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess** – Stanja poskusov razpakiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-645">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess -** unpacking attempts statuses</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-646">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed** – Neuspešni poskusi odpiranja datoteke paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-646">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed -** failed attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-647">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess** – Uspešni poskusi odpiranja datoteke paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-647">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess -** successful attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-648">**Data\_SuccessHashValue** – Zgoščena vrednost, pridobljena iz imena datoteke, ko je bil paket prenesen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-648">**Data\_SuccessHashValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was downloaded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-649">**Data\_SuccessSource** – Platforma, za katero je bil paket prenesen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-649">**Data\_SuccessSource -** surface for which the package was downloaded</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidodwxpssotelemetry"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1227">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1227">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1228">S tem dogodkom boste lažje razumeli, s katero drugo Microsoftovo aplikacijo v napravi se je v naši aplikaciji izvedela tiha enotna prijava, s katere točke vnosa itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1228">This event helps in understanding with which other Microsoft app in the device, our app got silent single sign on, from which entry point and so on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1229">Prav tako pomaga pri razumevanju vzroka napake za neuspešno tiho enotno prijavo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1229">Also helps in understanding the failure reason for not getting silent single sign on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1230">Pridobivamo boljše vpoglede, na primer, iz katere Microsoftove aplikacije v napravi smo pridobili izkušnjo enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1230">We get better insights like from which Microsoft app in the device, we are getting single sign on experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1231">Ukrepi, kjer enotna prijava ne deluje pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1231">Act upon failures, where single sign on is not working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1232">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1232">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1233">**AccountType** – Označuje vrsto računa, s katerim je bila izvedena enotna prijava, denimo osebni Microsoftov račun ali službeni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1233">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which single sign on is happening, like personal Microsoft account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1234">**EntryPoint** – Označuje vstopno točko v aplikaciji, s katere je bil inicializiran poskus enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1234">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where single sign on attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1235">**ErrorCode** – Označuje kodo napake pri poskusu enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1235">**ErrorCode** - Indicates the error code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1236">**ErrorDescription** – Označuje sporočilo o napaki poskusa enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1236">**ErrorDescription** - Indicates the error message of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1237">**HResult** – Označuje rezultat kode stanja pri poskusu enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1237">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1238">**ProviderPackageId** – Druga Microsoftova aplikacija v napravi, iz katere se je izvedla enotna prijava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1238">**ProviderPackageId** - Other Microsoft app in the device from which single sign on is happening.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidphonenumbersignins"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1239">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1239">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1240">S tem dogodkom poskušamo razumeti, ali se je uporabnik prijavil ali vpisal z računom, povezanim s telefonsko številko, ali z računom, povezanim z e-poštnim naslovom osebnega Microsoftovega računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1240">This event helps in understanding if user signed in or signed up with phone number-based account or email based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1241">S tem dogodkom določimo število uporabnikov, ki se prijavljajo ali vpisujejo z osebnim Microsoftovim računom, povezanim s telefonsko številko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1241">This event helps in knowing count of users signing in or signing up with phone number based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1242">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1242">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1243">**EntryPoint** – Označuje vstopno točko v aplikaciji, s katere je bil inicializiran poskus vpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1243">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1244">**IsEmailMissing** – Ali je v podatkih profila računa naveden e-poštni naslov?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1244">**IsEmailMissing** - Is email missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1245">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** – Ali je v podatkih profila računa navedena telefonska številka?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1245">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** - Is phone number missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1246">**UserDecision** – Označuje izbiro uporabnika, kot je vpis ali prijava oz. poznejši vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1246">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidusersignindecision"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1247">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1247">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1248">S tem dogodkom poskušamo razumeti, na kateri stopnji je prišlo do težave pri vpisu, zakaj vpis ni bil uspešen, koliko uporabnikov se je uspešno vpisalo iz določene vstopne točke v aplikaciji itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1248">This event helps in understanding at which stage user is dropping in sign in flow, why sign in is failing, how many users are getting signed in successfully from which entry point in the app and so on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1249">S tem dogodkom lažje usmerjamo podatke o vpisu, ki so nam v pomoč pri določanju, na kateri stopnji uporabniki naletijo na težave itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1249">This event helps with sign-in funnel data, which helps in understand at which stage users are getting dropped more and so on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1250">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1250">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1251">**AccountType** – Označuje vrsto računa, s katerim je bil izveden poskus vpisa, denimo osebni račun ali službeni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1251">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which sign-in is attempted like personal account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1252">**AfterLicensingState** – Označuje stanje licence aplikacije po dokončanem vpisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1252">**AfterLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state after sign-in completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1253">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** – Označuje, koliko prostih urejanj je poteklo, preden je bil izveden vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1253">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** - Indicates how many free edits have lapsed before sign-in was attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1254">**BeforeLicensingState** – Označuje stanje licence aplikacije pred vpisom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1254">**BeforeLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state before sign-in attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1255">**CompletionState** – Označuje stopnjo dokončanja vpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1255">**CompletionState** - Indicates the stage of sign-in completion.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1256">**EntryPoint** – Označuje vstopno točko v aplikaciji, s katere je bil inicializiran poskus vpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1256">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1257">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** – Označuje število pospešenih vpisov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1257">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1258">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** – Označuje število preklicanih pospešenih vpisov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1258">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups cancelled.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1259">**HResult** – Označuje rezultat kode stanja za vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1259">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the sign-in operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1260">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** – Ali je dovoljen vpis z računom, povezanim s telefonsko številko?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1260">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** - Is phone number-based sign-in allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1261">**LicenseActivationHResult** – Označuje stanje kode za poskus aktivacije licence.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1261">**LicenseActivationHResult** - Indicates the status code of license activation attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1262">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** – Označuje kodo sporočila iz storitve licenciranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1262">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** - Indicates the message code from licensing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1263">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** – Ali so prosta urejanja dovoljena?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1263">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** - Is free edits allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1264">**SignUpAttemptCount** – Označuje število poskusov prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1264">**SignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1265">**StartMode** – Označuje način, v katerem je bil zagnan poskus vpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1265">**StartMode** - Indicates the mode in which sign-in attempt was started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1266">**UserDecision** – Označuje izbiro uporabnika, kot je vpis ali prijava oz. poznejši vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1266">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1267">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1267">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1268">Ustvarjeno je ob zagonu odjemalca, če je končni uporabnik omogočil nadzorno ploščo za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1268">Generated on client startup when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1269">Zbira informacije o tem, kdaj je posrednik za telemetrijo sistema Office prenesel podatke v mapo v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1269">It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent has uploaded data to the share folder.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1270">Primarna uporaba tega dogodka je spremljanje ustreznosti stanja posrednika za telemetrijo sistema Office, sekundarna uporaba dogodka pa je ocena uporabe nadzorne plošče za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1270">The primary use of this event is to monitor the health of the Office Telemetry agent and the secondary use of the event is to estimate usage of the Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1271">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1271">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1272">**UploadTime** – časovni žig zadnjega uspešnega prenosa, ki ga je izvedel posrednik za telemetrijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1272">**UploadTime** - the timestamp of the last successful upload performed by the Telemetry Agent.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentscanandupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1273">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentScanAndUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1273">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentScanAndUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1274">Podatki so zbrani le, če je uporabnik omogočil nadzorno ploščo za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1274">Only collected when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1275"> Zbira informacije o tem, kdaj se izvaja posrednik za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1275"> It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent is executed.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1276">  Ti podatki so zbrani le, če je nadzorna plošča za telemetrijo sistema Office omogočena in uporabljena za določanje ustreznosti stanja posrednika za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1276">  This is only collected when Office Telemetry Dashboard is enabled and is used to determine the health of Office Telemetry agent.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1277">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1277">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1278">**Data.AgentExit** – Časovni žig, ko se je posrednik za telemetrijo uspešno zaprl.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1278">**Data.AgentExit** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent exits successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1279">**Data.AgentScan** – Časovni žig, ko je posrednik za telemetrijo uspešno dokončal pregled.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1279">**Data.AgentScan** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completed a scan successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1280">**Data.AgentUpload** – Časovni žig, ko je posrednik za telemetrijo uspešno dokončal nalaganje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1280">**Data.AgentUpload** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completes the upload successfully</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompattelemetrydashboardresiliencycrashlog"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1281">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1281">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1282">Ti podatki so zbrani le, če je končni uporabnik (najverjetneje skrbnik) omogočil nadzorno ploščo za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1282">Only collected when Office Telemetry Dashboard has been enabled by end user (most likely an admin).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1283">Zbira pojavitve dodatkov za Office in zrušitve dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1283">It collects the occurrence of Office Add-ins and documents crashes.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1284"> Ti podatki so zbrani le, če je končni uporabnik omogočil nadzorno ploščo za telemetrijo sistema Office. Z njimi določimo morebitno povečano pojavitev dodatkov ali zrušitev dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1284"> This is only collected when user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard and is used to determine if there is an increased occurrence of add-in or document crashes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1285">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1285">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1286">**Data.CollectionTime** – Časovni žig, kdaj je bil zabeležen dogodek zrušitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1286">**Data.CollectionTime** - Timestamp of when a crash event was logged</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_activateperpetual"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1287">Office_Apple_ActivatePerpetual</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1287">Office_Apple_ActivatePerpetual</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1288">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1288">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1289">Dogodek uporabljamo za nadzorovanje ustreznosti stanja stalnega postopka aktiviranja ter preiskovanje vzrokov napak na osnovi pregleda vrednosti FailedAt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1289">The event is used to monitor the health of the perpetual activation flow as well as investigating causes of failures by reviewing the FailedAt values.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1297">**Data_ActivatingPrimaryIdentity** – vrednost true/false, ki označuje, ali je bila uporabljena primarna identiteta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1297">**Data_ActivatingPrimaryIdentity** - A true/false value denoting if the primary identity was used.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1300">Ta dogodek se zbira za Officeove programe, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1300">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1301">Dogodek se uporablja za zajemanje napak pri ustvarjanju žetonov za preverjanje pristnosti med InAppPurchase v računalniku Mac (dogodek zabeleži kodo napake, ki jo je prejel).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1301">The event is used for capturing auth token generation failures during InAppPurchase on the Mac (the event logs the error code received).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1302">Ta dogodek se uporablja za odkrivanje in pomoč pri odpravljanju napak pri ustvarjanju žetonov za preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1302">This event is used for detecting and helping troubleshoot auth token generation failures</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1304">**Data_EmptyAuthToken** – zbrali smo niz, ki predstavlja, kje v neprekinjenem poteku licence je prišlo do napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1304">**Data_EmptyAuthToken** - We collect a string representing where in the activate perpetual license flow we failed.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_inappassociationactivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1307">Office_Apple_InAppAssociationActivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1307">Office_Apple_InAppAssociationActivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1308">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1308">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1309">Zbiramo informacije, povezane s povezavo izdelka po nakupu znotraj aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1309">We collect information related to product association after an in-app purchase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1310">Zabeležimo, katero inventarno številko naročnine povezujemo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1310">We log which subscription SKU we are associating.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1311">To se uporablja za nadzorovanje ustreznosti stanja povezav izdelkov pri nakupu znotraj aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1311">This is used to monitor the health of the in-app purchase product associations.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1313">**Data_ProductID** – inventarna številka naročnine, s katero poskušamo povezati izdelek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1313">**Data_ProductID** - The subscription SKU we are trying to associate the product to.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_inapppurchaseactivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1314">Office_Apple_InAppPurchaseActivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1314">Office_Apple_InAppPurchaseActivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1315">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1315">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1316">Zbiramo informacije, povezane z nakupi izdelkov v trgovini AppStore.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1316">We collect information related to product purchases on the AppStore.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1317">Sledimo rezultatu postopka nakupa (neuspešen, uspešen, težava s plačilom ipd.), vrsti zahteve za nakup (obnovitev, nakup) in inventarni številki/izdelku, ki je predmet nakupa (Office 365 Home itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1317">We track the result of the purchase (Failure, success, payment issue, etc.), the type of the purchase request (restore, purchase) and the SKU/product being purchased (Office 365 Home, etc.).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1318">Te podatke uporabljamo za nadzorovanje ustreznosti stanja postopkov nakupa znotraj aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1318">This data is used for monitoring the health of the in-app purchase flows.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1319">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1319">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1320">**Data_ Data_PurchaseResult** – rezultat postopka nakupa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1320">**Data_ Data_PurchaseResult** - The result of the purchase operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1321">**Data_ProductID** – izdelek, ki je predmet nakupa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1321">**Data_ProductID** - The product being purchased</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1322">**Data_PurchaseRequestType** – vrsta zahteve za nakup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1322">**Data_PurchaseRequestType** - The type of purchase request</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_intune"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1323">Office_Apple_InTune</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1323">Office_Apple_InTune</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1324">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1324">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1325">Zbiramo informacije o tem, ali je trenutna seja upravljana s storitvijo Intune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1325">We collect whether the current session is Intune-managed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1326">Ta dogodek se uporablja za določevanje/filtriranje sej, upravljanih s storitvijo Intune, in nam omogoča, da raziščemo morebitne težave, povezane z Officeom, ki se izvaja kot aplikacija, upravljana s storitvijo Intune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1326">This is used to pivot/filter on Intune managed sessions and allows us to investigate potential issues related to Office being run as an Intune-managed application.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1327">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1327">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1328">**Data_EventID** – zbiramo podatke o nizu, ki predstavlja kodo, ki označuje, ali je seja upravljana s storitvijo Intune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1328">**Data_EventID** - We collect a string representing a code that indicates whether the session is intune-managed.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_licensing_mac_licensingstate"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1329">Office_Apple_Licensing_Mac_LicensingState</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1329">Office_Apple_Licensing_Mac_LicensingState</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1330">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1330">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1331">Dogodek zajame trenutno stanje licence za sejo v računalniku (ID licence OLS, inventarna številka, ki se uporablja, dovoljeno obdobje ali njegova odsotnost, način zmanjšane funkcionalnosti ipd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1331">The event captures the current state of the license for a session in a machine (OLS license id, SKU being used, grace-period or not, RFM, etc.).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1332">Zbrane podatke uporabljamo za odkrivanje napak in preiskovanje vzrokov napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1332">The data collected is used for detecting errors and investigating causes of failures.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1333">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1333">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1334">**Data_DidRunPreview** – niz, ki označuje, ali se ta seja izvaja v predogledu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1334">**Data_DidRunPreview** - A string indicating if this session is run under preview</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1335">**Data_LicensingACID** – niz, ki predstavlja notranji identifikator sistema licenciranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1335">**Data_LicensingACID** - A string representing a licensing system internal identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1336">**Data_LicensingType** – niz, ki predstavlja vrsto licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1336">**Data_LicensingType** - A string representing the type of license</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1337">**Data_OLSLicenseId** – niz, ki predstavlja identifikator licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1337">**Data_OLSLicenseId** - A string representing a license identifier</span></span>
