#### <a name="office_docs_apple_docsuxiossaveasthroughfilemenu"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1360">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1360">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1361">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1361">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1362">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se izvede operacija »Shrani kot«, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o datotečnih operacijah, kot so kategorije mest.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1362">The event records when a “Save as” operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1363">Operacija »Shrani kot« se izvede vsakič, ko uporabnik ustvari novo datoteko in jo shrani prvič ali ko shrani kopijo obstoječe datoteke na novo mesto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1363">A “Save as” operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1364">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1364">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1365">**Data_OriginServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija izvirnega mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1365">**Data_OriginServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the original location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1366">**Data_ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija novega mesta datoteke po dokončanem shranjevanju, na primer »SharePoint« , »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1366">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the new location of a file after the save is completed like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docs_apple_docsuxmacatmentioninsertedatmention"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1367">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXMacAtMentionInsertedAtMention</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1367">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXMacAtMentionInsertedAtMention</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1368">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1368">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1369">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik @omeni drugega uporabnika, uporablja pa se za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi tega, kako uporabniki sodelujejo z drugimi uporabniki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1369">This event records when a user “@” mentions another user and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on how users collaborate with other users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1370">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1370">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1371">**Data_CharactersTyped** – številska vrednost, ki označuje skupno število znakov vnesenega besedila @omembe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1371">**Data_CharactersTyped** - A numerical value that indicates the total number of characters typed in the “@” mention text.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docs_apple_docsuxmacodspsharingwebviewsharingcompleted"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1372">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXMacODSPSharingWebViewSharingCompleted</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1372">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXMacODSPSharingWebViewSharingCompleted</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1373">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1373">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1374">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik da dokument v oblaku v skupno rabo z uporabo izkušnje dajanja v skupno rabo OneDrive, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1374">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1375">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1375">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1376">**Data_ShareType** – vprogramiran niz, ki označuje, katera vrsta operacije za skupno rabo je bila dokončana, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »Kopiranje povezave«, »Več aplikacij« in »Teams«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1376">**Data_ShareType** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share operation was completed including but not limited to “Copy Link”, “More apps”, “Teams”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1377">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** – vprogramiran niz, ki označuje, kakšen način skupne rabe je bil aktiven, ko je bilo dokončano dajanje v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »ManageAccess«, »AtMentions« in »Skupna raba«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1377">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share mode was active when the share was completed including but not limited to “ManageAccess”, “AtMentions”, “Share”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_collaboration_coauthorgalleryrowtapped"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1378">Office_DocsUI_Collaboration_CoauthorGalleryRowTapped</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1378">Office_DocsUI_Collaboration_CoauthorGalleryRowTapped</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1379">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1379">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1380">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko si uporabnik ogleda seznam trenutnih soavtorjev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1380">This event records when a user selects to look at the list of current co-authors.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1381">Te podatke uporabljamo za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj, povezanih s sočasnim soavtorstvom dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1381">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to co-authoring a document at the same time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1382">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1382">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1383">**Data_CoauthorCount** – številska vrednost, ki predstavlja skupno število oseb, ki trenutno urejajo isti dokument kot uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1383">**Data_CoauthorCount** - A numerical value that represents the total number of people who are currently editing the same document as the user.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1385">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1385">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1386">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se spremeni število aktivnih soavtorjev v dokumentu v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1386">The event records when the number of active co-authors in a cloud document changes.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1387">Te podatke uporabljamo za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj, povezanih s sočasnim soavtorstvom dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1387">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to co-authoring a document at the same time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1388">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1388">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1389">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** – število soavtorjev, ki so se pridružili dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1389">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** - The number of co-authors that joined the document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1390">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** – število soavtorjev, ki so zapustili dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1390">**Data_CoauthorsLeft** - The number of co-authors that left the document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1393">**Data_ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1393">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_docstage_docstagecreatenewfromtemplate"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1394">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1394">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1395">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1395">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1396">Dogodek zabeleži, ko je ustvarjena nova datoteka na osnovi izkušnje »Novo iz predloge«, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o ustvarjanju dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1396">The event records when a new file is created from the “New from template” experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on document creation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1397">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1397">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1398">**Data_InHomeTab** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila nova datoteka iz predloge ustvarjena na zavihku »Osnovno« datoteke Nova izkušnja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1398">**Data_InHomeTab** - A Boolean value that indicate whether the new file from template was created from the Home tab of the file new experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1399">**Data_InSearch** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila datoteka ustvarjena, ko je uporabnik iskal predlogo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1399">**Data_InSearch** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1400">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je zavihek »Osnovno« trenutno na voljo uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1400">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1401">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je izkušnja »Priporočeno« trenutno na voljo uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1401">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the “Recommended” experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1402">**Data_TemplateIndex** – številski indeks datoteke predloge, kot je vizualno prikazan uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1402">**Data_TemplateIndex** - The numerical index of the template file as it is displayed visually to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1403">**Data_TemplateType** – klasifikacija za boljše razlikovanje vrste predloge, kar med drugim vključuje tudi predloge »V spletu«, predloge »Spletno iskanje« in predloge »Lokalno«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1403">**Data_TemplateType** - A classification to help distinguish the type of template like, but not limited to, “Online” templates, “Online search” templates, “Local” templates.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_docstage_recommendedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1404">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_RecommendedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1404">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_RecommendedOpen</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1405">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1405">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1406">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se operacija odpiranja datoteke izvede iz razdelka za priporočene datoteke v galeriji dokumentov, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o operaciji odpiranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1406">The event records when a file-open operation takes place from the recommended files section of the document gallery and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1410">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1410">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1411">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se izvede operacija za odpiranje datoteke, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o operaciji odpiranja datoteke, kot so kategorije mest »ServiceType« in prvi štirje znaki pripone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1411">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories “ServiceType” and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1412">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1412">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1413">**Data_Ext** – pripona datoteke, omejena na največ prve štiri znake pripone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1413">**Data_Ext** - The file extension limited to the first four characters of the extension or less.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1414">**Data_ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1414">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_opendocumentmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1415">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenDocumentMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1415">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenDocumentMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1416">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformi iOS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1416">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1417">Dogodek se zabeleži ob odpiranju datoteke, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj glede na informacije o odpiranju datoteke, zlasti informacije o učinkovitosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1417">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories “ServiceType” and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1418">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1418">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1419">**Data_AppDuration** – Čas, zahtevan za obdelavo aplikacije med odpiranjem datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1419">**Data_AppDuration** - The duration spent in application processing during a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1420">**Data_BootDuration** – Čas, zahtevan za zagon postopka za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1420">**Data_BootDuration** - The duration of boot process of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1421">**Data_ClickOrigin** – Niz, ki označuje, izvirno mesto povezave, ko je uporabnik kliknil povezavo v Outlooku v sistemu iOS za odpiranje datoteke v Officeovi aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1421">**Data_ClickOrigin** - A string indicating which part the link was from when user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open a file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1422">**Data_ClickTime** – čas Unixa, ko je uporabnik kliknil povezavo v Outlooku v sistemu iOS za odpiranje datoteke v Officeovi aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1422">**Data_ClickTime** - The Unix epoch time when the user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open the file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1423">**Data_DetachedDuration** – Trajanje, zahtevano za odpenjanje postopka dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1423">**Data_DetachedDuration** - The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1424">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja način za dostop datoteke, npr. samo za branje, branje in pisanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1424">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1425">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja vrsto asinhronega poteka, ki se uporablja za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1425">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** - An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1426">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja vrsto algoritma za razdruževanje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1426">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1427">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja stanje zaščite poslovnih podatkov datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1427">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1428">**Data_Doc_Ext** – Datotečna pripona datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1428">**Data_Doc_Ext** - File extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1429">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – Ime gostitelja strežnika datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1429">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1430">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa ime gostitelja strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1430">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1431">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – GUID, ki enolično prepozna identiteto, uporabljeno za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1431">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the identity used to open a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1432">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje podrobno vrsto scenarija pri odpiranju datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1432">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1433">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje V-/I-zastavice postopka za odpiranje datoteke, npr. ali je bila datoteka predpomnjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1433">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, e.g. if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1434">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** – Ali je za datoteko omogočeno sodelovanje v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1434">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** - Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1435">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta s funkcijo postopnega odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1435">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1436">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – Ali datoteka podpira Officeovo storitev sodelovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1436">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1437">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta iz predpomnjene kopije brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1437">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1438">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** – Ali je bila datoteka vnaprej pridobljena, preden se je zagnal postopek odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1438">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** - Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1439">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – Ali je na voljo lokalna različica datoteke, ki je sinhronizirana s strežnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1439">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1440">**Data_Doc_Location** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje mesto datoteke, npr. lokalno ali v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1440">**Data_Doc_Location** - An enumeration indicating where the file is located, e.g. locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1441">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje razlog datoteke, ki je samo za branje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1441">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1442">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa ID vira strežnika datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1442">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource id of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1443">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto kanala v realnem času (RTC), ki ga uporablja datoteka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1443">**Data_Doc_RtcType** - An enumeration indicating type of real-time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1444">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – GUID, ki enolično določa ID dokumenta strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1444">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1445">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje protokol strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1445">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1446">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1446">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1447">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje različico strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1447">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1448">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – Celo število, ki se poveča za 1 za vsak postopek odpiranja datoteke v seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1448">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - An integer which is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1449">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – Niz, ki se uporablja za korelacijo odjemalskih in strežniških dnevnikov, po navadi je to neke vrste ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1449">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - A string used to correlate client-side and server-side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1450">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – Velikost datoteke v bajtih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1450">Data**Size:long** - File size in bytes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1451">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto posebnega znaka, ki ga ima URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1451">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1452">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1452">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1453">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta postopoma z vnaprej predpomnjenimi podatki WRS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1453">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre-cached WRS data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1454">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – Niz, ki označuje, iz katere storitve je datoteka WOPI (Web Application Interface Protocol).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1454">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - A string indicating which service a WOPI (Web Application Open Platform Interface Protocol) file is from.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1455">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** – Vrednost niza, ki beleži čas, zahtevan za klice funkcij, v obliki zapisa z oznako funkcije ter trajanjem, ki vključuje trajanje klicev podfunkcij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1455">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which includes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1456">**Data_InitializationReason** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje, način odpiranja datoteke, npr. iz katerega elementa uporabniškega vmesnika oz. odpiranje sprožila aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1456">**Data_InitializationReason** - An enumeration indicating how the file is opened, e.g. from which UI element or trigged by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1457">**Data_Measurements** – Vrednost niza, ki beleži čas, zahtevan za klice funkcij, v obliki zapisa z oznako funkcije ter trajanjem, ki ne vključuje trajanje klicev podfunkcij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1457">**Data_Measurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which excludes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1458">**Data_OpenInPlace** – Ali je treba datoteko kopirati v vsebnik z varnostnimi omejitvami v Officeu, preden jo uporabnik lahko odpre.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1458">**Data_OpenInPlace** - Whether or not a file must be copied to the Office’s sandboxed container before user can open it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1459">**Data_OpenStartTime** – Čas Unixa, ko je bil zagnan postopek odpiranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1459">**Data_OpenStartTime** - The Unix epoch time when the file open started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1460">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** – Trajanje upodabljanja za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1460">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** - The duration of rendering of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1461">**Data_SourceApplication** – Niz, ki označuje ID snopa izvorne aplikacije, ko je postopek odpiranja datoteke sprožila aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1461">**Data_SourceApplication** - A string indicating the bundle ID of the source application when a file open was triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1462">**Data_StopwatchDuration** – Trajanje od začetka do konca dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1462">**Data_StopwatchDuration** - The duration from beginning of the event to the end of the event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1463">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** – Vrednost niza, ki beleži čas, zahtevan za klice funkcij, v obliki zapisa z oznako funkcije, časovnim žigom začetka in trajanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1463">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag, start timestamp and duration.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_openfilewithreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1464">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenFileWithReason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1464">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenFileWithReason</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1465">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1465">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1466">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se izvede operacija odpiranja datoteke, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o operaciji odpiranja datoteke, kot so kategorije mest »ServiceType« in mesto v aplikaciji, s katerega je uporabnik zahteval odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1466">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories “ServiceType” and from where within Application the user requested to open a file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1467">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1467">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1468">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** – to je logična vrednost, ki je zabeležena, če na podlagi pregleda poti datoteke menimo, da je morda iz mape, ki jo sinhronizira storitev DropBox.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1468">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** - This is a Boolean value that is logged if by inspecting the path of the file we think it might be from a folder that is sync’d by Drop Box.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1469">**Data_IsSignedIn** – označuje, ali je uporabnik pri shranjevanju datoteke vpisan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1469">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1470">**Data_OpenReason** – razlog za odpiranje je številska vrednost, ki označuje mesto v aplikaciji, s katerega je uporabnik odprl datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1470">**Data_OpenReason** - The open reason is a numerical value that indicates from where within the application a user opened a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1471">**Data_ServiceType** – abstraktna številska kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1471">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract numerical categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_savetourl"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1472">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_SaveToURL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1472">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_SaveToURL</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1473">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1473">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1474">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se izvede operacija »Shrani kot«, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o operaciji za datoteko, kot so kategorije mest in prvi štirje znaki pripone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1474">The event records when a “save as” operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1475">Operacija »Shrani kot« se izvede vsakič, ko uporabnik ustvari novo datoteko in jo shrani prvič ali ko shrani kopijo obstoječe datoteke na novo mesto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1475">A “save as” operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1476">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1476">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1477">**Data_FileExtension** – prvi štirje znaki pripone nove datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1477">**Data_FileExtension** - The first four characters of the new file’s extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1478">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** – označuje, ali je operacija shranjevanja izvedena za novo datoteko ali kopijo obstoječe datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1478">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** - Indicates if the save operation is for a new file or a copy of an existing file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1479">**Data_IsSignedIn** – označuje, ali je uporabnik pri shranjevanju datoteke vpisan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1479">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1480">**Data_SaveErrorCode** – številska vrednost, ki je nastavljena, če pride do napake, in pomaga prepoznati vrsto napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1480">**Data_SaveErrorCode** - A numerical value that is set if there is an error to help identify the kind of error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1481">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** – navaja domeno za SaveErrorCode, kot to določa Apple SaveErrorDomains »so poljubni nizi, ki se uporabljajo za razlikovanje skupin kod«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1481">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** - Specifies the domain of the SaveErrorCode as defined by Apple SaveErrorDomains “are arbitrary strings used to differentiate groups of codes”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1482">**Data_SaveLocation** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1482">**Data_SaveLocation** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1483">**Data_SaveOperationType** – številska vrednost, ki jo določa skupina vrednosti NSSaveOperationType družbe Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1483">**Data_SaveOperationType** - A numerical value defined by Apple’s NSSaveOperationType group of values.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_cloudupsellshown"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1484">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellShown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1484">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellShown</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1485">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1485">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1486">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik izvede postopek za shranjevanje dokumentov v oblak v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1486">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1487">Ti podatki so uporabljeni za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj, povezanih s premikanjem dokumentov na mesta v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1487">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1488">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1488">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1489">**Data_FileStyle** – številska vrednost, ki označuje, v kakšnem primeru je bila prikazana izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov, npr. na preklopnem stikalu za samodejno shranjevanje ali gumbu »Skupna raba«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1489">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like from an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1490">**Data_FileType** – prvi štirje znaki pripone trenutne datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1490">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file’s extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1491">**Data_InDocStage** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov prikazana v galeriji dokumentov ali v oknu dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1491">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1492">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je odprt tudi trenutni dokument, za katerega je prikazana izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1492">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1493">**Data_IsDraft** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila trenutna datoteka že kdaj shranjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1493">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1494">**Data_IsSheetModal** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov predstavljena modalno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1494">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_cloudupsellupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1495">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1495">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellUpload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1496">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1496">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1497">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik prenese novo ali lokalno datoteko v oblak in rezultat te operacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1497">This event records when a user chooses to upload a new or local file to the cloud and the result of that operation.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1498">Ti podatki so uporabljeni za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj, povezanih s premikanjem dokumentov na mesta v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1498">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1499">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1499">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1500">**Data_FileStyle** – številska vrednost, ki označuje, v kakšnem primeru je bila prikazana izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov, npr. na preklopnem stikalu za samodejno shranjevanje ali gumbu »Skupna raba«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1500">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1501">**Data_FileType** – prvi štirje znaki pripone trenutne datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1501">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file’s extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1502">**Data_InDocStage** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov prikazana v galeriji dokumentov ali v oknu dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1502">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1503">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali gre pri izbranem mestu za prenos dokumenta za privzeto mesto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1503">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** - A Boolean value that indicates if the selected location to upload the document to is the default location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1504">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je odprt tudi trenutni dokument, za katerega je prikazana izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1504">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1505">**Data_IsDraft** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila trenutna datoteka že kdaj shranjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1505">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1506">**Data_IsSheetModal** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov predstavljena modalno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1506">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1507">**Data_LocationServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1507">**Data_LocationServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1508">**Data_UploadAction** – vprogramiran niz, ki označuje, ali je pri prenosu v strežnik šlo za operacijo premikanja ali kopiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1508">**Data_UploadAction** - A hard coded string that indicates whether the upload was a move or a copy operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1509">**Data_UploadResult** – vprogramiran niz, ki označuje rezultat poskusa prenosa v strežnik, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »Success«, »UserCancelledUpload« in »PreAuthFailed«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1509">**Data_UploadResult** - A hard coded string that indicates the result of the attempt to upload including but not limited to ‘’Success”, “UserCancelledUpload”, and “PreAuthFailed”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_copylinkoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1510">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CopyLinkOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1510">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CopyLinkOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1511">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1511">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1512">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik da dokument v skupno rabo v oblak z ustvarjanjem povezave do dokumenta v oblaku, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1512">This event records when a user chooses to share a document by generating a link to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1513">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1513">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1514">**Data_ ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1514">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1515">**Data_LinkType** – vprogramiran niz, ki opisuje vrsto izvedene operacije povabila, npr. »ViewOnly« in »ViewAndEdit«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1515">**Data_LinkType** - A hard coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like “ViewOnly” and “ViewAndEdit”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1516">**Data_ShareScenario** – vprogramiran niz z opisom mesta v uporabniškem vmesniku aplikacije, s katerega je bila datoteka dana v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »FileMenu«, »OpenTabShareActionMenu« in »RecentTabShareActionMenu«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1516">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard-coded string description of where within the application’s user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, “FileMenu”, “OpenTabShareActionMenu”, “RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_docsuionedriveshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1517">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_DocsUIOneDriveShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1517">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_DocsUIOneDriveShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1518">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1518">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1519">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik da dokument v oblaku v skupno rabo z uporabo izkušnje dajanja v skupno rabo OneDrive, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1519">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1520">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1520">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1521">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** – številska vrednost, ki v primeru pojava napake pri izkušnji skupne rabe omogoča lažje prepoznavanje vzroka napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1521">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** - If the sharing experience experiences an error this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1522">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** – logična vrednost, ki v primeru vrednosti »true« označuje, da je bila operacija poenostavljenega dajanja v skupno rabo uspešno dokončana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1522">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** - A Boolean value that when true indicates that a lightweight sharing operation successfully completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1523">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** – številska vrednost, ki se v primeru uspešno dokončane operacije dajanja v skupno rabo uporablja za ugotavljanje vrste dokončane operacije dajanja v skupno rabo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1523">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** - When a share operation successfully completes this is a numerical value used to determine what kind of sharing operation was completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1524">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** – številska vrednost, ki omogoča lažje prepoznavanje vzroka napake, če se uporabniški vmesnik ne naloži.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1524">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** - If the user interface fails to load this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1525">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** – številska vrednost, ki zabeleži čas, ki je bil potreben za nalaganje spletnega uporabniškega vmesnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1525">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** - A numerical value that records the amount of time it took for the web user interface to load.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_invitepeople"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1526">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_InvitePeople</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1526">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_InvitePeople</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1527">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1527">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1528">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik povabi osebe v dokument v oblaku, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1528">This event records when a user chooses to invite people to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1529">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1529">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1530">**Data_ ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1530">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1531">**Data_InviteeCount** – skupno število stikov, povabljenih v dokument v okviru enega dejanja povabila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1531">**Data_InviteeCount** - The total number of contacts invited to a document in one invite action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1532">**Data_LinkType** – vprogramiran niz, ki opisuje vrsto izvedene operacije povabila, npr. »ViewOnly« in »ViewAndEdit«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1532">**Data_LinkType** - A hard-coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like “ViewOnly” and “ViewAndEdit”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1533">**Data_MessageLength** – številsko štetje skupnega števila znakov, poslanih v sporočilu s povabilom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1533">**Data_MessageLength** - A numerical count of the total number of characters sent in the invite message.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1534">**Data_ShareScenario** – vprogramiran niz z opisom mesta v uporabniškem vmesniku aplikacije, s katerega je bila datoteka dana v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »FileMenu«, »OpenTabShareActionMenu« in »RecentTabShareActionMenu«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1534">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application’s user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, “FileMenu”, “OpenTabShareActionMenu”, “RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_sendacopyoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1535">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_SendACopyOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1535">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_SendACopyOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1536">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1536">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1537">Dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik pošlje kopijo dokumenta, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1537">The event records when a user chooses to send a copy of a document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1538">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1538">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1539">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je zavihek »Osnovno« trenutno na voljo uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1539">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1540">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je izkušnja »Priporočeno« trenutno na voljo uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1540">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the “Recommended” experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1541">**Data_OperationType** – številska vrednost, ki označuje, katera vrsta operacije pošiljanja kopije se izvaja, npr. pošiljanje kopije v e-poštnem sporočilu ali pošiljanje kopije z nadzorom skupne rabe v storitvi družbe Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1541">**Data_OperationType** - A numerical value to indicate what kind of send a copy operation is taking place like sending a copy in an email or sending a copy through Apple’s share control.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1542">**Data_ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1542">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1543">**Data_ShareFileType** – vprogramiran niz z opisom vrste predmeta, ki se daje v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »Dokument«, »PDF« in »Slika«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1543">**Data_ShareFileType** - A hard coded string description of what type of object is being shared including but not limited to, “Document”, “PDF”, “Picture”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1544">**Data_ShareScenario** – vprogramiran niz z opisom mesta v uporabniškem vmesniku aplikacije, s katerega je bila datoteka dana v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »FileMenu«, »OpenTabShareActionMenu« in »RecentTabShareActionMenu«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1544">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application’s user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, “FileMenu”, “OpenTabShareActionMenu”, “RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1545">**Data_SharingService** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila datoteka ustvarjena, ko je uporabnik iskal predlogo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1545">**Data_SharingService** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_upsellshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1546">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_UpsellShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1546">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_UpsellShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1547">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1547">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1548">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik pri poskusu dajanja dokumenta v skupno rabo izvede postopek za shranjevanje dokumentov v oblak v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1548">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow when trying to share a document.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1549">Te podatke uporabljamo za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj, povezanih s premikanjem dokumentov na mesta v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1549">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1550">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1550">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1551">**Data_FileOperationResult** – številska vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila operacija uspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1551">**Data_FileOperationResult** - A numerical value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1552">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali uporabnik izvede postopek za shranjevanje dokumentov v oblak v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov iz izkušnje DocStage ali iz odprtega dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1552">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** - A Boolean to indicate if a user is going through the upsell to cloud flow from the DocStage experience or from an open document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1553">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali uporabnik obdrži lokalno kopijo dokumenta, ki je predmet prenosa na mesto v oblaku, ali obstoječi dokument premakne na mesto v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1553">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** - A Boolean to indicate if the use chose to keep a local copy of the document being uploaded to a cloud location or move the existing document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1554">**Data_NewFileType** – abstraktna kategorizacija novega mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1554">**Data_NewFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of the new location of the file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1555">**Data_OriginalFileType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1555">**Data_OriginalFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1556">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali uporabnik trenutni dokument prenese na mesto v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1556">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** - A Boolean to indicate if the user chose to upload the current document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1557">**Data_UploadError** – številska vrednost, ki označuje vrsto napake, do katere pride, če operacija prenosa datoteke v strežnik ne uspe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1557">**Data_UploadError** - A numerical value that indicates the kind of error that occurred if an upload operation fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1558">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bil pogled prikazan v meniju »Skupna raba«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1558">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** - A Boolean value to indicate if the view was shown from the share menu.</span></span>

#### <a name="officefileiocsiccachedfilecsiloadfilebasic"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1583">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiLoadFileBasic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1583">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiLoadFileBasic</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1584">S tem dogodkom lahko prepoznamo, ali je bila datoteka uspešno odprta v plasti FIO.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1584">Allows us to know if a file successfully opened from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1585">Uporabljamo ga za zagotavljanje ustreznosti delovanja funkcij in nadzor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1585">Used for feature health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1586">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1586">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1587">**Activity.Group** – Oznaka, ki omogoča združevanje nabora dogodkov nadzora za upravljanje uspešnega delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1587">**Activity.Group -** tag that allows a set of monitoring events to be grouped to manage overall success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1588">**Activity.IsHVA** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da je dogodek ključen za zagotavljanje uspešnega delovanja za uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1588">**Activity.IsHVA -** flag to indicate that event is critical to user success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1589">**Data.AsyncOpen** – Zastavica, ki označuje odpiranje vsebine, prejete potem, ko je bilo glavno telo dokumenta že odprto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1589">**Data.AsyncOpen -** flag to indicate the open had content that arrived after the main body was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1590">**Data.CacheFileId** – Povezava do telemetrije predpomnilnika Officeovih dokumentov za omogočanje analize posledic težav s predpomnilnikom na uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1590">**Data.CacheFileId -** connects to Office Document Cache telemetry to enable impact analysis of cache issues on the user experience</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1591">**Data. CFREnabled** – označuje, da je za sejo omogočena možnost CacheFileRuntime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1591">**Data.CFREnabled** - Indicates that CacheFileRuntime is enabled for the session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1592">**Data. CFRFailure** – označuje, da je CacheFileRuntime naletel na napako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1592">**Data.CFRFailure** - Indicated that CacheFileRuntime ran into error.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1593">**Data.CoauthStatus** – Poroča o stanju sodelovanja v dokumentu ob odpiranju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1593">**Data.CoauthStatus -** reports collaborative status of the document on Open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1594">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload** – Število vrnitev v strežnik, ki se uporablja za odpravljanje težav z učinkovitostjo delovanja in omrežjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1594">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1595">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload** – Število vrnitev v strežnik, ki se uporablja za odpravljanje težav z učinkovitostjo delovanja in omrežjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1595">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1596">**Data.DialogId** – To polje je nastavljeno, če je bilo pogovorno okno za UI prikazano med odpiranjem, in označuje, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilno sporočilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1596">**Data.DialogId -** Set if a UI dialog was displayed during Open, indicating a that a warning message was displayed to the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1597">**Data.DidFallbackToDAV** – To polje je nastavljeno, če je bil dokument odprt s starejšim protokolom za prenos datotek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1597">**Data.DidFallbackToDAV -** Set if the document was opened using an older file transfer protocol</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1598">**Data.Doc.AccessMode** – Dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1598">**Data.Doc.AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1599">**Data.Doc.AssistedReadingReasons** – To polje je nastavljeno, če je za dokument izbrana elektronska zaščita podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1599">**Data.Doc.AssistedReadingReasons -** Set if the document has electronic data protection in place</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1600">\*\*Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind – \*\* Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1600">**Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1601">**Data.Doc.ChunkingType** – Enote, uporabljene za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1601">**Data.Doc.ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1602">**Data.Doc.EdpState** – Nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1602">**Data.Doc.EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1603">**Data.Doc.Ext** – Pripona dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1603">**Data.Doc.Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1604">**Data.Doc.Extension** – Zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1604">**Data.Doc.Extension -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1605">**Data.Doc.FileFormat** – Različica protokola za obliko zapisa dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1605">**Data.Doc.FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1606">**Data.Doc.Fqdn** – Ime domene za OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1606">**Data.Doc.Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1607">**Data.Doc.FqdnHash** – Enostranska zgoščena vrednost imena domene, ki omogoča identifikacijo stranke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1607">**Data.Doc.FqdnHash -** One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1608">**Data.Doc.IdentityTelemetryId** – Enostranska zgoščena vrednost identitete uporabnika, uporabljena za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1608">**Data.Doc.IdentityTelemetryId -** A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1609">**Data.Doc.IdentityUniqueId** – Zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1609">**Data.Doc.IdentityUniqueId -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1610">**Data.Doc.InitializationScenario** – Zabeleži način odpiranja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1610">**Data.Doc.InitializationScenario -** Records how the document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1611">**Data.Doc.IOFlags** – Poroča o predpomnjenih zastavicah, uporabljenih za nastavitev možnosti zahtev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1611">**Data.Doc.IOFlags -** Reports on the cached flags used to set request options</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1612">**Data.Doc.IrmRights** – Dejanja, ki jih je dovolil pravilnik za elektronsko zaščito podatkov, ki velja za dokument/uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1612">**Data.Doc.IrmRights -** Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1613">**Data.Doc.IsCloudCollabEnabled** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da storitev podpira sodelovanje v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1613">**Data.Doc.IsCloudCollabEnabled -** Flag indicating that the service supports Cloud Collaboration</span></span>

#### <a name="officefileiocsiccachedfilecsisavefilebasic"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1708">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1708">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1709">S tem dogodkom lahko prepoznamo, ali je bila datoteka uspešno shranjena v plasti FIO.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1709">Allows us to know if a file was successfully saved from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1710">Uporabljamo ga za zagotavljanje ustreznosti delovanja funkcij in nadzor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1710">Used for Feature Health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1711">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1711">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1712">**Activity.Group** – Oznaka, ki omogoča združevanje nabora dogodkov nadzora za upravljanje uspešnega delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1712">**Activity.Group -** tag that allows a set of monitoring events to be grouped to manage overall success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1713">**Activity.IsHVA** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da je dogodek ključen za zagotavljanje uspešnega delovanja za uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1713">**Activity.IsHVA -** flag to indicate that event is critical to user success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1714">**Data.AsyncOpen** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da je bil odprt dokument z vsebino, prejeto potem, ko je bilo glavno telo dokumenta že odprto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1714">**Data.AsyncOpen -** flag to indicate that the document was opened with content that arrived after the main body was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1715">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered** – Diagnostika sledenja spremembam, vključno s podatki, da je bila zahtevana osnovna različica dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1715">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered -** Change tracking diagnostic indicating that the base version of the document was requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1716">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons** – Kode vzroka za blokirano stanje nalaganja (npr. samodejno shranjevanje je vklopljeno, dokument je v stanju prehoda).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1716">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons -** Reason codes for blocked upload state (e.g. Autosave is turned off, the document is transitioning)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1717">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting** – Nalaganje je blokirano, saj bi bil vnovičen poskus neuspešen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1717">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting -** Upload is blocked as it would fail if retried</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1718">**Data.CacheFileId** – Povezava do telemetrije predpomnilnika Officeovih dokumentov za omogočanje analize posledic težav s predpomnilnikom na uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1718">**Data.CacheFileId -** connects to Office Document Cache telemetry to enable impact analysis of cache issues on the user experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1719">**Data.ChartType** – Zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1719">**Data.ChartType -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1720">**Data.CoauthStatus** – Poroča o stanju sodelovanja v dokumentu ob shranjevanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1720">**Data.CoAuthStatus -** reports collaborative status of the document on Save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1721">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext** – Poroča o kontekstu (spajanje/postopno odpiranje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1721">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext -** reports context (Merge/Incremental Open)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1722">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload** – Število vrnitev v strežnik, ki se uporablja za odpravljanje težav z učinkovitostjo delovanja in omrežjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1722">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-1726">**Data.DialogChoice** – Zabeleži izbrane možnosti v katerih koli pogovornih oknih napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-1726">**Data.DialogChoice -** Records choice made in any error dialogs</span></span>

#### <a name="officemanageabilityclient-fetchpolicyprechecks"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2030">Office.Manageability.Client Fetch.PolicyPreChecks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2030">Office.Manageability.Client Fetch.PolicyPreChecks</span></span>
