#### <a name="officeonenotecanvasinkinkstrokelogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2042">Office.OneNote.Canvas.Ink.InkStrokeLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2042">Office.OneNote.Canvas.Ink.InkStrokeLogger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2045">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2045">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2046">**CurrentCanvasZoomFactor** – Trenutni dejavnik povečave platna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2046">**CurrentCanvasZoomFactor** - Current Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2047">**CurrentNotebook** – Identifikator trenutno aktivnega zvezka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2047">**CurrentNotebook** - Identifier of the current active notebook.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2048">**CurrentPage** – Identifikator trenutno aktivne strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2048">**CurrentPage** - Identifier of the current active page</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2049">**CurrentSection** – Identifikator trenutno aktivnega odseka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2049">**CurrentSection** - Identifier of the current active section.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2050">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** – Privzeti dejavnik povečave platna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2050">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** - Default Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2051">**InkStrokeCount** – Skupno število potez rokopisa od zadnjega dnevnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2051">**InkStrokeCount** - Total count of ink strokes since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2052">**InkStrokeWithLayerInkEffect** – Število potez rokopisa z učinkom črnila na plasteh od zadnjega dnevnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2052">**InkStrokeWithLayerInkEffect** - Count of ink strokes with layer ink effect since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2053">**InkStrokeWithoutPressureCount** – Število potez rokopisa brez pritiska od zadnjega dnevnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2053">**InkStrokeWithoutPressureCount** - Count of Ink Strokes without Pressure since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2054">**InkStrokeWithPencilInkEffect** – Število potez rokopisa z učinkom črnila svinčnika od zadnjega dnevnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2054">**InkStrokeWithPencilInkEffect** - Count of ink strokes with pencil ink effect since the last log.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenotenavigationcreatepage"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2056">Office.OneNote.Navigation.CreatePage</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2056">Office.OneNote.Navigation.CreatePage</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2057">Kritični signal, uporabljen za spremljanje možnosti uporabnikov OneNota za ustvarjanje strani v OneNotu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2057">Critical signal used to monitor the ability of OneNote users to create pages in OneNote.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2058">Telemetrija, uporabljena za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in ustreznosti stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2058">Telemetry used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2059">Če uporabniki ne morejo ustvariti strani, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2059">If users can’t create a page this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2060">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2060">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2061">**IsAtSectionEnd** – označuje, ali je na koncu odseka ustvarjena nova stran ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2061">**IsAtSectionEnd** - Indicates whether a new page is created at the end of section or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2062">**IsBlank** – označuje, ali je nova stran prazna ali pa je ustvarjena na podlagi predloge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2062">**IsBlank** - Indicates whether a new page is blanked page or created with a template.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2063">**IsRecentsView** – označuje, ali je stran ustvarjena na podlagi nedavnih elementov ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2063">**IsRecentsView** - Indicates whether a page is created from a recents or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2064">**NavView** – označuje, ali je stran ustvarjena na podlagi pogleda krmarjenja ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2064">**NavView** - Indicates whether a page is created from a navigation view or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2065">**NoteType** – označuje vrsto strani (hitra beležka, seznam ali fotografija).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2065">**NoteType** - Indicates the type (quick note, list, or photo) of a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2066">**QuickNoteType** – označuje vrsto strani (hitra beležka, seznam ali fotografija).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2066">**QuickNoteType** - Indicates the type (quick note, list, or photo) of a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2067">**RailState** – označuje stanje sledi krmarjenja OneNota pri ustvarjanju strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2067">**RailState** - Indicates the state of OneNote's navigation rail when creating a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2068">**Trigger** – označuje vhodno točko, na kateri se začne dejanje ustvarjanja strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2068">**Trigger** - Indicates an entry point where the create page action is started.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-ios-onenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-android"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2124">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (na iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (na Android)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2124">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on Android)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2125">To je kritični signal, ki se uporablja za nadzor zmogljivosti Lepljivih zapiskov za ustvarjanje zapiskov v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2125">This is a critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2126">Telemetrija se uporablja za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2126">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2127">Če uporabniki ne morejo ustvariti zapiska, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2127">If users can’t create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2128">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2128">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2129">**NoteLocalId** – razpoznavni enolični identifikator, ki je dodeljen zapisku v času, ko uporabnik ustvari zapiski v programu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2129">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time of a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2130">**IsExportable** – zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil dogodek rezultat dejanja uporabnika ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2130">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2131">Mora biti nastavljen na vrednost true, ker je NoteCreated dejanje, ki ga je sprožil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2131">Should be set to True as NoteCreated is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2132">**StickyNotes – SDKVersion** – številka različice, ki označuje različico Lepljivih zapiskov, ki jo uporablja uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2132">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2133">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerih različicah izdelka je prišlo do težave ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2133">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2143">**StickyNotes – SDKVersion** – številka različice, ki označuje različico Lepljivih zapiskov, ki jo uporablja uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2143">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2144">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerih različicah izdelka je prišlo do težave ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2144">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2179">**SyncDestinationType** – vrsta cilja sinhronizacije, tj. OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2179">**SyncDestinationType** -sync destination type, i.e. OneDrive or SharePoint Online</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2199">**AccountInfoSource** – Vir nastavitev računa (npr. samodejno odkrivanje, GuessSmart, samodejno zaznavanje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2199">**AccountInfoSource** - account settings source (e.g. AutoDiscover, GuessSmart, AutoDetect, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2200">**AccountType** – Vrsta konfiguriranega računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2200">**AccountType** – The type of account being configured.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationclose"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2271">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Close</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2271">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Close</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2272">Podatki so zbrani ob zapiranju PowerPointovih predstavitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2272">Collected when PowerPoint presentations are closed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2273">Ta dogodek vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav pri postopku zapiranja, ki vključuje shranjevanje in sinhroniziranje uporabnikovih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2273">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the close process which entail persisting and syncing the user's data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2274">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanje postopka zapiranja in uspešnega shranjevanja uporabnikove vsebine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2274">Microsoft uses this data to ensure that close is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2275">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2275">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2276">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – Ali ima ta dolgi vnos vso zahtevano telemetrijo dokumenta (polja »Data\_Doc\_\*«)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2276">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2277">Če je nima, zakaj?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2277">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2278">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bilo samodejno shranjevanje onemogočeno v tem dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2278">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string -** Predefined set of values of why was autosave disabled on this document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2279">(Napaka spajanja, napaka shranjevanja, pravilnik skupine itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2279">(Merge error, Save error, Group policy etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2280">**Data\_CloseReason:long** – Kako je bil izveden postopek zapiranja?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2280">**Data\_CloseReason:long -** How was close performed?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2281">Ali ste zaprli dokument?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2281">Closing document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2282">Ali ste zaprli aplikacijo?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2282">Closing app?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2283">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – Število neobravnavanih izjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2283">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Number of unhandled exceptions</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2284">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long** – Čas odpete dejavnosti/neizvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2284">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2285">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long** – Način odpiranja dokumenta (samo za branje/branje in pisanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2285">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2286">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2286">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2287">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long – \*\* Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2287">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2288">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long** – Način shranjevanja dokumenta v SharePointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2288">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2289">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long** – Stanje zaščite podatkov podjetja za dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2289">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2290">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2290">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2291">**Data\_Doc\_Extenstion:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2291">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2292">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za obliko zapisa datoteke (bolj podrobno kot za pripono).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2292">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2293">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string** – Mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2293">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2294">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost mesta shrambe dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2294">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2295">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string** – Enolični GUID uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2295">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2296">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string** – Enolični identifikator identitete, ki je bila uporabljena za dokumente v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2296">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2297">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long** – Bitna maska za različne zastavice danega dokumenta, povezane z V/I.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2297">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2298">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto upravljanja pravic do informacij, ki velja za ta dokument (»Forward«, »Reply«, »SecureReader«, »Edit« itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2298">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2299">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** – Ima vrednost »true«, če je bila že prejeta glava HTTP »IsCloudCollabEnabled«, ki njo je poslala zahteva OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2299">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2300">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** – Ali je bil dokument odprt postopoma (nova funkcija, ki odpre dokument tako, da ne prenese celoten dokument).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2300">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2301">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool** – Ali dokument podpira soavtorstvo z novo storitvijo OCS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2301">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2302">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** – Preverja, ali je bil dokument odprt v lokalnem predpomnilniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2302">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** verifies if document is being opened from local cache</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2303">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool** – Preverja, ali je bil dokument odprt v mapi, za katero je uporabljena aplikacija za povratno sinhronizacijo v storitvi OneDrive.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2303">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** verifies if document is being opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2304">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za mesto shranjevanja dokumenta (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, omrežje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2304">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2305">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti podrobnejše lokacije (mapa »Začasno«, mapa »Prenosi«, dokumenti storitve OneDrive, slike storitve OneDrive itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2305">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2306">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long** –Število soavtorjev, ko je bil dokument odprt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2306">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long -** Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2307">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za način šifriranja dokumenta z geslom (brez, geslo za branje, geslo za urejanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2307">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)-</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2308">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil ta dokument označen samo za branje (zaklenjeno v strežniku, dokončni dokument, zaščiteno z geslom za urejanje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2308">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2309">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost identifikatorja vira za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2309">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string -** Hash of resource identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2310">\*\*Data_Doc_RtcType – \*\*  označuje, kako je bil kanal v realnem času (RTC) nastavljen za trenutno datoteko (onemogočeno, nepodprto, na zahtevo, vedno vklopljeno itn.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2310">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2312">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, ki jih protokol uporablja za komunikacijo s strežnikom (Http, Cobalt, WOPI itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2312">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long -** Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2313">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto strežnika (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2313">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long -** Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2314">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long** – Preverja, ali strežnik temelji na sistemu Office14, Office15 ali Office 16.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2314">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long -** verifies if server is based off Office14, Office15 or Office 16</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2315">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long** – Ustvarjeni GUID, ki prepozna primerek dokumenta v seji istega procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2315">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2316">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string** – Neprosojen niz, običajno »GridManagerID.FarmID«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2316">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string -** An opaque string, typically GridManagerID.FarmID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2317">Uporabni podatki za korelacijo odjemalskega in strežniškega dnevnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2317">Useful for correlating client-side and server-side log</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2318">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long** – Velikost dokumenta v bajtih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2318">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2319">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long** – Bitna maska, ki označuje posebne znake v URL-ju ali poti dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2319">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long -** Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2320">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string** – Niz, ki prepozna ponudnika za shranjevanje dokumentov, npr. »DropBox«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2320">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string -** A string that identifies the document's storage provider, like "DropBox"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2321">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za stanje dokumenta Stream (na voljo, stalno onemogočeno, ni na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2321">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability:long -** Predefined set of values of status of document Stream(available, permanently disabled, not available)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2322">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost polnega URL-ja za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2322">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string -** hash of full URL of documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2323">**Data\_Doc\_UsedWrsDataOnOpen:bool** – Ima vrednost »true«, če je bila datoteka odprta postopoma z vnaprej predpomnjenimi podatki WRS na strani gostitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2323">**Data\_Doc\_UsedWrsDataOnOpen:bool -** true if the file was opened incrementally using pre cached WRS data on the host</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2324">**Data\_Doc\_WopiServiceId:string** – Identifikator storitve WOPI, npr. »Dropbox«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2324">**Data\_Doc\_WopiServiceId:string -** WOPI Service identifier, e.g. "Dropbox"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2325">**Data\_DocHasStorage:bool** – Ali ima ta dokument lokalno shrambo?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2325">**Data\_DocHasStorage:bool -** Does this document have local storage?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2326">**Data\_fLifeguarded:bool** – Ali je bil dokument kdaj zavarovan (funkcija za samodejno odpravljanje težav z dokumenti brez pozivanja uporabnika)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2326">**Data\_fLifeguarded:bool -** Was document ever lifeguarded (feature to fix document errors by themselves without prompting user)?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2327">**Data\_IsDocAutoSaveable:bool** – Ali je predstavitev mogoče samodejno shraniti?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2327">**Data\_IsDocAutoSaveable:bool -** Is presentation auto savable?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2328">**Data\_IsDocDirty:bool** – Ali predstavitev vključuje spremembe, ki še niso shranjene?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2328">**Data\_IsDocDirty:bool -** Does presentation have changes that are not yet saved?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2329">**Data\_IsNewDoc:bool** – Ali je dokument nov oz. obstoječ?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2329">**Data\_IsNewDoc:bool -** Is new document or existing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2330">**Data\_IsRecoveredDoc:bool** – Ali je bil dokument obnovljen?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2330">**Data\_IsRecoveredDoc:bool -** Is document recovered one?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2331">(Če se je prejšnja seja zrušila, je podokno za obnovitev dokumenta prikazano v naslednji seji).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2331">(If prior session crashed, we show document recovery pane on next session)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2332">**Data\_NewDocDiscarded:bool** – Ali je bila nova predstavitev zavržena brez shranjevanja?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2332">**Data\_NewDocDiscarded:bool -** Was new presentation discarded without being saved</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2333">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgCanceled:bool** – Če je v strežniku OCS čakajoče nalaganje in uporabnik zapre dokument, je uporabniku prikazano pogovorno okno s sporočilom, naj počaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2333">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgCanceled:bool -** If upload is pending on OCS while user closes document, dialog is popped up to user to wait.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2334">Katero možnost naj uporabnik izbere?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2334">Which option user chose?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2335">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgExpired:bool** – Ali je pogovorno okno samodejno poteklo (po 1 minuti)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2335">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgExpired:bool -** Did dialog expire (after 1 minute) on its own?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2336">**Data\_OCSClosingStatus:long** – Kakšno je končno stanje strežnika OCS (»In CSI«, »Closable«, »In OCS Transition«, »In CSI transition« itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2336">**Data\_OCSClosingStatus:long -** What’s final status of OCS (In CSI, Closable, In OCS Transition, In CSI transition, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2337">**Data\_OCSClosingWaitDurationMS:long** – Koliko časa je moral uporabnik čakati, da se je strežnik OCS naložil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2337">**Data\_OCSClosingWaitDurationMS:long -** How much time user had to wait for OCS to upload</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2338">**Data\_OCSHandleTransitionResult:long** – Vnaprej določen nabor vrednosti rezultatov prehoda, izvedenega med zapiranjem (poskus je bil že izveden, nadaljuj zapiranje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2338">**Data\_OCSHandleTransitionResult:long -** Predefined set of values of result of transition performed during close (Already tried, continue to close, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2339">**Data\_ServerDocId:string** – GUID za enolično identifikacijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2339">**Data\_ServerDocId:string -** GUID to uniquely identify a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2340">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long** – Skupni čas dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2340">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long -** Total time for Activity</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2341">**Data\_UserContinuedZRTClose:bool** – Ali je uporabnik izbral možnost »Nadaljuj« zapiranje, ko je bilo ob zapiranju dokumenta prikazano pogovorno okno?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2341">**Data\_UserContinuedZRTClose:bool -** Upon showing dialog on close, did user selected ‘Continue’ to close?</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationnewdocument"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2342">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2342">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2343">Dogodek je zbran, ko PowerPoint ustvari novo predstavitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2343">Collected when PowerPoint creates a new presentation.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2344"> Vključuje metrike uspešnosti, neuspešnosti in učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2344"> Includes success failure and performance metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2345">Te informacije uporabljamo za zagotavljanje uspešnega ustvarjanja datotek brez kakršnega koli zmanjšanja učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2345">This information is used to ensure we can create files successfully and with no degradation in performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2346">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2346">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2347">**NewDocumentType** – Ali je nov dokument ustvarjen iz predloge oz. povsem na novo?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2347">**NewDocumentType** – Whether new document is created from template or just created blank?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2348">**FLifeguarded** – Ali je življenjski cikel dokumenta zaščiten (funkcija, ki obnovi stanje poškodovanega dokumenta brez pozivanja uporabnika)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2348">**FLifeguarded** – Is document life guarded (feature that restores corrupt document state without prompting user)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationopencompleteprotocol"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2349">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2349">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2350">Podatki so zbrani ob odpiranju PowerPointovih predstavitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2350">Collected when PowerPoint opens presentations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2351">Ta dogodek vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav, do katerih pride v zadnji fazi postopka odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2351">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the end stages of the open process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2352">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanja funkcije in učinkovitega postopka odpiranja predstavitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2352">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and there is no degradation to opening presentations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2353">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2353">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2354">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto protivirusnega pregleda (IOAV, AMSI, None itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2354">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long -** Predefined set of values of type of AntiVirus scanned (IOAV, AMSI, None etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2355">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za protivirusni pregled, ki se izvede za vsak odprti dokument (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2355">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long -** Predefined set of values of anti-virus scan that happens for every document opened (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2356">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool** – Ali je bil ta dokument zaprt in nato znova odprt?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2356">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool -** Was this document closed and reopened?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2357">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long** – Čas odpete dejavnosti/neizvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2357">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2358">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long** – Način odpiranja dokumenta (samo za branje/branje in pisanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2358">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2359">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2359">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2360">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long – \*\* Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2360">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2361">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long** – Način shranjevanja dokumenta v SharePointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2361">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2362">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long** – Stanje zaščite podatkov podjetja za dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2362">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2363">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2363">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2364">**Data\_Doc\_Extenstion:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2364">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2365">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za obliko zapisa datoteke (bolj podrobno kot za pripono).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2365">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2366">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string** – Mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2366">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2367">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost mesta shrambe dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2367">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2368">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string** – Enolični GUID uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2368">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2369">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string** – Enolični identifikator identitete, ki je bila uporabljena za dokumente v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2369">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2370">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long** – Bitna maska za različne zastavice danega dokumenta, povezane z V/I.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2370">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2371">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto upravljanja pravic do informacij, ki velja za ta dokument (»Forward«, »Reply«, »SecureReader«, »Edit« itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2371">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2372">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** – Ima vrednost »true«, če je bila že prejeta glava HTTP »IsCloudCollabEnabled«, ki njo je poslala zahteva OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2372">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2373">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** – Ali je bil dokument odprt postopoma (nova funkcija, ki odpre dokument tako, da ne prenese celoten dokument).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2373">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2374">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool** – Ali dokument podpira soavtorstvo z novo storitvijo OCS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2374">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2375">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** – Ali je bil dokument odprt iz lokalnega predpomnilnika?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2375">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** Is document being opened from local cache?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2376">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool** –Ali je bil dokument odprt iz mape, za katero se uporablja aplikacija za povratno sinhronizacijo v storitvi OneDrive.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2376">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2377">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za mesto shranjevanja dokumenta (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, omrežje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2377">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2378">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti podrobnejše lokacije (mapa »Začasno«, mapa »Prenosi«, dokumenti storitve OneDrive, slike storitve OneDrive itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2378">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsave"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2409">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2409">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2410">Podatki so zbrani, kadar koli PowerPoint izvede postopek shranjevanja s potjo sodobne kode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2410">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the modern code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2411">Dogodek vsebuje vrsto rezultata uspešne oz. neuspešne metrike učinkovitosti shranjevanja in pomembne metapodatke dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2411">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2412"> Napake pri shranjevanju lahko privedejo do izgube podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2412"> Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2413">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanje funkcije in uspešnega shranjevanja uporabnikove vsebine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2413">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2414">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2414">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2415">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – Ali ima ta dolgi vnos vso zahtevano telemetrijo dokumenta (polja »Data\_Doc\_\*«)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2415">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2416">Če je nima, zakaj?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2416">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2417">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long** – Trajanje pridobivanja dokumenta pred dogodkom shranjevanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2417">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long -** Time taken to raise Document Before Save Event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2418">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long** – Trajanje preverjanja revizije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2418">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to check revision</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2419">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long** – Trajanje shranjevanja makrov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2419">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to save macros</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2420">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long** – Trajanje čiščenja zastavice za samodejno shranjevanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2420">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear AutoSave flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2421">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long** – Trajanje čiščenja zastavice nečistega dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2421">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear document dirty flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2422">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long** – Trajanje kloniranja dokumenta pred začetkom postopka shranjevanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2422">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clone document before starting the save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2423">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long** – Trajanje potrjevanja transakcije shranjevanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2423">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long -** Time taken to commit the save transaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2424">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – Nezaznane izvorne izjeme med izvajanjem dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2424">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2425">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long** – Čas odpete dejavnosti/neizvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2425">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2426">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long** – Način odpiranja dokumenta (samo za branje/branje in pisanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2426">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2427">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2427">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2428">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long – \*\* Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2428">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2429">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long** – Način shranjevanja dokumenta v SharePointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2429">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2430">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long** – Stanje zaščite podatkov podjetja za dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2430">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2431">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2431">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2432">**Data\_Doc\_Extenstion:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2432">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2433">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za obliko zapisa datoteke (bolj podrobno kot za pripono).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2433">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2434">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string** – Mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2434">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2435">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost mesta shrambe dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2435">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2436">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string** – Enolični GUID uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2436">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2437">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string** – Enolični identifikator identitete, ki je bila uporabljena za dokumente v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2437">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2438">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long** – Bitna maska za različne zastavice danega dokumenta, povezane z V/I.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2438">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2439">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto upravljanja pravic do informacij, ki velja za ta dokument (»Forward«, »Reply«, »SecureReader«, »Edit« itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2439">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2440">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** – Ima vrednost »true«, če je bila že prejeta glava HTTP »IsCloudCollabEnabled«, ki njo je poslala zahteva OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2440">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2441">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** – Ali je bil dokument odprt postopoma (nova funkcija, ki odpre dokument tako, da ne prenese celoten dokument).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2441">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2442">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool** – Ali dokument podpira soavtorstvo z novo storitvijo OCS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2442">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2443">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** – Preverja, ali je bil dokument odprt v lokalnem predpomnilniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2443">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** verifies if document being is opened from local cache</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2444">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool** –Ali je bil dokument odprt iz mape, za katero se uporablja aplikacija za povratno sinhronizacijo v storitvi OneDrive.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2444">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2495">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2495">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2496">Podatki so zbrani, kadar koli PowerPoint izvede postopek »Shrani kot«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2496">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a Save As.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2497">Dogodek vsebuje vrsto rezultata uspešne oz. neuspešne metrike učinkovitosti shranjevanja in pomembne metapodatke dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2497">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2498">Napake pri shranjevanju lahko privedejo do izgube podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2498">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2499">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanje funkcije in uspešnega shranjevanja uporabnikove vsebine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2499">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2500">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2500">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2501">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – označuje, ali ima ta dolgi vnos vso zahtevano telemetrijo dokumenta (polja »Data_Doc_\*«)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2501">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2502">Če je nima, zakaj?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2502">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2503">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – nezaznane izvirne izjeme med izvedbo dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2503">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2504">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** – čas, v katerem je bila dejavnost ločena/ni bila izvajana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2504">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2505">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** – način odpiranja tega dokumenta (samo za branje | branje in pisanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2505">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2506">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2506">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2507">\*\*Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long – \*\* označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2507">**Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the new cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2508">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** – način shranjevanja dokumenta v SharePointu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2508">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** - How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2509">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** – stanje zaščite podatkov podjetja za dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2509">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** - Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2510">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** – pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2510">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2511">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** – pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2511">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2512">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za obliko zapisa datoteke (bolj podrobno kot za pripono).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2512">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** - Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2513">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** – mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2513">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** - Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsavelegacy"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2592">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveLegacy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2592">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveLegacy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2593">Podatki so zbrani, kadar koli PowerPoint izvede postopek shranjevanja s potjo podedovane kode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2593">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the legacy code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2594">Dogodek vsebuje vrsto rezultata uspešne oz. neuspešne metrike učinkovitosti shranjevanja in pomembne metapodatke dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2594">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2595">Napake pri shranjevanju lahko privedejo do izgube podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2595">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2596">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanje funkcije in uspešnega shranjevanja uporabnikove vsebine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2596">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2597">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2597">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2598">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – označuje, ali ima ta dolgi vnos vso zahtevano telemetrijo dokumenta (polja »Data_Doc_\*«)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2598">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2599">Če je nima, zakaj?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2599">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2600">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – nezaznane izvirne izjeme med izvedbo dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2600">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2601">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** – čas, v katerem je bila dejavnost ločena/ni bila izvajana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2601">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2602">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** – način odpiranja dokumenta (samo za branje | branje in pisanje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2602">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2603">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2603">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2604">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long – \*\* Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2604">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2605">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType:long** – način shranjevanja dokumenta v SharePointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2605">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType:long** - How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2607">**Data_Doc_Ext:string** – pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2607">**Data_Doc_Ext:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2610">**Data_Doc_Fqdn:string** – mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2610">**Data_Doc_Fqdn:string** - Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2613">**Data_Doc_IdentityUniqueId:string** – enolični identifikator identitete, ki je bila uporabljena za dejanje dokumentov v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2613">**Data_Doc_IdentityUniqueId:string** - Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2741">**CountOtherErrors** – Skupno število drugih napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2741">**CountOtherErrors** - total number of other errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2742">**CountPPTErrors** – Skupno število napak PPT.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2742">**CountPPTErrors** - total number of PPT errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2743">**CountSlideShowErrors** – Skupno število napak diaprojekcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2743">**CountSlideShowErrors** - total number of slide show errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2744">**FirstOArtError** – Prva napaka v komponenti OArt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2744">**FirstOArtError** - first error happened in OArt</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2745">**FirstOtherError** – Prva napaka v drugih območjih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2745">**FirstOtherError** - first error happened in other area</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2746">**FirstPPTError** – Prva napaka v datoteki PPT.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2746">**FirstPPTError** - first error happened in PPT</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2747">**FirstSlideShowError** – Prva napaka v diaprojekciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2747">**FirstSlideShowError** - first error happened in slide show</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2802">Spremlja število uporabnikov, ki prejemajo sporočila storitev BizBar in Dynamic Canvas storitve TMS (TargetedMessagingService).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2802">Tracks the number of users receiving BizBar and Dynamic Canvas messages from TargetedMessagingService (TMS).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2803">Ti podatki so ključni za razumevanje vrste in območij sporočil, ki jih prejemajo uporabniki. Z njimi lahko zagotovimo, da uporabniki prejmejo vsa sporočila, nujna za nadaljnjo uporabo izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2803">This data is critical to understand what messages users are getting and on what surface so that we can ensure they are not missing any messages that may be critical to their continued use of the product.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2804">Te podatke potrebujemo tudi za natančno ocenjevanje naših poskusov in akcij v storitvi TMS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2804">Also needed to accurately measure the success of our experiments and campaigns run through TMS.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2807">**Data\_Flight** – Identifikator pilotne različice ECS/CT, uporabljene za pošiljanje tega sporočila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2807">**Data\_Flight** – ECS/CT Flight identifier that was used to deliver this message</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2808">**Data\_CampaignId** – Identifikator akcije, kateri pripada to sporočilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2808">**Data\_CampaignId** – identifier of the campaign that this message is part of</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2809">**Data\_MessageId** – Identifikator sporočila, ki ga je poslala ta storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2809">**Data\_MessageId** – identifier of this service delivered message</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2810">**Data\_TransactionId** – Identifikator transakcije s storitvijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2810">**Data\_TransactionId** – identifier of this transaction with the service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2811">**Data\_TriggerPoint** – Korak, v katerem je bil zabeležen ta dogodek (v prejete ali prikazanem sporočilu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2811">**Data\_TriggerPoint** – The step in which this event was logged (message received vs message displayed)</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedrefreshsmartdiagram"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2953">Office.Visio.Shared.RefreshSmartDiagram</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2953">Office.Visio.Shared.RefreshSmartDiagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2957">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** – ima vrednost true, če je bil osveženi diagram prvotno ustvarjen s povezovalnikom na osnovi zaporedja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2957">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true if the refreshed diagram was originally created using connector based on sequence" option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2958">**Data\_DialogError**:**string** – napaka med osveževanjem pametnega diagrama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2958">**Data\_DialogError**:**string** - error during refreshing smart diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2959">**Data\_FileError:string** – niz napake, če povezana Excelova datoteka ni veljavna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2959">**Data\_FileError:string** - error string when connected Excel file is invalid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2960">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** – ima vrednost true, če je uporabnik med osveževanjem izbral možnost za prepisovanje diagrama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2960">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** - true if user selected overwrite diagram option during refresh</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2961">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** – ima vrednost true, če je uporabnik med postopkom osveževanja podatkov prejel opozorilo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2961">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** - true if there was any warning shown to user during data refresh</span></span>
