<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2963">Zajame vrednosti napak pri pisanju nazaj v Excelu, če je datoteka ustvarjena z vmesnikom DV.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2963">Captures Excel write back failures when file is created through DV.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2964">Na ta način lažje odpravljamo napake in težave pri pisanju podatkov nazaj v Excel v diagramu DV.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2964">This helps us debug the failures and issues in writing back data to Excel in a DV diagram.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2965">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2965">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2966">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** – vrednost true pomeni, da so povezovalniki ustvarjeni glede na nastavitve zaporedja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2966">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true means connectors are created based on sequence settings</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2967">**Data\_DataSourceType:string** – to polje ponazarja, ali je bil diagram ustvarjen iz možnosti »Tabela« oz. »ObsegPoMeri«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2967">**Data\_DataSourceType:string** - This filed indicates whether diagram is created from  "Table" or "CustomRange"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2968">**Data\_DialogError:string** – vrsta napake po meri med ustvarjanjem pametnega diagrama v Excelu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2968">**Data\_DialogError:string** - Custom Error type while creating smart diagram through Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2969">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** – število oblik, ki so bile dodane med postopkom pisanja nazaj v Excelove funkcije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2969">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** - Number of shapes added during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2970">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** – število oblik, ki so bile izbrisane med postopkom pisanja nazaj v Excelove funkcije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2970">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** - Number of shapes deleted during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2971">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** – ima vrednost true, če je uporabnik izbral možnost prepisovanja podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2971">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** - true indicate user selected overwrite data option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2972">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da so bili izvorni podatki spremenjeni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2972">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** - true indicates source data is modified</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2973">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilo o posodobitvi podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2973">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** - true means data update warning shown to the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2974">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilo zaradi formule v Excelu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2974">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user because of presence of formula in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2975">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilo, saj v Excelu ni prisoten identifikator naslednjega koraka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2975">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** - true indicates warning show to the user because next step Identifier missing in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2976">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilo, naj Excelove podatke pretvori v obliko zapisa za tabele</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2976">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user to convert Excel data to table format</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfilenewcreatenewfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2977">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2977">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2978">Ta dogodek označuje, da je bil ustvarjen nov dokument v Office Wordu, in spremlja, ali je bil postopek uspešen oz. neuspešen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2978">This event indicates that a new document is created in Office Word and tracks success or failure of the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2979">S tem dogodkom spremljamo ustreznost ustvarjanja novega dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2979">The event is used to monitor that new document creation is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2980">Ta dogodek uporabljamo tudi za ocenjevanje števila mesečnih aktivnih uporabnikov/naprav in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2980">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2981">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2981">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2982">**Data\_DirtyState** – Ali je bil dokument ustvarjen v nečistem stanju (s spremembami, ki jih je treba shraniti).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2982">**Data\_DirtyState** - whether the document was created in a dirty state (with changes that need to be saved)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2983">**Data\_ErrorID** – Identifikator napake v primeru napake postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2983">**Data\_ErrorID** - error identifier in case of operation failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2984">**Data\_MainPdod** – Identifikator dokumenta med sejo tega postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2984">**Data\_MainPdod** - The document identifier during this process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2985">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** – Označuje, ali je bil dokument ustvarjen s predlogo po meri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2985">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** - indicates whether the document was created from a custom template</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenuserinitiatedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2986">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2986">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2987">V tem dogodku je navedeno, da je Office Word odprl dokument z zagonom uporabnika namesto na programski način Office Word. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2987">This event indicates Office Word opens a document by user initiation instead of by Office Word programmatically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2988">Poleg tega vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2988">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2989">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija za odpiranje datoteke deluje pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2989">The event monitors whether file-open is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2990">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2990">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2991">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2991">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2992">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2992">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2993">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2993">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2994">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega je morda mogoče odpreti datoteko, če ga pridobimo, preden uporabnik začne urejati dokument oz. se ga morda odloči shraniti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2994">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2995">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega morda lahko odpremo datoteko, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2995">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2996">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2996">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2997">**Data_BytesUnknown** – število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2997">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2998">**Data.Doc.AccessMode** – dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2998">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-2999">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-2999">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3000">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enote, uporabljene za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3000">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3001">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3001">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3002">**Data_Doc_Ext** – pripona dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3002">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3003">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – različica protokola za obliko zapisa datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3003">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3004">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – ime domene za OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3004">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3005">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost imena domene, ki omogoča identifikacijo stranke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3005">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3006">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost identitete uporabnika, uporabljena za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3006">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3007">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – zabeleži način odpiranja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3007">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3008">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – poroča o predpomnjenih zastavicah, uporabljenih za nastavitev možnosti zahtev za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3008">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3009">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – dejanja, ki jih je dovolil pravilnik za elektronsko zaščito podatkov, ki velja za dokument/uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3009">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3010">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – zastavica, ki označuje postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3010">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3011">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – zastavica, ki označuje, da je storitev sodelovanja podprta v dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3011">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3012">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – zastavica, ki označuje, da je bila odprta kopija dokumenta brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3012">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3013">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – zastavica, ki označuje, da v računalniku obstaja samodejno sinhronizirana kopija dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3013">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3014">**Data_Doc_Location** – označuje, v kateri storitvi je dokument na voljo (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3014">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3015">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – označuje, v kateri znani mapi je na voljo lokalno shranjen dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3015">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3016">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – število souporabnikov v seji urejanja s sodelovanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3016">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3017">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – označuje nastavljene zastavice za branje ali branje/pisanje gesla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3017">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3018">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – razlogi, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu »samo za branje«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3018">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3019">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – anonimni identifikator dokumenta za diagnosticiranje težav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3019">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3020">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – nespremenljivi anonimni identifikator dokumenta za diagnosticiranje težav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3020">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3021">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – različica protokola za komunikacijo s storitvijo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3021">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3022">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – vrsta strežnika, ki zagotavlja storitev (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3022">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - the type of the server offering the service (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3023">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – različica strežnika, ki zagotavlja storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3023">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - the server version offering the service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3024">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – različica strežnika, ki zagotavlja storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3024">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - the server version offering the service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3025">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – diagnostične informacije zahtev storitve SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3025">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3026">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – indikator velikosti dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3026">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - Indicator of document size</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3027">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – indikator posebnih znakov v URL-ju ali poti dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3027">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3028">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** – indikator, ali je tok dokumenta na voljo/onemogočen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3028">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** - Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3029">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** – indikator vrste dokumenta (lokalno ali storitev).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3029">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** - Indicator as to the type of document (local or service based)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3030">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost za ustvarjanje naivnega identifikatorja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3030">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3031">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – vsebuje enolični identifikator za ponudnika storitve WOPI.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3031">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - Contains unique identifier of WOPI service provider</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3032">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** – identifikator prvega urejevalnika, ki je onemogočil preimenovanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3032">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** - Identifier of the first editor that caused for rename to be disabled</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3033">**Data_EditorsCount** – število urednikov v dokumentov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3033">**Data_EditorsCount** - Number of editors in the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3034">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** – vrednost celega števila, ki predstavlja vzrok za vsiljeni način za branje/pisanje pri datoteki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3034">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** - Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3035">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** – označuje, da je bilo odpiranje uspešno po odpravi napake med odpiranjem dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3035">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** - Indicates that open succeeded after repairing a failure while opening the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3036">**Data_LastLoggedTag** – enolična oznaka za mesto klica kode, ki se uporablja za prepoznavanje, ko poskušamo izvesti neuspešno odpiranje dvakrat zapored (uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3036">**Data_LastLoggedTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3037">**Data_LinkStyles** – označuje, ali povezujemo sloge predlog.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3037">**Data_LinkStyles** - Indicates whether we are linking to the template styles</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactcmdgosubsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3053">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3053">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3054">Ta dogodek označuje, da uporabnik shranjuje spremembe v nov dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3054">This event indicates that a user is saving their changes to a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3055">Dogodek nadzira ustreznost delovanja shranjevanja v nov dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3055">The event monitors whether saving to a new document is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3056">Ta dogodek uporabljamo tudi za ocenjevanje števila mesečnih aktivnih uporabnikov/naprav in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3056">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3060">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko časa je bila dejavnost ločena od niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3060">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3067">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – različica protokola za obliko zapisa datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3067">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3068">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – ime domene za OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3068">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3077">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – zastavica, ki označuje, da v računalniku obstaja samodejno sinhronizirana kopija dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3077">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3078">**Data_Doc_Location** – označuje, v kateri storitvi je dokument na voljo (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3078">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3081">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – označuje nastavljene zastavice za branje ali branje/pisanje gesla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3081">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3082">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – razlogi, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu »samo za branje«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3082">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactfconfirmsavedoccorequerysave"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3103">Office.Word.FileSave.ActFConfirmSaveDocCoreQuerySave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3103">Office.Word.FileSave.ActFConfirmSaveDocCoreQuerySave</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3104">Ta dogodek označuje, da Office Word pozove uporabnika k shranjevanju sprememb, ko ta poskuša zapreti dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3104">This event indicates Office Word prompts the user to save changes when it tries to close the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3105">Z njim Microsoft nadzira ustreznost delovanja funkcije shranjevanja dokumenta ob zapiranju ter tako prepreči morebitno izgubo podatkov v dokumentih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3105">It allows Microsoft to monitor whether save-at-quit works as expected to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3106">Dogodek nadzira, ali način shranjevanja ob zapiranju ustrezno deluje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3106">The event monitors whether save-at-quit is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3107">Ta dogodek uporabljamo tudi za ocenjevanje števila mesečnih aktivnih uporabnikov/naprav in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3107">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3108">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3108">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3166">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word shranjuje dokument v nov dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3166">This event indicates Office Word saves a document into a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3167">Microsoftu omogoča, da pri funkciji »Shrani kot« zazna napake, ki so pomembne za preprečevanje izgube podatkov v dokumentih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3167">It allows Microsoft to detect errors in save-as which is important to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3168">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Shrani kot« deluje običajno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3168">The event monitors whether save-as is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3169">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3169">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3177">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko časa je bila dejavnost ločena od niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3177">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3178">**Data.Doc.AccessMode** – dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3178">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3179">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3179">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordworddocumentdirtyflagchanged"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3290">Office.Word.Word.DocumentDirtyFlagChanged</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3290">Office.Word.Word.DocumentDirtyFlagChanged</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3291">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word ureja dokument, zaradi česar se je spremenilo notranje stanje dokumenta v »spremenjeno«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3291">This event indicates Office Word edits a document which changes the document internal state into "dirty".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3292">Microsoftu omogoča, da ovrednoti stanje funkcij urejenega dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3292">It allows Microsoft to evaluate the feature health of edit-document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3293">Dogodek predstavlja interval obveščanja o urejanjih uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3293">The event is a heartbeat of user edits.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3294">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3294">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3295">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3295">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3296">**Data\_CollectionTime –** časovni žig dogodka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3296">**Data\_CollectionTime-** Timestamp of the event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3297">**Data\_DocumentLocation –** vrsta za mesto dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3297">**Data\_DocumentLocation-** type of the document location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3298">**Data\_DocumentLocationDetails –** podvrsta za mesto dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3298">**Data\_DocumentLocationDetails-** Sub-type of the document location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3299">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled –** ponazarja, ali je omogočena funkcija »Vedno shrani«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3299">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled-** Indicates whether always-save was enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3300">**Data\_FirstEditTime –** časovni žig prvega urejanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3300">**Data\_FirstEditTime-** Timestamp of first edit</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3301">**Data\_NumberCoAuthors –** število soavtorjev, ki med sejo urejajo dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3301">**Data\_NumberCoAuthors-** Number of coauthors editing the document during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3302">**Data\_NumberOfTimesDocumentDirtied –** število urejanj dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3302">**Data\_NumberOfTimesDocumentDirtied-** Number of edits made to the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3303">**Data\_Pdod –** identifikator dokumenta v postopku programa Microsoft Office Word</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3303">**Data\_Pdod-** Document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3304">**Data\_UrlHash –** razpršitev poti dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3304">**Data\_UrlHash-** Hash of the document path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3305">**Data\_ViewKind –** vrsta Wordovega pogleda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3305">**Data\_ViewKind-** Type of Word view</span></span>

#### <a name="parselicenseop"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3318">ParseLicenseOp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3318">ParseLicenseOp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3319">Zbira, ko uporabnik poskuša odpreti dokument, zaščiten z upravljanjem pravic do informacij ali uporabiti zaščito za upravljanje pravic do informacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3319">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3320">Vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav, do katerih pride, ko se izvede operacija razčlenjevanja dovoljenj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3320">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when parsing licenses operation is performed.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3321">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3321">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3322">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hierarhija odjemalcev, ki označuje, da se program izvaja v produkcijskem okolju ali v okolju razvijalcev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3322">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3323">**AppInfo.Name** – ime aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3323">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3324">**AppInfo.Version** – različica aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3324">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3325">**iKey** – ID strežnika Logger </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3325">**iKey** - Logger server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3326">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** – ID scenarija, ki ga je posredovala aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3326">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3327">**RMS.Duration** – Skupen čas za izvedbo operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3327">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for the operation to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3328">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** – skupni čas minus zunanje operacije, kot je zakasnitev omrežja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3328">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3329">**RMS.ErrorCode** – koda napake je vrnjena, če izvira iz operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3329">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3330">**RMS.HttpCall** – označite, ali je prišlo do operacije HTTP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3330">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is HTTP operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3331">**RMS.LicenseFormat** – oblika licence: Xrml ali Json</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3331">**RMS.LicenseFormat** - The license Format: Xrml or Json</span></span>

#### <a name="ipccreateoauth2token"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3431">IpcCreateOauth2Token</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3431">IpcCreateOauth2Token</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3432">Zbira, ko uporabnik poskuša odpreti dokument, zaščiten z upravljanjem pravic do informacij ali uporabiti zaščito za upravljanje pravic do informacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3432">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3433">Vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav, do katerih pride, ko se izvede priklic API IpcCreateOauth2Token API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3433">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when the IpcCreateOauth2Token API call is made.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3434">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3434">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3435">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hierarhija odjemalcev, ki označuje, da se program izvaja v produkcijskem okolju ali v okolju razvijalcev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3435">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3436">**AppInfo.Name** – ime aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3436">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3437">**AppInfo.Version** – različica aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3437">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3438">**iKey** – ID strežnika za storitev pisanja dnevnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3438">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3439">**RMS.Duration** – Skupen čas za izvedbo API priklica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3439">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for API call to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3440">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** – skupni čas minus zunanje operacije, kot je zakasnitev omrežja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3440">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3441">**RMS.ErrorCode** – koda napake je vrnjena, če katera koli izvira iz priklica API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3441">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the API call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3442">**RMS.HttpCall** – označite, ali je prišlo do operacije HTTP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3442">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is HTTP operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3443">**RMS.Rezultat** – uspeh ali neuspeh priklica API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3443">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the API call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3444">**RMS.ScenarioId** – ID scenarija, ki ga določa API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3444">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3445">**RMS.SDKVersion** – različica odjemalca storitve za upravljanje pravic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3445">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3446">**RMS.StatusCode** – Koda stanja vrnjenega rezultata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3446">**RMS.StatusCode** - Status code of the returned result</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidoffice16bootlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3447">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3447">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3448">Ključnega pomena za zajem meritev učinkovitosti delovanja aplikacije glede na odzivni čas aplikacije od zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3448">Critical to capture for app performance metric with respect to the response time of the app from the boot.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3449">Microsoft s tem dogodkom zbira čas, zahtevan za odzivnost aplikacije, in za zaznavanje scenarijev, ki lahko vplivajo na čas zagona v aplikacijah WXP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3449">Microsoft uses this to collect the time taken for the app to be responsive and also detect scenarios that may impact boot time in WXP apps.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3450">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3450">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3451">**AppLaunchResponsiveTimeInMilliSec** – Čas odzivnosti pri zagonu aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3451">**AppLaunchResponsiveTimeInMilliSec** - App launch responsive time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3452">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila aplikacija prekinjena med zagonom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3452">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3453">**CollectionTime** – Čas dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3453">**CollectionTime** - Timestamp of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3454">**FileActivationAttempted** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je prišlo do poskusa aktivacije datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3454">**FileActivationAttempted** - Boolean to indicate if file activation as attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3455">**FirstIdleOnAppThreadTimeInMilliSec** – Čas nedejavnosti za nit aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3455">**FirstIdleOnAppThreadTimeInMilliSec** - App thread idle time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3456">**IsThisFirstLaunch** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je to zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3456">**IsThisFirstLaunch** - Boolean to indicate if this is first time app launch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3457">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je med zagonom prišlo do blokiranja uporabniškega vmesnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3457">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if there was a blocking UI during boot</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilityofficejsappactivated"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3458">Office.Extensibility.OfficeJS.Appactivated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3458">Office.Extensibility.OfficeJS.Appactivated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3459">Zapiše informacije o nepričakovanih zaustavitvah v Officeu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3459">Records information about unexpected shutdowns of Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3460">Tako lahko prepoznamo zrušitve ali neodzivanja izdelka in ustrezno ukrepamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3460">This allows us to identify crashes or hangs in the product so that they can be addressed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3462">**Data\_AirspaceInitTime:integer –** Čas, zahtevan za inicializacijo Officeove komponente Airspace.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3462">**Data\_AirspaceInitTime:integer-** time taken to initialize Airspace office component</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3464">**Data\_APIInitTime:integer –** čas, zahtevan za inicializacijo modula Visio API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3464">**Data\_APIInitTime:integer -** time taken to initialize Visio API module</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3465">**Data\_AppSizeHeight –** višina okna za dodatek**-**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3465">**Data\_AppSizeHeight –** Add**-** in window size’s height</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3466">**Data\_AppSizeWidth –** širina okna za dodatek**-**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3466">**Data\_AppSizeWidth –** Add**-** in window size’s width</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3467">**Data\_AppURL –** URL prijave; zapiše polni URL za dodatke iz trgovine in domeno URL-ja za dogodke, ki jih niste pridobili iz trgovine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3467">**Data\_AppURL -** URL of the Add in; Logs full URL for Store Add ins and URL domain for non-store Add ins</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3468">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long – \*\* Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3468">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3469">**Data\_AuthorsCount:integer –** število avtorjev, ki so uredili dokument v tej seji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3469">**Data\_AuthorsCount:integer -** number of authors who edited the document in this session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3470">**Data\_BackgroundPages:integer –** število strani v ozadju diagrama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3470">**Data\_BackgroundPages:integer -** number of background pages in diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3471">**Data\_BootTime:integer –** čas, zahtevan za zagon Visia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3471">**Data\_BootTime:integer -** The amount of time it took to boot Visio</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3472">**Data\_Browser –** niz brskalnika, ki vsebuje informacije o vrsti in različici brskalnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3472">**Data\_Browser -** Browser string with information about the browser such as type, version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3473">**Data\_ChildWindowMixedModeTime:integer –** čas, zahtevan za omogočanje mešanega načina v Visiu (podrejeno okno ima lahko različno vrednost DpiAwareness kot nadrejeno okno)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3473">**Data\_ChildWindowMixedModeTime:integer -** time taken to enable mixed mode in Visio (Child window can have different DpiAwareness from parent window)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3474">**Data\_CommentsCount:integer –** število komentarjev v dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3474">**Data\_CommentsCount:integer -** number of comments in document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3475">**Data\_ConnectionCount:integer –** število podatkovnih povezav v diagramu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3475">**Data\_ConnectionCount:integer -** number of data connection in diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3476">**Data\_ContentMgrInitTim:integer –** čas, zahtevan za inicializacijo upravitelja vsebine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3476">**Data\_ContentMgrInitTim:integer -** time taken to initialize content manager</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3477">**Data\_CreateMainFrameTime:integer –** čas, zahtevan za ustvarjanje glavnega okvirja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3477">**Data\_CreateMainFrameTime:integer -** Create mainframe time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3478">**Data\_CreatePaletteTime:integer –** čas, zahtevan za ustvarjanje globalne palete z barvami</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3478">**Data\_CreatePaletteTime:integer -** Time taken to create the global color palette</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3479">**Data\_DispFormatCount:integer –** število podatkovnih grafik v diagramu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3479">**Data\_DispFormatCount:integer -** number of data graphics in diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3480">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string –** pripona dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3480">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3481">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string –** mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3481">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3482">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string –** razpršitev mesta shrambe dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3482">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3483">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool-**: ali je bil dokument odprt postopoma (nova funkcija, ki dokument odpre, brez da prenese celoten dokument)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3483">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool-** : Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3484">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool –** ali je bil dokument odprt iz lokalnega predpomnilnika?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3484">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** Is document being opened from local cache?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3485">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool –** ima vrednost true, če gre za dokument strežnika, ki je na voljo lokalno in je sinhroniziran s strežnikom (npr. prek storitve OneDrive ali odjemalskih aplikacij ODB)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3485">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool-** true when this is a server document that exists locally, and is synchronized with the server (e.g. through OneDrive or ODB client apps)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3486">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long-**: nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za mesto shranjevanja dokumenta (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, omrežje itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3486">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long-** : Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3487">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long –** nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti podrobnejše lokacije (mapa »Začasno«, mapa »Prenosi«, dokumenti storitve One Drive, slike storitve One Drive)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3487">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3488">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string –** razpršitev identifikatorja vira za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3488">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string -** Hash of resource Identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3489">\*\*Data_Doc_RtcType – \*\*  označuje, kako je bil kanal v realnem času (RTC) nastavljen za trenutno datoteko (onemogočeno, nepodprto, na zahtevo, vedno vklopljeno itn.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3489">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3490">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string –** nespremenljivi identifikator za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3490">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string -** immutable identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3491">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long –** ustvarjeni GUID, ki prepozna primerek dokumenta v seji istega procesa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3491">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3492">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long –** velikost dokumenta v bajtih</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3492">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3493">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long –** dolga bitna maska, ki ponazarja posebne znake v URL-ju ali poti dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3493">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long -** long Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationhanging"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3618">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3618">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3619">Zbira podatke, ko zagon Officeovega dodatka traja nepričakovano dolgo (> 5 s).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3619">Collects when an Office add-in takes unexpectedly long to launch (>5 sec).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3620">Uporablja se za zaznavanje in odpravljanje težav pri zagonih Officeovih dodatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3620">Used to detect and fix problems with Office add-ins launching.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3621">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3621">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3622">**AppId** – ID aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3622">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3623">**AppInfo** – podatki glede vrste dodatka (podokno opravil ali UILess ali znotraj vsebine itd.) in vrste ponudnika (Omen, SharePoint, datotečni sistem itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3623">**AppInfo** - data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3624">**AppInstanceId** – ID primerka aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3624">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3625">**AssetId** – ID sredstva aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3625">**AssetId** - asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3626">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** – števec aktiviranih dodatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3626">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3627">**RemoterType** – določa vrsto remoterja (zaupanja vreden, ni vreden zaupanja, Win32webView, zaupanja vreden UDF itd.), ki se uporablja za aktiviranje dodatka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3627">**RemoterType** - specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3628">**StoreType** – izvor aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3628">**StoreType** - origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3629">**TimeForAuth** – čas, porabljen za preverjanje pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3629">**TimeForAuth** - time spent on auth</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3630">**TimeForSandbox** – čas, porabljen za peskovnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3630">**TimeForSandbox** - time spent on the sandbox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3631">**TimeForServerCall** – čas, porabljen za klic strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3631">**TimeForServerCall** - time spent on the server call</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3632">**TotalTime** – skupni porabljeni čas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3632">**TotalTime** - total time spent</span></span>

#### <a name="onenoteappappbootcomplete"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3633">OneNote.App.AppBootComplete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3633">OneNote.App.AppBootComplete</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3634">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja, da lahko novi uporabniki (Microsoftov račun) prvič uspešno zaženejo in začnejo uporabljati OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3634">The critical signal used to ensure new consumer users (Microsoft Account) can successfully launch and use OneNote for the first time.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3635">Uporablja se za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3635">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3636">Če uporabniki prvič ne morejo zagnati aplikacije, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3636">If users can’t launch the app for the first time, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3637">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3637">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3638">**ACTIVITY_BOOT_TIME_IN_MS** – Čas, zahtevan, za ustvarjanje dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3638">**ACTIVITY_BOOT_TIME_IN_MS** - Time taken to complete Activity creation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3639">**ACTIVITY_NAME** – Ime dejavnosti, odprte pri zagonu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3639">**ACTIVITY_NAME** - Name of the Activity opened when booted</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3640">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** – Označuje, ali se med zagonom prikaže pogovorno okno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3640">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** - Indicates if any dialog is shown during boot time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3641">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** – Označuje, ali je bil zagon vnaprej izpraznjen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3641">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** - Indicates if the boot was pre-empted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3642">**APP_THREAD_CREATION_WAIT_TIME_TIME_FOR_APP_THREAD_CREATION** – Čas, zahtevan za ustvarjanje niti aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3642">**APP_THREAD_CREATION_WAIT_TIME_TIME_FOR_APP_THREAD_CREATION** - Time taken to create Application threads</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3706">Zbere podatke o načinu aktiviranja Outlooka, na primer z naročnino ali s količinskim licenciranjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3706">Collects how Outlook is activated, such as with a subscription or volume license.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3707">Podatke spremljamo, da zagotovimo, da ne pride do morebitnih konic napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3707">The data is monitored to ensure we don’t see any spikes in failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3708">Z analiziranjem teh podatkov odkrijemo tudi področja, ki jih moramo izboljšati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3708">We also analyze the data to find areas of improvement.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3712">Ta dogodek je zbran vsakokrat, ko PowerPoint odpre datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3712">Collected whenever PowerPoint opens a file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3713">Vsebuje informacije o uspehu, podrobnosti o napaki, metriko učinkovitosti delovanja in osnovne podrobnosti o datoteki, vključno z vrsto oblike zapisa datoteke ter metapodatki dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3713">Contains success information, failure details, performance metrics, and basic details about the file including file format type and document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3714">Te informacije so zahtevane, da PowerPoint lahko uspešno odpira datoteke in pri tem ne izgublja na učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3714">This information is necessary to ensure PowerPoint can open files successfully with no degradation in performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3715">Z njimi lahko diagnosticiramo težave, ki jih odkrijemo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3715">It allows us to diagnose any problems we discover.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3716">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3716">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3893">**Automation –** iz avtomatiziranega načina</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3893">**Automation -** from automation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3900">**IsOpen –** je odprt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3900">**IsOpen -** is open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3903">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** – v ukazni vrstici je preveč presledkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3903">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** – there is non-standard space in command line</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3956">**Data\_Outcome –** skupni čas, zahtevan za zagon in odpiranje datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3956">**Data\_Outcome -** Total boot and file open time.</span></span>

#### <a name="officesessionidproviderofficeprocesssessionstart"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3958">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3958">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3959">Velja za vse vrste Officeovih aplikacij v okolju sistema Windows: win32 and UWP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3959">Applicable to all the Office windows-based applications: win32 and UWP</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3960">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3960">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3961">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** pošlje osnovne informacije ob zagonu nove Officeove seje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3961">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** sends basic information upon the start of a new Office session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3962">Ta dogodek se uporablja za štetje števila enoličnih sej, zaznanih v dani napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3962">This is used to count the number of unique sessions seen on a given device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3963">Ta dogodek se uporablja kot signal obveščanja o izvajanju aplikacije, s katerim se zagotovi, ali se aplikacija izvaja v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3963">This is used as a heartbeat event to ensure that the application is running on a device or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3964">Poleg tega se uporablja tudi kot kritičen signal za splošno zanesljivost aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3964">In addition, it serves as a critical signal for overall application reliability</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3965">**AppSessionGuid** – identifikator določene seje aplikacije, ki se je začela z ustvarjanjem procesa in traja vse do konca procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3965">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3966">Dogodek je oblikovan kot standardni 128-bitni GUID, sestavljen iz 4 delov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3966">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3967">Ti štirje deli v vrstnem redu so (1) 32-bitni ID procesa (2) 16-bitni ID seje (3) 16-bitni ID zagona (4) čas ustvarjanja 64-bitnega procesa v UTC 100ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3967">Those four parts in order are (1) 32 bit Process ID (2) 16 bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64 bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3968">**processSessionId** – naključno ustvarjeni GUID za prepoznavanje seje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3968">**processSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3969">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** – logična vrednost konstante.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3969">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Constant boolean value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3970">Vedno ima vrednost true.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3970">Always true.</span></span>

#### <a name="officesystemsessionhandoff"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3971">Office.System.SessionHandoff</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3971">Office.System.SessionHandoff</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3972">Označuje, da gre pri trenutni Officeovi seji za sejo prenosa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3972">Indicates that the current Office session is a handoff session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3973">To pomeni, da je obravnava uporabnikove zahteve za odpiranje dokumenta prenesena na primerek iste aplikacije, ki se že izvaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3973">This means that handling of a user’s request to open a document is being handed off to an already running instance of the same application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3975">**ParentSessionId** – ID seje, ki bo prevzela obravnavo uporabnikove zahteve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3975">**ParentSessionId** - The ID of the session that will be taking over handling of the users’ request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3981">**appVersionBuild** – številka različice za gradnjo aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3981">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3985">**SessionId** – naključno ustvarjeni GUID za prepoznavanje seje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3985">**SessionID** - Randomly generated GUID to identify the app session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3990">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3990">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-3995">**childSessionId** – naključno ustvarjeni GUID za prepoznavanje seje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-3995">**childSessionID** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4001">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4001">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4002">**Data_AppBootTime** – trajanja zagona aplikacije v milisekundah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4002">**Data_AppBootTime** - Duration taken for app to boot, in milliseconds.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopencmdfilemrupriv"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4008">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4008">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4009">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da je Microsoft Office Word odprl dokument s seznama nedavno uporabljenih elementov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4009">This event indicates Office Word opens a document from the Most Recent Used (MRU) list.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4010">Poleg tega vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4010">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4011">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Odpri datoteko s seznama nazadnje uporabljenih datotek« deluje v skladu s pričakovanji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4011">The event monitors whether fileopen-from-MRU is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4012">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4012">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4013">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4013">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4014">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4014">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4015">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4015">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4016">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega je morda mogoče odpreti datoteko, če ga pridobimo, preden uporabnik začne urejati dokument oz. se ga morda odloči shraniti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4016">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4017">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega morda lahko odpremo datoteko, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4017">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4018">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4018">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4019">**Data_BytesUnknown** – število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4019">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4020">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko časa je bila dejavnost ločena od niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4020">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenffileopenxstzcore"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4075">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4075">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4076">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word odpira dokument, ki ga je uporabnik dvokliknil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4076">This event indicates Office Word opens a document who is double clicked by a user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4077">Poleg tega vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4077">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4078">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Odpri datoteko z dvoklikom« deluje v skladu s pričakovanji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4078">The event monitors whether file-openfrom-file-double-click is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4079">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4079">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4080">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4080">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4081">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4081">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4082">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4082">Used for data quality diagnostics</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4083">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega je morda mogoče odpreti datoteko, če ga pridobimo, preden uporabnik začne urejati dokument oz. se ga morda odloči shraniti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4083">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4084">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega morda lahko odpremo datoteko, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4084">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4085">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4085">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4086">**Data_BytesUnknown** – število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4086">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4087">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko časa je bila dejavnost ločena od niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4087">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4088">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4088">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4089">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4089">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4090">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind – \*\* Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4090">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4091">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enote, uporabljene za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4091">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4092">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4092">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>
