#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenifrinitargs"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4142">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4142">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4143">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word odpira dokument s pomočjo aktivacije modula COM ali ukazne vrstice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4143">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via COM activation or command line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4144">Prav tako vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4144">It also contains critical file open performance data, and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4145">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Odpri datoteko iz ukazne vrstice« deluje običajno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4145">The event monitors whether file-open-from-command-line is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4146">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4146">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4147">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4147">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4148">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes** – Poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4148">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes -** Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4149">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4149">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4150">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous –** število bajtov (stisnjenih), za katerega menimo, da lahko odpremo datoteko brez tega števila, če jih pridobimo, preden uporabnik želi začeti urejati dokument oz. ga morda shraniti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4150">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4151">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork –** število bajtov (stisnjenih), pri katerem morda še lahko odpremo datoteko brez tega števila, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4151">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4152">**Data\_BytesSynchronous –** število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4152">**Data\_BytesSynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4153">**Data\_BytesUnknown –** število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4153">**Data\_BytesUnknown -** Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4154">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode –** dokument je samo za branje ali omogoča urejanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4154">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4155">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4155">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4156">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind – \*\* Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4156">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4157">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType** – Enote, ki se uporabljajo za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4157">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4158">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState –** nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4158">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4159">**Data\_Doc\_Ext –** pripona dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4159">**Data\_Doc\_Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4160">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat –** različica protokola za obliko zapisa dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4160">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4161">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn** – Ime domene za OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4161">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4162">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash** – Enostranska zgoščena vrednost imena domene, ki omogoča identifikacijo stranke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4162">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash -** One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4163">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags –** poroča predpomnjenje zastavice za nastavitev možnosti odprtih zahtev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4163">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags -** Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4164">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId –** enosmerna razpršitev identitete uporabnika, ki je bila uporabljena za odpiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4164">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId -** A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenloadfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4208">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4208">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4209">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word odpira dokument s pomočjo pogovornega okna za odpiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4209">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via Open dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4210">Poleg tega vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4210">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4211">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Odpri datoteko v pogovornem oknu za odpiranje datotek« deluje v skladu s pričakovanji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4211">The event monitors whether file-open-from-the-open-filedialog is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4212">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4212">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4213">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4213">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4214">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4214">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4215">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4215">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4216">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega je morda mogoče odpreti datoteko, če ga pridobimo, preden uporabnik začne urejati dokument oz. se ga morda odloči shraniti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4216">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4217">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega morda lahko odpremo datoteko, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4217">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4218">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4218">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4219">**Data_BytesUnknown** – število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4219">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4220">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko časa je bila dejavnost ločena od niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4220">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4221">**Data.Doc.AccessMode** – dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4221">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4222">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4222">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4223">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind – \*\* Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4223">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4224">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enote, uporabljene za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4224">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4225">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4225">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4226">**Data_Doc_Ext** – pripona dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4226">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4227">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – različica protokola za obliko zapisa datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4227">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4228">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – ime domene za OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4228">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4229">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost imena domene, ki omogoča identifikacijo stranke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4229">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4230">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost identitete uporabnika, uporabljena za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4230">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4231">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – zabeleži način odpiranja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4231">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4232">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – poroča o predpomnjenih zastavicah, uporabljenih za nastavitev možnosti zahtev za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4232">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4233">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – dejanja, ki jih je dovolil pravilnik za elektronsko zaščito podatkov, ki velja za dokument/uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4233">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4234">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – zastavica, ki označuje postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4234">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4235">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – zastavica, ki označuje, da je storitev sodelovanja podprta v dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4235">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4236">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – zastavica, ki označuje, da je bila odprta kopija dokumenta brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4236">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

#### <a name="officeaccessibilityaccessibilitytoolsessionpresencewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4316">Office.Accessibility.AccessibilityToolSessionPresenceWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4316">Office.Accessibility.AccessibilityToolSessionPresenceWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4317">Omogoča nam, da odkrijemo uporabnikovo orodje za pomoč uporabnikom s posebnimi potrebami in njegovo ime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4317">Allows us to detect that the user has an Assistive technology tool and its name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4318">S pomočjo tega dogodka vidimo, ali ima Officeov uporabnik težave z določenim orodjem za pomoč uporabnikov s posebnimi potrebami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4318">This allows us to understand if an Office user is experiencing issues with a specific Assistive Technology tool.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4319">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4319">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4320">**Data\_Data\_Jaws –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljal bralnik Jaws**Data\_Data\_Magic –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljalo orodje Magic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4320">**Data\_Data\_Jaws -** indicates if Jaws was running during the session**Data\_Data\_Magic -** indicates if Magic was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4321">**Data\_Data\_Magnify –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje povečave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4321">**Data\_Data\_Magnify -** indicates if Magnify was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4322">**Data\_Data\_Narrator –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljal pripovedovalec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4322">**Data\_Data\_Narrator -** indicates if Narrator was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4323">**Data\_Data\_NVDA –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje NVDA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4323">**Data\_Data\_NVDA -** indicates if NVDA was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4324">**Data\_Data\_SA –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje SA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4324">**Data\_Data\_SA -** indicates if SA was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4325">**Data\_Data\_Supernova –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje Supernova</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4325">**Data\_Data\_Supernova -** indicates if Supernova was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4326">**Data\_Data\_SuperNovaessSuite –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje SuperNovaAccessSuite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4326">**Data\_Data\_SuperNovaessSuite -** indicates if SuperNovaAccessSuite was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4327">**Data\_Data\_WinEyes –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje WinEyes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4327">**Data\_Data\_WinEyes -** indicates if WinEyes was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4328">**Data\_Data\_ZoomText –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje ZoomText</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4328">**Data\_Data\_ZoomText -** indicates if ZoomText was running during the session</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_darkmode"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4329">Office_Apple_DarkMode</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4329">Office_Apple_DarkMode</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4330">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4330">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4331">Dogodek nam pove, ali je uporabnik zagnal sistem v načinu DarkMode in ali je uporabnik prepisal nastavitev sistema DarkMode v Officeu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4331">The event tells us if user is running a System on DarkMode and whether the user overwrote the DarkMode System setting in Office.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4332">Ta dogodek nam pomaga zagotoviti dostopnost in prednostno obravnavo optimizacije uporabniške izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4332">We use this event to help ensure accessibility and prioritize user-experience optimization.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4333">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4333">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4334">**Data_DarkModeIsEnabled** – označuje, ali je v sistemu omogočen način DarkMode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4334">**Data_DarkModeIsEnabled** - Whether DarkMode is enabled in the system.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4335">**Data_RequiresAquaSystemAppearanceEnabled** – označuje, ali je v Officeu prepisan način DarkMode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4335">**Data_RequiresAquaSystemAppearanceEnabled** - Whether DarkMode is overwritten in Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4337">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4337">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4338">Dogodek nam pove, da ima uporabnik na svojo prenosno napravo priključeno tipkovnico.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4338">The event tells us that a user is attaching a keyboard to their mobile device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4339">Dogodek nam pomaga pri izboljšanju dostopnosti in optimizaciji uporabniške izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4339">The event helps us improve accessibility and optimize our user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4340">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4340">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4341">**Data_CollectionTime** – časovni žig, ki označuje čas zbiranja dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4341">**Data_CollectionTime** - A timestamp denoting the event collection time.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordaccessibilitylearningtoolsreadaloudplayreadaloud"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4369">Office.Word.Accessibility.LearningTools.ReadAloud.PlayReadAloud</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4369">Office.Word.Accessibility.LearningTools.ReadAloud.PlayReadAloud</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4370">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word naglas bere besedilo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4370">This event indicates Office Word reads aloud the text in the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4371">Dogodek predstavlja signal obveščanja o izvajanju funkcije dostopnosti, ki Microsoftu omogoča, da ovrednoti stanje storitve branja besedila naglas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4371">The event is a heartbeat of the accessibility feature which allows Microsoft to evaluate the feature health of read-aloud-text.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4372">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4372">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4373">**Data\_CharacterCount –** število znakov v dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4373">**Data\_CharacterCount -** character count of the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4374">**Data\_CharactersWithSpaceCount –** število znakov s presledki v dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4374">**Data\_CharactersWithSpaceCount -** character and space count of the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4375">**Data\_IsPageCountInProgress –** ali se izvaja štetje strani</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4375">**Data\_IsPageCountInProgress -** is the page count in progress</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4376">**Data\_LineCount –** število vrstic v dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4376">**Data\_LineCount -** line count of the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4377">**Data\_PageCount –** število strani v dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4377">**Data\_PageCount -** page count of the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4378">**Data\_ParagraphCount –** število odstavkov v dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4378">**Data\_ParagraphCount -** paragraph count of the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4379">**Data\_Play –** ali Word prvič bere dokument naglas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4379">**Data\_Play -** Is this the first time for Word to read aloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4380">**Data\_ViewKind –** vrsta pogleda v dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4380">**Data\_ViewKind -** view type of the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4381">**Data\_WordCount –** število besed v dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4381">**Data\_WordCount -** word count of the document</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordaccessibilitylearningtoolsreadaloudstopreadaloud"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4382">Office.Word.Accessibility.LearningTools.ReadAloud.StopReadAloud</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4382">Office.Word.Accessibility.LearningTools.ReadAloud.StopReadAloud</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4383">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da je Microsoft Office Word prenehal naglas brati besedilo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4383">This event indicates Office Word stops reading aloud the text in the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4384">Microsoft uporabi ta dogodek za ovrednotenje stanja funkcije branja besedila naglas tako, da izmeri trajanje izvajanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4384">The event allows Microsoft to evaluate the feature health of read-aloud-text by measuring the working duration.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4385">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4385">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

### <a name="privacy-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4387">*Podvrsta zasebnosti*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4387">*Privacy subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4388">Nastavitve zasebnosti za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4388">Office privacy settings</span></span> 

#### <a name="officeintelligentserviceprivacyconsentprivacyevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4389">Office.IntelligentService.PrivacyConsent.PrivacyEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4389">Office.IntelligentService.PrivacyConsent.PrivacyEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4390">Ta dogodek predstavlja dejanje uporabnika ali sistema, ki je del uporabniške izkušnje z zasebnostjo za Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4390">This event represents a user or system initiated action that is part of the privacy User experience for Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4391">Aktivira se v pogovornih oknih zasebnosti ob prvem zagonu, pogovornem oknu zasebnosti računa in obvestilih o zasebnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4391">It is triggered on the privacy First Run dialogs, Account Privacy dialog, and privacy notifications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4392">Dogodek se uporablja za naslednje: razumevanje soglasja uporabnikov za nastavitve zasebnosti za Office, uporabnikovo spreminjanje nastavitev zasebnosti za Office in za posodabljanje nastavitev zasebnosti za Office v uporabniških sejah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4392">The event is used to understand the following: users consenting to Office privacy settings, users changing Office privacy settings, and Office privacy settings getting updated in user sessions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4393">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4393">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4394">**Data_ActionId –** dejanje uporabnika v pogovornem oknu zasebnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4394">**Data_ActionId -** User action in a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4395">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState –** nastavitev pravilnika uporabnika za dodatne izbirne povezane izkušnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4395">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState -** User policy setting for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4396">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState –** nastavitev uporabnika za preneseno vsebino</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4396">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for downloaded content</span></span> 
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4397">**Data_ForwardLinkId –** povezava do dokumentacije o zasebnosti za scenarij uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4397">**Data_ForwardLinkId -** Link to privacy documentation for the user scenario</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4398">**Data_HRESULT –** zapisovanje napak med interakcijo v pogovornem oknu zasebnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4398">**Data_HRESULT -** Record of errors during interaction with a privacy dialog</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4408">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState –** nastavitev uporabnika za analizo vsebine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4408">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for analyzing content</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4414">Napaka pri dejavnosti aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4414">Application activity error</span></span>](#application-activity-error-subtype)

### <a name="unexpected-application-exit-crash-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4415">*Podvrsta nepričakovanega izhoda iz aplikacije (zrušitev)*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4415">*Unexpected application exit (crash) subtype*</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappdomainunhandledexceptionhandlerfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4417">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4417">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4418">Zbira informacije za morebitne neobravnavane izjeme z orodjem za pretakanje podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4418">Collects information for any unhandled exceptions using the Data Streamer App.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4419">Ti podatki se uporabljajo za nadzor stanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4419">This data is used to monitor the health of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4420">Ta dogodek ustvari Microsoftovo orodje za pretakanje podatkov za Excelov dodatek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4420">This event is generated by Microsoft Data Streamer for Excel Add-in.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4421">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4421">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4422">**Exception** – nabor klicev za izjemo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4422">**Exception** - Call stack for the Exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4423">**Event Name** – kategorija dogodka in oznaka dogodka predstavljata ime dogodka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4423">**Event Name** - Event Name is the Event Category and Event Label.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_identitydomainname"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4424">Office_Apple_IdentityDomainName</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4424">Office_Apple_IdentityDomainName</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4425">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4425">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4426">Dogodek uporabljamo za nadzorovanje ustreznosti stanja sistema in preiskovanje vzrokov napak nekaterih uporabnikov domene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4426">The event is used to monitor the health of our system as well as investigating causes of failures by certain domain users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4427">Zbiramo podatke o domeni, ki jo uporabljajo naši uporabniki pri preverjanju pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4427">We collect the domain used by our users when they authenticate.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4428">Ti podatki nam pomagajo prepoznati in odpraviti težave, ki se morda na širši ravni ne zdijo preveč vplivne, za določeno domeno uporabnikov pa se izkažejo za zelo vplivne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4428">We use this data to help identify and fix those issues that might not seem too impactful at a broader level, but that turn out to be very impactful to a certain domain of users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4429">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4429">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4430">**Data_Domain** – domena, ki se uporablja za preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4430">**Data_Domain** - the domain used for authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4431">**Data_IdentityProvider** – ime ponudnika identitete za preverjanje pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4431">**Data_IdentityProvider** - The authentication identity provider name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4432">(npr. LiveId ali ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4432">(i.e. LiveId or ADAL)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4433">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** – koda ponudnika identitete za preverjanje pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4433">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** - The authentication identity provider code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4434">(Število)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4434">(A number)</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_systemhealthappexitmacandios"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4435">Office_Apple_SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4435">Office_Apple_SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4436">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4436">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4437">Dogodek uporabljamo za nadzorovanje ustreznosti stanja Officeovih aplikacij in preiskovanje vzrokov napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4437">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications as well as for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4438">Zbiramo podatke o posameznem izhodu iz aplikacije, da bi ugotovili, ali se je aplikacija zaprla brez napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4438">We collect data on each application exit to determine whether an application exited gracefully.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4439">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4439">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4440">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** – identifikator seje, pri kateri je prišlo do izhoda iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4440">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** - The identifier for the session that experience the application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4441">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** – podrazličica aplikacije, pri kateri je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4441">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4442">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** – dolžina seje od začetka do izhoda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4442">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** - The length of the session from start to exit</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4443">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** – kazalnik ustreznosti stanja telemetrije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4443">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4444">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** – kazalnik ustreznosti stanja telemetrije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4444">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4445">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** – območne nastavitve operacijskega sistema, v katerem je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4445">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** - The Locale of the OS under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4446">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** – različica operacijskega sistema, v katerem je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4446">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** - The OS version under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4447">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** – prostor v stalnem pomnilniku, ki je bil zaseden, ko je prišlo do izhoda iz aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4447">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of resident memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4448">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** – identifikator, ki označuje določeno napako, do katere je prišlo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4448">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** - An identifier that will denote the specific error being hit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4449">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** – čas, ko se je začela seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4449">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** - The time at which the session started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4450">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** – vrsta zaznanega izhoda iz aplikacije (če gre za izhod z napako, ta koda označuje vrsto zaznane napake)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4450">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** - The type of application exit observed (if it was an ungraceful exit, this code will denote the type of error observed)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4451">**Data_AffectedSessionVersionr** – glavna različica aplikacije, pri kateri je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4451">**Data_AffectedSessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4452">**Data_AffectedSessionVirtualMemoryOnCrash** – prostor v navideznem pomnilniku, ki je bil zaseden, ko je prišlo do izhoda iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4452">**Data_AffectedSessionVirtualMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of virtual memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4453">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** – označuje, ali je šlo za izhod iz aplikacije brez napak ali z napakami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4453">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** - Whether the application Exit was graceful or ungraceful.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitycomaddinunhandledexception"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4454">Office.Extensibility.COMAddinUnhandledException</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4454">Office.Extensibility.COMAddinUnhandledException</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4455">Dogodek, ustvarjen ob zrušitvah dodatka COM v potrošniški različici Officeovih aplikacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4455">Event generated when COM Add-in crashes on a consumer version of Office applications.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4456">Uporaba: uporablja se za izračun globalnega »sprejetja« Office 365 ProPlus (ni omejeno na podjetje) za dodatek, ki ga uporabljajo orodja, kot je komplet orodij Readiness.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4456">Usage: this is used to compute a global, non-enterprise-specific Office 365 ProPlus "adoption" for an add-in which is then used by tools like the Readiness Toolkit.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4457">S tem lahko poslovne stranke preverijo, če so dodatki, ki so bili uvedeni v njihovih podjetjih, združljivi z najnovejšimi različicami sistema Office 365 ProPlus, in ustrezno načrtujejo njihove nadgradnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4457">This allows enterprise customers to validate if the add-ins they have deployed in their organizations are compatible with the latest versions of Office 365 ProPlus and plan their upgrades accordingly.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4458">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4458">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4459">**ScopeId** – obseg trenutne niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4459">**ScopeId** – the current thread scope</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4460">**Method** – Officeov način, kjer je prišlo do izjeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4460">**Method** – Office method where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4461">**Interface** – Officeov vmesnik, kjer je prišlo do izjeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4461">**Interface** – Office interface where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4462">**AddinId** – ID razreda za dodatek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4462">**AddinId** – the add-in Class Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4463">**AddinProgId** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4463">**AddinProgId** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4464">**AddinFriendlyName** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4464">**AddinFriendlyName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4465">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – časovni žig dodatka iz metapodatkov DLL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4465">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – the add-in timestamp from the DLL metadata</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4466">**AddinVersion** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4466">**AddinVersion** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4467">**AddinFileName** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4467">**AddinFileName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4468">**VSTOAddIn** – ali je dodatek vrste VSTO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4468">**VSTOAddIn** – whether add-in is VSTO</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4469">**AddinConnectFlag** – vedenje trenutnega nalaganja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4469">**AddinConnectFlag** – current load behavior</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4470">**LoadAttempts** – število poskusov za nalaganje izdelka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4470">**LoadAttempts** – number of attempts to load add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4480">**AddinFriendlyName** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4480">**AddinFriendlyName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4481">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – časovni žig dodatka iz metapodatkov DLL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4481">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – the add-in timestamp from the DLL metadata</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4482">**AddinVersion** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4482">**AddinVersion** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4483">**AddinFileName** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4483">**AddinFileName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4484">**VSTOAddIn** – ali je dodatek vrste VSTO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4484">**VSTOAddIn** – whether add-in is VSTO</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4487">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4487">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4488">Dodatki za Office se zaženejo v peskovniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4488">Office Add-ins run in a sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4489">Ta dogodek zbira informacije o signalih obveščanja o izvajanju programa ob aktiviranjih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4489">This event collects heartbeat information on activations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4490">Ko pride do zrušitve dodatka, ta dogodek zbira podatke o tem, zakaj je prišlo do zrušitve v primeru, ki je povezan z našim peskovnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4490">When an add-in crashes, this event collects why it crashed in the case it’s related to our sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4491">Uporablja se za preiskovanje, ko stranke stopnjujejo težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4491">Used to investigate when customers escalate issues.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4492">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4492">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4493">**AppId** – ID aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4493">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4494">**AppInfo** – podatki glede vrste dodatka (podokno opravil ali UILess ali znotraj vsebine itd.) in vrste ponudnika (Omen, SharePoint, datotečni sistem itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4494">**AppInfo** - Data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4495">**AppInstanceId** – ID primerka aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4495">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4496">**AssetId** – ID sredstva aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4496">**AssetId** - Asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4497">**ErrorCode** – skupni porabljeni čas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4497">**ErrorCode** - Total time spent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4498">**IsDebug** – označuje sejo za odpravljanje napak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4498">**IsDebug** - indicates if session is a debug session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4499">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** – števec aktiviranih dodatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4499">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - Counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4500">**RemoterType** – določa vrsto remoterja (zaupanja vreden, ni vreden zaupanja, Win32webView, zaupanja vreden UDF itd.), ki se uporablja za aktiviranje dodatka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4500">**RemoterType** - Specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF, etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4501">**StoreType** – izvor aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4501">**StoreType** - Origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4502">**Oznaka**– določa, kje točno je prišlo do napake kode, in sicer z enolično oznako, ki je povezana s kodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4502">**Tag**- Specifies where exactly the code has failed using the unique tag associated with it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4503">**UsesSharedRuntime** – označuje, ali aplikacija uporablja sharedRuntime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4503">**UsesSharedRuntime** - indicates the app uses sharedRuntime or not.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeextensibilityvbatelemetrybreak"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4504">Office.Extensibility.VbaTelemetryBreak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4504">Office.Extensibility.VbaTelemetryBreak</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4505">Dogodek, ki se ustvari, ko datoteka z omogočenimi makri naleti na napako pri prevajanju ali izvajanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4505">Event generated when a macro-enabled file runs into a compile or runtime error</span></span>

Wordovi makri, Excelovi makri itd.), ki se uporabljajo za določitev, ali je med pilotnim projektom dodatek »pripravljen na nadgradnjo« v proizvodnem ciklu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4506">Desktop Analytics: This is used as numerator in the computation of enterprise-specific health status for macro types (e.g. Word macros, Excel macros, etc.) which is used to infer during pilot if the add-in is "ready to upgrade" in the production ring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4507">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4507">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4508">**TagId** – ID oznake za telemetrijo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4508">**TagId** – the id of the telemetry tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4509">**BreakReason** – razlog za prekinitev (napaka pri izvajanju, prevajanju ali druga napaka.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4509">**BreakReason** – the reason for the break (runtime, compile, other error)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4511">**Data.ErrorCode** – koda napake, ki jo je zaznal mehanizem VBA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4511">**Data.ErrorCode** – error code reported by VBA engine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4516">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4516">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktophangbucketmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4519">Office.Outlook.Desktop.HangBucketMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4519">Office.Outlook.Desktop.HangBucketMetrics</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4520">Zbira informacije o neodzivnosti v Outlooku – enolični identifikator za posamezne dogodke neodzivnosti, pretečeni čas in informacije o naboru klicev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4520">Collects hang time for outlook hangs – a unique identifier per hang, elapsed time, and call stack information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4521">Podatki se uporabljajo za zaznavanje in prepoznavanje zrušitev informacij, zahtevanih za odpravljanje napak v bodočih posodobitvah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4521">The data is used to detect and identify app crashes in order to fix in future updates.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktophangreportingscopeperfmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4526">Office.Outlook.Desktop.HangReportingScopePerfMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4526">Office.Outlook.Desktop.HangReportingScopePerfMetrics</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4527">Zbira podatke o času, zahtevane za ključne scenarije v Outlooku – switchfolder switchmodule, sendmailoutbox, openitemclassic, sendmailtransport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4527">Collects time taken for outlook core scenarios – switchfolder, switchmodule, sendmailoutbox, openitemclassic, sendmailtransport.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4528">Ti podatki so aktivno nadzorovani proti nenavadnim težavam z učinkovitostjo delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4528">The data is actively monitored for anomalous performance issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4529">Uporabljajo se za zaznavanje in diagnosticiranje težav z učinkovitostjo delovanja ter izboljšanje učinkovitosti delovanja v bodočih posodobitvah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4529">It is used to detect and diagnose performance issues as well as improve performance with each update.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4532">**ScopeId** – ime funkcije, ki vsebuje deklaracijo ali ime po meri, podeljen prek definicije obsega</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4532">**ScopeId** - name of the function containing the declaration or a custom name given through scope definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4534">To pravilo zbira informacije o zrušitvi iz dnevnikov dogodkov, ko se je zrušil Outlook v prejšnji seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4534">This rule collects the crash information from the event logs when Outlook crashed in the previous session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4537">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4537">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4538">**BucketId** – razpršitev nabora klicev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4538">**BucketId** – hash of the call stack</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4539">**ElapsedTotal** – skupni čas, porabljen za klic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4539">**ElapsedTotal** - total time spent in the call</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointsession"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4541">Office.PowerPoint.Session</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4541">Office.PowerPoint.Session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4542">Zbiranje uporab funkcije v posameznih PowerPointovih sejah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4542">Collecting feature usages on each PowerPoint session.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4543"> Ti podatki se uporabljajo za izračun razmerja neprimernih izhodov iz PowerPointa med uporabo funkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4543"> This data is used to calculate the ratio of PowerPoint ungraceful exit while using a feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4544">Razmerje neprimernih izhodov iz PowerPointa predstavlja poglavitni signal za zagotovitev, da PowerPoint ne deluje po pričakovanjih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4544">The ratio of PowerPoint ungraceful exit is a key signal to guarantee PowerPoint is running as expected.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4546">**Flag** – zastavice sej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4546">**Flag** – session flags</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4547">**Usage** – uporabe funkcij</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4547">**Usage** – feature usages</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointuaedialog"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4548">Office.PowerPoint.UAE.Dialog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4548">Office.PowerPoint.UAE.Dialog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4549">Ti podatki so zbrani vsakič, ko se PowerPoint neprimerno zapre, ko je prikazano pogovorno okno na vrhu glavnega okna v PowerPointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4549">Collected every time when PowerPoint ungracefully exited while a dialog open on top of PowerPoint main window.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4550">Te informacije so ključnega pomena za zaznavanje neprimernih izhodov iz PowerPointa, ki jih povzroči aktivno pogovorno okno, ki blokira glavno okno v PowerPointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4550">This information is critical to catch PowerPoint ungracefully exits due to an active dialog blocking PowerPoint main window.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4551">Microsoft s temi podatki diagnosticira težave in tako zagotovi pravilno delovanje PowerPointa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4551">Microsoft is using this data to diagnose the issue in order to guarantee PowerPoint running as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4552">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4552">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4553">**DlgCnt** – skupno število odprtih pogovornih oken ob zrušitvi seje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4553">**DlgCnt** – total number of open dialogs when session crashed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4554">**DlgId** – identifikator odprtega pogovornega okna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4554">**DlgId** – open dialog identifier</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4555">**IdType** – vrsta identifikatorja odprtega pogovornega okna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4555">**IdType** – open dialog identifier type</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4556">**InitTime** – čas inicializacije zrušene seje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4556">**InitTime** – crashed session initialized time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4557">**SessionId** – identifikator zrušene seje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4557">**SessionId** – crashed session identifier</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4558">**TopId** – identifikator zgornjega pogovornega okna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4558">**TopId** – top dialog identifier</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4559">**Version** – različica zrušene seje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4559">**Version** – crashed session version</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointuaedocument"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4560">Office.PowerPoint.UAE.Document</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4560">Office.PowerPoint.UAE.Document</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4561">Dogodek, ki zbira podatke o funkciji, ki je bila uporabljena v dokumentu, ko je prišlo do nenavadnega izhoda iz PowerPointa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4561">Collecting what feature is being used on a document when PowerPoint ungracefully exited.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4562">Te funkcije vključujejo diaprojekcijo, odpiranje, shranjevanje, urejanje in soavtorstvo dokumenta ter zaustavitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4562">These features include slide show, document open, save, edit, co-authoring, shutdown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4563">Te informacije so ključnega pomena za zaznavanje nenavadnih izhodov iz PowerPointa med uporabo funkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4563">This information is critical to catch PowerPoint ungracefully exits while using a feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4564">Microsoft s temi podatki diagnosticira težave in tako zagotovi pravilno delovanje PowerPointa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4564">Microsoft is using this data to diagnose the issue in order to guarantee PowerPoint running as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4565">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4565">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4566">**CoauthFlag** – zastavice za uporabo soavtorstva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4566">**CoauthFlag** – coauth usage flags</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4567">**CommandFlag** – zastavice za spreminjanje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4567">**CommandFlag** – document modification flags</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4627">**FriendlyName** – prijazno ime dodatka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4627">**FriendlyName** – the add-in friendly name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4628">**Interface** – Officeov vmesnik, kjer je prišlo do izjeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4628">**Interface** – the Office interface where the exception occurred</span></span>

#### <a name="initial_page_landing"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4670">Initial_page_landing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4670">Initial_page_landing</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4671">Ta dogodek nam pomaga slediti vrsti izkušnje, ki je prikazana uporabnikom, ko se znajdejo na strani aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4671">This event helps track the type of experience that users see when they land in our application page.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4672">Te podatke uporabljamo za ugotavljanje prometa uporabnikov, ki se steka v okviru posamezne izkušnje v aplikaciji, in za lažje usklajevanje rezultatov eksperimentiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4672">This data is used to determine the traffic of users piped into each experience in our application and also helps us to easily consolidate experimentation results.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4673">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4673">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4674">**Stran** – to se uporablja se za sledenje vrsti izkušnje, ki je uporabniku najprej prikazana, ko se znajde na naši strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4674">**Page** - This is used to track the type of experience that user first sees when they land on our page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4675">Možne vrednosti so »Preskusna različica«, »Preskoči«, »V paketu«, »Naročnina« itn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4675">Possible values are “Trial”, “Skip”, “Prebundled”, “Subscription” etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4676">**storeExperience** – to se uporablja za ugotavljanje, ali je bil uporabnik upravičen do ogleda izkušnje SDK za Store.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4676">**storeExperience** - This is used to determine if user was eligible to see the Store SDK Experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4677">**stringVariant** – to se uporablja za ugotavljanje vrste nizov, ki so prikazani uporabnikom, ko se znajdejo na naši strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4677">**stringVariant** - This is used to determine the type of strings that user sees when they land on our page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4678">Na vsaki strani, npr. »Preskusna različica«, je uporabnik upravičen do ogleda različnih nizov, in sicer glede na to, ali ima nameščen podedovan Office ali če je že kdaj prej aktiviral Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4678">Note that for any page such as “Trial”, user can be eligible to see different strings based on whether they had Legacy Office installed, or if they had previously activated Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4679">Možni elementi naštevanja za to lastnost so »LegacyUpsell«, »OfficeOpened«, »Privzeto «, »YesIntent«, »NoIntent« itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4679">Possible enumerations of this property are “LegacyUpsell”, “OfficeOpened”, “Default”, “YesIntent”, “NoIntent” etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4680">**windowsBuildType** – to se uporablja za sledenje vrsti graditve WindowsBuildType, ki jo uporabnik uporablja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4680">**windowsBuildType** - This is used to track the type of WindowsBuildType that user is on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4681">Npr. »RS4«,»RS5«,»RS19H1«,»Vibranium« ipd. Ker so izkušnje običajno namenjene različnim vrstam graditve WindowsBuildTypes, je ta lastnost ključnega pomena pri razlikovanju med uvedbami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4681">i.e. “RS4”, “RS5”, “RS19H1”, “Vibranium etc. As our experiences are usually targeted to different WindowsBuildTypes, this property is vital in differentiating between rollouts.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidofficelaunchtolandingpagelatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4723">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeLaunchToLandingPageLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4723">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeLaunchToLandingPageLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4724">Ključnega pomena za zajem meritev učinkovitosti delovanja aplikacije glede na odzivni čas aplikacije od zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4724">Critical to capture for app performance metric with respect to the response time of the app from the boot.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4725">Microsoft s tem dogodkom zbira čas, zahtevan za odzivnost aplikacije, in za zaznavanje scenarijev, ki lahko vplivajo na čas zagona v aplikacijah WXP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4725">Microsoft uses this to collect the time taken for the app to be responsive and also detect scenarios that may impact boot time in WXP apps.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4726">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4726">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4727">**AnyCrashInteractionDuringBoot** – Logična vrednost za morebitno zrušitev med zagonom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4727">**AnyCrashInteractionDuringBoot** - Boolean for any crash encountered during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4728">**AppActivationTimeInMs** – Čas zrušitve aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4728">**AppActivationTimeInMs** - App phase time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4729">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** – Logična vrednost za začasno prekinitev aplikacije med zagonom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4729">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean for app suspension during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4730">**AvailableMemoryInMB, ki je na voljo** – Pomnilnik, ki je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4730">**AvailableMemoryInMB** - available memory</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4731">**CollectionTime** – Čas dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4731">**CollectionTime** - Timestamp of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4732">**DalvikHeapLimitInMB** – Informacije kopice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4732">**DalvikHeapLimitInMB** - Heap info</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4733">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bil dokument obnovljen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4733">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** - Boolean to indicate if any document was recovered</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4734">**ExtractionDone** – Čas ekstrahiranja izvorne knjižnice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4734">**ExtractionDone** - Native library extraction time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4735">**FastBootGainTimeInMs** – Čas, zahtevan za dokončanje hitrega zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4735">**FastBootGainTimeInMs** - Time for fast boot completion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4736">**FileActivationAttempted** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila aplikacija zagnana zaradi aktivacije datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4736">**FileActivationAttempted** - Boolean to indicate if app was launched due to File activation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4737">**HasLogcatLoggingImpactOnBoot** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali Logcat vpliva na čas zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4737">**HasLogcatLoggingImpactOnBoot** - Boolean to indicate if logcat impacted boot time</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_msoappdelegate_bootperf"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4841">Office_Apple_MsoAppDelegate_BootPerf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4841">Office_Apple_MsoAppDelegate_BootPerf</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4842">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4842">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4843">Dogodek uporabljamo za zbiranje podatkov o času in prostoru v pomnilniku, porabljenima med zagonom z Officeovimi aplikacijami ter nekaj podatkov o vrsti izvedenega zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4843">The event is used to collect time and memory consumed during boot by Office apps, as well as some details on the type of boot done.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4844">Ta dogodek nam pomaga pri nadziranju učinkovitost delovanja in zagotavljanju izboljšav učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4844">This event helps us monitor our performance and provide performance improvements.</span></span>
