- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4847">**Data_AppLaunchFinishSystemTime** – časovni žig pri določeni oznaki kode zagona</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4847">**Data_AppLaunchFinishSystemTime** - A timestamp at a particular boot code marker</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4848">**Data_AppLaunchStartSystemTime** – časovni žig pri določeni oznaki kode zagona</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4848">**Data_AppLaunchStartSystemTime** - A timestamp at a particular boot code marker</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4849">**Data_ResidentMemory** – posnetek stalnega pomnilnika, ki je na voljo med zagonom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4849">**Data_ResidentMemory** - A snapshot of the available resident memory during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4850">**Data_VirtualMemory** – posnetek navideznega pomnilnika, ki je na voljo med zagonom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4850">**Data_VirtualMemory** - A snapshot of the available virtual memory during boot</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_ungracefulappexithangsinprevioussession"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4851">Office_Apple_UngracefulAppExitHangsInPreviousSession</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4851">Office_Apple_UngracefulAppExitHangsInPreviousSession</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4852">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4852">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4853">Dogodek uporabljamo za nadzorovanje ustreznosti stanja Officeovih aplikacij in preiskovanje vzrokov napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4853">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications as well as for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4854">Zbiramo podatke o tem, kolikokrat je bila aplikacija neodzivna, preden je prišlo do izhoda iz aplikacije z napakami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4854">We collect the number of times an application appeared to be unresponsive prior to hitting an ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4855">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4855">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4856">**Data_HangsDetected** – označuje, kolikokrat je bila aplikacija neodzivna, preden je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije z napakami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4856">**Data_HangsDetected** - The number of times the application appeared to become unresponsive prior to observing the ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4857">**Data_LastSessionId** – identifikator seje, pri kateri je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije z napakami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4857">**Data_LastSessionId** - The identifier for the session in which the ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4858">**Data_SessionBuildNumber** – podrazličica aplikacije, pri kateri je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije z napakami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4858">**Data_SessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4859">**Data_SessionVersion** – glavna različica aplikacije, pri kateri je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije z napakami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4859">**Data_SessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_whatsnewerrorandwarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4860">Office_Apple_WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4860">Office_Apple_WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4861">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4861">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4862">Dogodek uporabljamo za nadziranje ustreznosti stanja funkcije »Novosti«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4862">The event is used to monitor the health of the What’s New feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4863">Ta dogodek pomeni, da je med razčlenjevanjem vsebine »Novosti« prišlo do napake/opozorila, kar kaže na morebitne težave z avtorstvom vsebine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4863">This event denotes that an error/warning occurred while parsing What's New content, pointing to potential content authoring issues.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4864">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4864">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4865">**Data_ContentKey** – kazalec na del vsebine, ki je verjetno povzročil napako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4865">**Data_ContentKey** - A pointer to the section of the content that is likely to have caused the error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4866">**Data_ErrorCode** – zaznana koda napake (če je na voljo)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4866">**Data_ErrorCode** - The observed error code (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4867">**Data_ErrorDescription** – opis napake (če je na voljo)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4867">**Data_ErrorDescription** - A description of the error (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4868">**Data_EventID** – zbiramo niz, ki predstavlja vrsto zaznane napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4868">**Data_EventID** - We collect a string representing the type of error observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4869">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** – označuje, ali vsebina vključuje obogateni html</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4869">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** - Whether the content contains rich html</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4870">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** – označuje, ali vsebina vključuje hierarhijo elementov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4870">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** - Whether the content contains a hierarchy of items</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4871">**Data_LengthOfRawData** – velikost vsebine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4871">**Data_LengthOfRawData** - The size of the content</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4872">**Data_RequestURL** – spletni naslov, s katerega je bila vsebina prenesena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4872">**Data_RequestURL** - The URL from which the content was downloaded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4873">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** – jezik, v katerem je bila vsebina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4873">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** - The language the content was in.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4874">**Data_StatusCode** – stanje napake (če je na voljo)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4874">**Data_StatusCode** - The status of the error (if available)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilityrichapimethodinvocation"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4875">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4875">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4876">Ko stranka uporablja Officeov dodatek in izvaja klice obogatenega API-ja za zagotavljanje storitve, bo sprožen ta dogodek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4876">When customer uses an Office Add-in and calls Rich API for providing service, this event will be triggered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4877">Uporablja se za merjenje zanesljivosti, učinkovitosti delovanja in uporabe storitve za priklic načina obogatenega API-ja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4877">Used to measure the service reliability, performance and usage for Rich API method invocation.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4878">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4878">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4879">**Api** – polno ime API-ja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4879">**Api** - Full name of the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4880">**DispFlag** – bitna zastavica, ki opisuje vrsto metode (npr.: 0x1 = METHOD, 0x2 = PROPERTYGET, 0x4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0x8 = PROPERTYPUTREF)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4880">**DispFlag** - A bit flag describing the type of method call (Ex: 0x1 = METHOD, 0x2 = PROPERTYGET, 0x4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0x8 = PROPERTYPUTREF)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4881">**Despid** – ID razpošiljanja za metodo, ki je klicana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4881">**DispId** - Dispatch ID for the method being called</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4882">**HResult** – »HResult« za klic metode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4882">**HResult** - HResult for the method call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4883">**Latency** – zakasnitev klica v mikrosekundah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4883">**Latency** - Latency for the call, in microseconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4884">**ReqId** – GUID za paketno zahtevo, ki ji ta metoda pripada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4884">**ReqId** - GUID for the batch request that this method belongs to</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4885">**TypeId** – GUID za vmesnik, v katerem je ta metoda klicana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4885">**TypeId** - GUID for the interface on which this method being called</span></span>


#### <a name="officemanageabilityserviceapplypolicy"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4886">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4886">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4887">Kritična telemetrija za sledenje neuspeha\\uspeha pri uporabi nastavitev pravilnika v oblaku v registru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4887">Critical telemetry to track failure\\Success of applying cloud policy settings to registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4888">Iz elementa LastError je razvidno, zakaj in kje je prišlo do napake pri uveljavljanju pravilnika v registru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4888">LastError tells why and where the Application of policy in registry failed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4889">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4889">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4890">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** – sporočilo izjeme, če je bil uveljavljen pravilnik while</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4890">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** - The exception msg if any while policy was being applied</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4891">**Data.Cid** – dinamično ustvarjeni identifikator korelacije, poslan storitvi, ko je bil opravljen klic storitve za pridobivanje pravilnika v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4891">**Data.Cid** - dynamically generated correlation identifier sent to the service when the service call was made to fetch the cloud policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4892">Uporablja se za medsebojno odvisnost pri uporabi pravilnikov v oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4892">Used to correlate which call caused an issue while applying the policies on the cloud.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4893">**Data.Last Error** – ena od petih vrednosti niza (popisovalnik) za beleženje, katera stopnja pravilnika je bila izvedena, ko je prišlo do izjeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4893">**Data.Last Error** - One of five string values (enumerators) to log which stage of policy application was being executed when the exception occurred</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktopbootperfmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4894">Office.Outlook.Desktop.BootPerfMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4894">Office.Outlook.Desktop.BootPerfMetrics</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4895">Zbira čas, zahtevan za zagon Outlooka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4895">Collects time taken to boot Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4896">Čas zagona Outlooka je aktivno nadzorovan za zaznavanje in diagnosticiranje regresij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4896">The boot time of Outlook is actively monitored to detect and diagnose regressions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4897">Prav tako se uporablja za diagnosticiranje stopnjevanj stranke in za izboljšanje učinkovitosti delovanja zagona v bodoče.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4897">It is also used to diagnose customer escalations as well as improve boot performance over time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4898">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4898">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4899">**AddinElapsedTotal** – skupni čas, porabljen za nalaganje dodatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4899">**AddinElapsedTotal** - Total time spent for loading add-ins</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4900">**CredPromptCount** – število prikazanih pozivov za vnos poverilnic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4900">**CredPromptCount** – Number of credential prompts shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4901">**ElapsedTotal** – skupni čas, porabljen za zagon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4901">**ElapsedTotal** - Total time spent for boot</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4902">**IsLoggingEnabled** – ali je omogočeno pisanje dnevnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4902">**IsLoggingEnabled** - Is logging enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4903">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – ali je bilo prikazano pogovorno okno za izbiranje profila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4903">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – Whether the Choose Profile Dialog was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4904">**ShowFirstRunDlg** – ali je bil Outlook prvič zagnan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4904">**ShowFirstRunDlg** - is outlook launched for the first time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4905">**ShowIMAPSrchfldWarningDlg** – opozorila v primeru računa IMAP z elementi ANSI PST</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4905">**ShowIMAPSrchfldWarningDlg** - Warnings in case we have an IMAP account with an ANSI PST</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4906">**ShowNeedSupportDlg** – neuspešen zagon je aktiviral pogovorno okno podpore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4906">**ShowNeedSupportDlg** - Boot failure triggered support dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4907">**ShowSafeModeDlg** – ali je bila seja odprta v varnem načinu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4907">**ShowSafeModeDlg** - is the session opened in safe mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4908">**ShowScanPstDlg** – pregled za popravilo trgovine je prikazal sporočilo o napaki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4908">**ShowScanPstDlg** - Store repair check displayed error message</span></span>


#### <a name="officeoutlookmacbootperf"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4909">Office.Outlook.Mac.BootPerf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4909">Office.Outlook.Mac.BootPerf</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4910">Zbira čas, zahtevan za zagon Outlooka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4910">Collects time taken to boot Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4911">Čas zagona Outlooka je aktivno nadzorovan za zaznavanje in diagnosticiranje regresij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4911">The boot time of Outlook is actively monitored to detect and diagnose regressions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4912">Prav tako se uporablja za diagnosticiranje stopnjevanj stranke in za izboljšanje učinkovitosti delovanja zagona v bodoče.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4912">It is also used to diagnose customer escalations as well as improve boot performance over time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4913">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4913">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4914">**MacOLKBootPerfDuration** – skupni čas, porabljen za zagon.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4914">**MacOLKBootPerfDuration** - total time spent booting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4915">**MacOLKBootPerfID** – identifikator časa, ki je porabljen za zagon.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4915">**MacOLKBootPerfID** - identifier for the time spent booting</span></span>


#### <a name="officeoutlookmacperformanceunresponsive"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4916">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4916">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4917">Uporablja se za identifikacijo težav v Outlooku, ki vplivajo na uporabnike in se lahko izrazijo kot poslabšano delovanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4917">Used to identify user impacting issues in Outlook that may manifest as degraded performance.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4918">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4918">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4919">**Duration** – čas, potekel od poslabšanega delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4919">**Duration** - time elapsed of degraded performance</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4920">**EventType** – vrsta dogodka, pri katerem prihaja do izkušnje poslabšane učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4920">**EventType** - type of event experiencing degraded performance</span></span>


#### <a name="officeperformanceboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4921">Office.Performance.Boot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4921">Office.Performance.Boot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4922">Zbrano, ko je zagnana Officeova aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4922">Collected when an Office application is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4923">Vključuje podatke o tem, kdaj je bil zagnan inicializiran z odpiranjem datoteke ali z zagonom prek začetnega menija, ali je bil to prvi zagon aplikacije, koliko pomnilnika porablja aplikacija in ali je bil uporabniku prikazan UV, ki je oviral pogled.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4923">Includes whether the boot was initiated by opening a file or launching via the Start menu, whether this was the first boot of the application, how much memory the application is using, and whether there was any blocking UI shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4924">Uporabljeno za merjenje hitrosti zagona Officeovih aplikacij in koliko pomnilnika porabijo, ko se zaženejo. Na ta način je zagotovljena sprejemljiva uporabniška izkušnja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4924">Used to measure how fast Office applications boot and how much memory they use when they start, to ensure there is an acceptable user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4925">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4925">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4926">**ActivationKind** – ali je bila aplikacija zagnana z zagonom v začetnem meniju, z odpiranjem datoteke ali avtomatizacijo OLE.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4926">**ActivationKind** - Whether the application was started by launching from the Start menu, by opening a file, or through OLE Automation.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4927">**BootToStart** – ali se je uporabnik odločil za prikaz začetnega zaslona, ko se ta aplikacija zažene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4927">**BootToStart** - Whether the user has chosen to show the start screen when this application starts.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4928">**Data_DocumentLocation** – pri odpiranju dokumenta označuje, v kateri storitvi je na voljo dokument (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4928">**DocLocation** -  When opening a document, indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4929">**FirstBoot** – ali je bil to prvi zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4929">**FirstBoot** - Whether this was a first boot of the application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4930">**InitializationDuration** – koliko časa v mikrosekundah je preteklo za prvo inicializacijo Officeovega postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4930">**InitializationDuration** - The duration in microseconds it took to first initialize the Office process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4931">**InterruptionMessageId** – ID pogovornega okna, če je zagon prekinilo pogovorno okno, ki je uporabnika pozivalo k vnosu podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4931">**InterruptionMessageId** - If the boot was interrupted by a dialog asking for user input, the ID of the dialog.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4932">**TotalWorkingSetMB** – količina pomnilnika v megabajtih v delovnem naboru postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4932">**TotalWorkingSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process’s working set.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4933">**VirtualSetMB** – količina pomnilnika v megabajtih v navideznem naboru postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4933">**VirtualSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process’s virtual set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4934">(Samo MacOS/iOS)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4934">(MacOS / iOS only)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4935">**WorkingSetPeakMB** – največja količina pomnilnika v megabajtih, ki je bila doslej v delovnem naboru postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4935">**WorkingSetPeakMB** - The largest amount of memory in megabytes that was ever in the process’s working set so far.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeuxofficeinsidershowofficeinsiderdlg"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4951">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4951">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4952">Uporabniška interakcija sledenja kritičnega signala s pogovornim oknom »Pridružite se programu Office Insider«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4952">Critical signal tracking user interaction with Join Office Insider dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4953">Uporablja se za prepoznavanje kakršnih koli težav pri izvajanju sprememb, ki jih sproži uporabnik, kot sta pridružitev programu Office Insider ali zapuščanje tega programa in spreminjanje ravni programa Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4953">It is used for identifying any issues in performing user-initiated changes such as joining or leaving Office Insider program and changing Office Insider level.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4954">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4954">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4956">**Data_InsiderLevel** – raven programa Insider pri odpiranju pogovornega okna »Pridružite se programu Office Insider«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4956">**Data_InsiderLevel** - Insider Level on opening of “Join Office Insider” dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4957">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** – raven programa Insider pri zapiranju pogovornega okna »Pridružite se programu Office Insider«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4957">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** - Insider level on closing of “Join Office Insider” dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4958">**Data_IsInternalUser** – označuje, ali se aplikacija izvaja s poverilnicami Microsoftovega poslovnega računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4958">**Data_IsInternalUser** - Indicates whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4959">**Data_IsInternalUserInit** – označuje, ali lahko koda določi, ali se aplikacija izvaja s poverilnicami Microsoftovega poslovnega računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4959">**Data_IsInternalUserInit** - Indicates whether the code could determine whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4960">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** – označuje, ali je bila povezava do naročnine na glasilo »Office Insider« sprožena pod pogojem, da se je uporabnik pridružil programu »Office Insider«, da je omogočena funkcija »Naročnina na glasilo« in da uporabnik ni preklical odpiranja spletne strani z naročnino na glasilo »Office Insider«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4960">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** - Indicates whether Office Insider Newsletter Subscription link was triggered under condition that user has joined Office Insider program, Newsletter Subscription feature is enabled, and the user have not cancelled opening of Office Insider Newsletter Subscription webpage.</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4961">**Data_RegisterInsider** – stanje registracije programa Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4961">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4962">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** – koda rezultata za registracijo v programu Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4962">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** - Result code for Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4963">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** – trenutno stanje registracije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4963">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** - Current registration state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4964">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** – zahtevano stanje registracije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4964">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** - Requested registration state</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4966">Ta dogodek zajame čas, zahtevan za upodobitev datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4966">This event captures file render time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4967">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko poskrbimo za učinkovito upodabljanje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4967">This event helps us keep file render performance in check.</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiovisiofileopenreliability"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4974">Office.Visio.VisioFileOpenReliability</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4974">Office.Visio.VisioFileOpenReliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4975">Ta dogodek zbira podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek za Visio Dev16.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4975">This event collects File open perf data for Visio Dev16.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4976">Ta dogodek se uporablja za nadzor učinkovitosti delovanja za odpiranje datoteke, ki jo poveže z lastnostmi datoteke, kot je velikost datoteke, za Visio Dev16.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4976">This event is used to monitor performance of File open and associates it with file properties like file size for Visio Dev16.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4977">Lastnosti datoteke nam omogočajo, da hitreje odkrijemo napako in poiščemo glavni vzrok.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4977">File properties enable us debug and root cause issues faster.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4978">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4978">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4979">**Data\_CorrelationId: string –** identifikator korelacije dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4979">**Data\_CorrelationId: string -** Document correlation identifier</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4980">**Data\_DocIsEnterpriseProtected: bool –** ima vrednost true, če je dokument zaščiten z zaščito informacij sistema Windows</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4980">**Data\_DocIsEnterpriseProtected: bool -** true if document is protected with Windows information protection</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4981">**Data\_DocumentId: string -** GUID za pot datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4981">**Data\_DocumentId: string -** GUID of file path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4982">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds:double –** čas, zahtevan za dokončanje shranjevanja, v milisekundah</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4982">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds: double -** Duration to complete save as in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4983">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMillisecondsSquared: double –** kvadratna vrednost za DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4983">**Data\_DurationToCompleteInMillisecondsSquared: double -** squared value for DurationToCompleteInMilliseconds</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4984">**Data\_ErrorCode: integer –** koda notranje napake za neuspešno odpiranje datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4984">**Data\_ErrorCode: integer -** Internal error code for file open failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-4985">**Data\_Extension\_Docs: string –** pripona datoteke za odprti diagram</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-4985">**Data\_Extension\_Docs: string -** File extension of diagram opened</span></span>

### <a name="application-activity-error-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5011">*Podvrsta napake pri dejavnosti aplikacije*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5011">*Application activity error subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5012">Napake v delovanju funkcije ali uporabniške izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5012">Errors in functionality of a feature or user experience.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriversofthang"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5013">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5013">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5014">Microsoftu pomaga razlikovati dolgotrajne neodzivnosti gonilnika grafične kartice od kratkotrajnih. Na ta način je lažje določiti, pri katerih gonilnikih grafične kartice se je pojavila napaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5014">Helps Microsoft separate long video card driver hangs from short ones, which in turn helps make decisions about which video card drivers may be having problems.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5015">Gonilnik grafične kartice uporabnika je povzročil neodzivnost Officea, vpliv neodzivnosti pa še ni določen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5015">The user's video card driver has caused Office to hang, but the impact of the hang is not known yet</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5016">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5016">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5017">**Data\_InDeviceCall** – poklicani način grafične kartice, ki je povzročil neodzivnost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5017">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - The method called on the video card that produced the hang</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5018">**Data\_Timeout** – čas neodzivnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5018">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted</span></span>

  #### <a name="officeandroidadalsigninuiprompts"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5019">Office.Android.ADALSignInUIPrompts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5019">Office.Android.ADALSignInUIPrompts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5020">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da je bil uporabniku prikazan poziv za vpis v šolski ali službeni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5020">This event denotes that sign-in prompt came to the user, for school or work account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5021">Ta dogodek omogoča lažje razumevanje stanja vpisa naših aplikacij in izvedbo ustreznih dejanj, ko zaznamo nepričakovane pozive za vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5021">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected sign-in re-prompts.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5022">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5022">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5023">**LastLoginDelta** – Delta čas zadnje uspešne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5023">**LastLoginDelta** - the time delta from last successful login</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5024">**PreviousIdentityCredProviderState** – Označuje stanje računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5024">**PreviousIdentityCredProviderState** - Indicates the state of the account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5025">**PreviousIdentityState** – Označuje stanje računa, kot je potekla seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5025">**PreviousIdentityState** - Indicates state of the account, like session expired.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5026">**SignInResultCode** – Označuje kodo rezultata za končanje poziva za vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5026">**SignInResultCode** - Indicates the result code of sign-in prompt end.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5027">**UseCache** – Označuje, ali smo uporabnika pozvali k ponovnemu vpisu gesla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5027">**UseCache** - Indicates if we force prompted the user to provide the password again.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5028">**UserType** – Označuje, ali gre za obstoječi ali nov račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5028">**UserType** - Indicates whether it is existing account or new account</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidappdocsfileoperationends"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5029">Office.Android.AndroidAppDocsFileOperationEnds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5029">Office.Android.AndroidAppDocsFileOperationEnds</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5030">Telemetrični podatki kritičnih dokumentov samo za Android (AppDocs) za končanje operacij Datoteka > Novo/Odpri/Shrani kot.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5030">Critical Docs Android Only (AppDocs) telemetry data for File New/Open/SaveAs end operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5031">S tem dogodkom zabeležite kode napak za vse neuspešne operacije AppDocs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5031">This captures error codes for failures of these AppDocsOperations.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5032">Microsoft s tem dogodkom prepozna napake v različnih postopkih datoteke in sloj, v katerem se je pojavila napaka v aplikacijah WXP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5032">Microsoft uses this to identify failures in various file operation and the exact layer at which the failure has occurred in WXP apps.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5033">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5033">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5034">**AccessMode** – Vrednost oštevilčenja za način dostopa do datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5034">**AccessMode** - enumeration value for the access mode for the file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5035">Vrednosti – None, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5035">Values- None, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5036">**BlockingUIShown** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bil v toku prikazan blokiran uporabniški vmesnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5036">**BlockingUIShown** - Boolean to indicate if blocking UI was shown in the flow anywhere.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5037">**ContentUriAuthority** – overitelj URL-ja vsebina iz SAF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5037">**ContentUriAuthority** - the authority of the content URL from SAF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5038">**Correlation** – GUID za ID korelacije, povezanega s postopkom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5038">**Correlation** - GUID for the correlation Id related to the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5039">**DocId** – ID dokumenta, ki ga je ustvaril AppDocs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5039">**DocId** - the document ID generated by AppDocs</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5040">**DocInstanceId** – ID primerka dokumenta, ki ga je ustvaril AppDocs, glede na obseg primerka operacije v dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5040">**DocInstanceId** - DocInstanceId the document instance ID generated by AppDocs that is scoped to an operation instance on a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5041">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je dokument zaščiten.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5041">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** - Boolean to indicate if document is protected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5042">**DocUserId** – ID uporabnika iz plasti MS auth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5042">**DocUserId** - user ID from the MS auth layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5043">**DocUserIdProvider** – Oštevilčenje, ki predstavlja ponudnika ID-ja uporabnika, 0 = neznano, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5043">**DocUserIdProvider** - enumeration that represents the user ID provider, 0 = Unkown, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5044">**DurationInMs** – Čas v milisekundah, da se operacija datoteke konča.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5044">**DurationInMs** - time in millisecond for the file operation to end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5045">**EndReason** – Vrednost oštevilčenja za vzrok končanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5045">**EndReason** - enumeration value for the end reason.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5046">Vrednosti – None, Success, Failure, Cancel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5046">Values - None, Success, Failure, Cancel</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5047">**ErrorCode** – Koda napake za delovanje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5047">**ErrorCode** - error code for the file operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5048">**Extension** – Razširitev datoteke, ki jo želite odpreti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5048">**Extension** - extension of the file being opened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5049">**FileSourceLocation** – Vrednost oštevilčenja za mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5049">**FileSourceLocation** - enumeration value for file location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5050">Morebitne vrednosti: None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5050">Possible values: None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5051">**FILETIME** – Čas dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5051">**FILETIME** - Time of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5052">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** – Informacije o kodi napake, povezani s pretvorbami datotek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5052">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** - Error code information related to file conversions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5053">**HttpStatusCode** – Koda odziva http za zahtevo spletne storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5053">**HttpStatusCode** - http response code for web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5054">**InitalizationReason** – Vstopna točka za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5054">**InitalizationReason** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5055">**K2FileIOHresult** – Koda Hresult za končanje odpiranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5055">**K2FileIOHresult** - Hresult code for File open operation end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5056">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** – Zadnja napaka v odjemalcu BCS (binarna storitev pretvorbe).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5056">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** - last error of BCS (binary conversion service) client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5057">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** – Zastavica stanja za zahtevo spletne storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5057">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** - status flag for the web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5058">**OpEndEventId** – Oznaka, ki predstavlja, kje se je operacija dejansko končala.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5058">**OpEndEventId** - tag that represents where the operation actually ended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5059">**OpFlags** – Zastavice parametrov za operacijo dokumenta, ki jih uporablja plast AppDocs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5059">**OpFlags** - Document operation param flags used by AppDocs layer.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5060">**OpSeqNum** – Število, ki predstavlja zaporedje klicev v zvezi z delovanjem datoteke v plasti AppDocs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5060">**OpSeqNum** - A number that represents the sequencing of file operation related calls in AppDocs layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5061">**OpType** – Oštevilčenje vrste operacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5061">**OpType** - operation type enumeration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5062">Vrednosti: »None«, »CreateDocument«, »OpenDocument«, »CopyDocument«, »CloseDocument«, »SaveDocument«, »OpenVersion«, »CloseVersion«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5062">Values: "None", "CreateDocument", "OpenDocument", "CopyDocument", "CloseDocument", "SaveDocument", "OpenVersion", "CloseVersion"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5063">**PreFetchState** – Oštevilčenje za vnaprejšnje stanje predlog za ustvarjanje novih datotek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5063">**PreFetchState** - enumeration for prefetch state of templates for new file create operations.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5064">**ProviderApp** – Ime paketa aplikacije, v kateri se je odprla datoteka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5064">**ProviderApp** - the package name of the app from which file is opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5066">**Size** – Velikost datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5066">**Size** - file size</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidofficeactivationlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5155">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5155">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5156">Kritični podatki za zbiranje celovitega časa, zahtevanega za odpiranje datoteke, za vsa odpiranja datotek v sistemu Windows ter Excelovih in PowerPointovih aplikacijah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5156">Critical data to collect end-to-end file open time for all file opens in Windows, Excel, PowerPoint apps.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5157">Ta dogodek Microsoft uporablja za določanje metrike za učinkovitost pri odpiranju datoteke naših aplikacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5157">This is used by Microsoft to find out the metric for file open performance of our apps</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5158">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5158">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5159">**AppBootingOccured** – Logična vrednost za preverjanje, ali je zagon aplikacije končan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5159">**AppBootingOccured** - Boolean to check if app boot is complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5160">**ApplicationBootTime**– Čas, zahtevan za določeno stopnjo zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5160">**ApplicationBootTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5161">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** – Logična vrednost za preverjanje, ali je bila aplikacija prekinjena med zagonom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5161">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to check if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5162">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je med odpiranjem datoteke prišlo do blokiranja pogovornih oken.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5162">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** - Boolean to indicate if there was any blocking dialog during the file open operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5163">**CachedInfoAvailable** – Logična vrednost za iskanje predpomnjenih informacij, značilnih za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5163">**CachedInfoAvailable** - Boolean to look for cached info specific to file open operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5164">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je na voljo dokument, ki čaka na obnovitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5164">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** - Boolean to indicate if there was a document pending for recovery</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5165">**EndToEndActivationTime** – Čas, zahtevan za upodobitev datoteke za datoteke, zagnane zunaj aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5165">**EndToEndActivationTime** - time taken to render the file for files opened from outside the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5166">**EndToEndFileOpenTime** – Čas, zahtevan za upodobitev datoteke za datoteke, zagnane v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5166">**EndToEndFileOpenTime** - time taken to render the file for files opened from inside the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5167">**FileOpenPhaseDurationInMs** – Čas za odpiranje datoteke, ki ga porabi določena faza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5167">**FileOpenPhaseDurationInMs** - file open operation time consumed by specific phase</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5168">**FileSourceLocation** – Vrednost oštevilčenja za mesto datoteke, kot so: None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5168">**FileSourceLocation** - enumeration value for File location such as None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5169">**InitalizationReason** – Vstopna točka za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5169">**InitalizationReason** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5170">**InitialBootPhaseTime**– Čas, zahtevan za določeno stopnjo zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5170">**InitialBootPhaseTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5171">**IsThisFirstLaunch** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je to prvi zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5171">**IsThisFirstLaunch** - Boolean to indicate if this is the first launch of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5172">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** – Čas, zahtevan za določeno stopnjo zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5172">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5173">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** – Čas, zahtevan za določeno stopnjo zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5173">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5174">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** – Čas, zahtevan za določeno stopnjo zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5174">**MinimumLibraryLoadPhaseTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5175">**PostAppInitTimeInMs** – Čas, zahtevan za določeno stopnjo zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5175">**PostAppInitTimeInMs** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5178">**ProviderApp** – Ime paketa aplikacije, v kateri se je odprla datoteka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5178">**ProviderApp** - the package name of the app from which file is opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5179">**TelemetryReason** – Podobno kot InitialisationReason, vendar bolj podrobna vrednost oštevilčenja glede na vstopno točko za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5179">**TelemetryReason** - similar to InitialisationReason, but more detailed enumeration value regarding the entry point for File open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5180">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je med zagonom prišlo do blokiranja pogovornih oken.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5180">**UserDialogInterruptionDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if there was any blocking dialog during the boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5200">**ErrorCode** – Koda napake za delovanje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5200">**ErrorCode** - error code for the file operation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5227">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5227">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidmsasigninuiprompts"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5382">Office.Android.MSASignInUIPrompts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5382">Office.Android.MSASignInUIPrompts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5383">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da je bil uporabniku prikazan poziv za vpis v osebni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5383">This event denotes that sign-in prompt came to the user, for personal account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5384">Ta dogodek omogoča lažje razumevanje stanja vpisa naših aplikacij in izvedbo ustreznih dejanj, ko zaznamo nepričakovane pozive za vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5384">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected sign-in re-prompts.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5385">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5385">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5386">**ExternalCacheRefreshError** – Koda napake pri poskusu osveževanja žetona pred prikazom poziva za vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5386">**ExternalCacheRefreshError** - Error code of token refresh attempt, before showing sign-in prompt.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5449">**0 –** ime procesa, ki je sporočil poškodbo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5449">**0 -** The Process name which reported corruption</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5583">Zbira, ko uporabnik poskuša odpreti dokument, zaščiten z upravljanjem pravic do informacij ali uporabiti zaščito za upravljanje pravic do informacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5583">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5584">Vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav, do katerih pride, ko obnovitev uporabniških dovoljenj ne uspe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5584">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when failed to renew user certificates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5585">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5585">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5587">**AppInfo.Name** – ime aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5587">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5588">**AppInfo.Version** – različica aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5588">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5589">**Failure.Category** – Kategorija napake »UnhandledError«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5589">**Failure.Category** - The category of the failure “UnhandledError”</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5590">**Failure.Detail** – podrobnejše informacije o napaki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5590">**Failure.Detail** - The detailed info of the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5591">**Failure.Id** – ID napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5591">**Failure.Id** - Failure Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5596">**RMS.SDKVersion** – različica odjemalca storitve za upravljanje pravic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5596">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5603">Uporabnik je posodobil gonilnik grafične kartice, ki je povzročal zrušitve Officea in se posledični ni več uporabljal za upodabljanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5603">User has updated a video card driver that was previously causing Office crashes and thus no longer being used to render.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5604">Obvešča Microsoft, da so uporabniki, ki so nekoč bili v neoptimalnem stanju upodabljanja, ponovno v priporočenem stanju upodabljanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5604">Informs Microsoft that users who were once in a sub-optimal rendering state are once again in the recommended rendering state.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5608">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** – različica posodobljenega gonilnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5608">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** - Version of the updated driver</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacelocalblocklistinfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5609">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5609">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5610">Podrobnosti o gonilniku grafične kartice uporabnika, ki je povzročil več nedavnih zrušitev Officeovih aplikacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5610">Details on the user's video card driver that has caused multiple recent crashes of Office applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5611">Office ne bo uporabljal te grafične kartice v tej Officeovi seji (namesto tega se uporabi programska oprema za upodabljanje), dokler ne posodobite gonilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5611">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5612">Obvesti Microsoft o gonilnikih grafične kartice, ki povzročajo težave v Officeu. Na ta način je mogoče prepoznati trende in analizirati učinek, ki ga imajo takšni gonilniki na uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5612">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5613">Microsoft tako izve, koliko uporabnikov ni v optimalnem stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5613">Tell Microsoft how many users are in this sub-optimal state.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5616">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** – identifikator grafične kartice na seznamu prepovedanih</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5616">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5631">**Data\_AppName** – katera aplikacija je naletela na neodzivnost gonilnika grafične kartice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5631">**Data\_AppName** - Which app has encountered video card driver hangs</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorregistrywrite"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5632">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5632">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5633">Office je prepoznal, da je gonilnik grafične kartice uporabnika povzročil neodzivno stanje, ki ga je treba analizirati pri naslednjem zagonu Officeove aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5633">Office has identified that the user's video card driver has caused a hang that should be analyzed at the next Office application boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5634">Se uporablja za odločitev, ali bi uporaba drugega gonilnika grafične kartice ali vmesnika zagotovila boljšo uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5634">Used to determine whether using a different video card driver or adapter would offer a better user experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5635">Če se pojavijo vzorci, Microsoft lahko poskrbi za prilagoditve, s katerimi zagotovi čim bolj neovirano delovanje Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5635">As patterns occur, Microsoft may make adjustments to keep the Office experience as smooth as possible.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5636">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5636">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5637">**Data\_HangDetected** – ali je bila zaznana zrušitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5637">**Data\_HangDetected** - Whether a hang was detected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5638">**Data\_InDeviceCall** – kateri klic za upodabljanje grafične kartice je bil aktiviran za Office, ko je bila zaznana neodzivnost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5638">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - Which video card rendering call Office was in when the hang occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5639">**Data\_Timeout** – čas neodzivnosti, če je bila ta odpravljena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5639">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted, if it recovered</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5640">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** – ali je neodzivnost v tem ukazu za upodabljanje grafične kartice mogoče obnoviti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5640">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** - Whether the hang in this video card rendering command is typically recoverable.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32localblocklistactivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5641">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistActivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5641">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistActivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5642">Podrobnosti o gonilniku grafične kartice uporabnika, ki je povzročil več nedavnih zrušitev Officeovih aplikacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5642">Details on the user's video card driver that has caused multiple recent crashes of Office applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5643">Office ne bo uporabljal te grafične kartice v tej Officeovi seji (namesto tega se uporabi programska oprema za upodabljanje), dokler ne posodobite gonilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5643">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5644">Obvesti Microsoft o gonilnikih grafične kartice, ki povzročajo težave v Officeu. Na ta način je mogoče prepoznati trende in analizirati učinek, ki ga imajo takšni gonilniki na uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5644">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5645">Microsoft tako izve, koliko uporabnikov ni v optimalnem stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5645">Tell Microsoft how many users are in this sub-optimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5646">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5646">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5647">**Data.AllAppsBlocked** – ali so blokirane vse Officeove aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5647">**Data.AllAppsBlocked** - Whether all Office apps are blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5648">**Data.BlockedDeviceId** – identifikator blokirane grafične kartice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5648">**Data.BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocked</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5649">**Data.BlockedDriverVersion** – različica gonilnika na seznamu blokiranih</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5649">**Data.BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5650">**Data.CrashHistory System.String** – niz, ki predstavlja zgodovino gonilnika grafične kartice, ki je povzročil zrušitve za analizo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5650">**Data.CrashHistory System.String** - A string that represents the history of video card driver caused crashes for analysis</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5651">**Data.SecsBetweenCrashes** – kako pogosto prihaja do zrušitev grafične kartice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5651">**Data.SecsBetweenCrashes** - How frequently driver card crashes are occurring</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32localblocklistdriverupdatedactivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5652">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistDriverUpdatedActivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5652">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.LocalBlocklistDriverUpdatedActivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5653">Uporabnik je posodobil gonilnik grafične kartice, ki je povzročal zrušitve Officea in se posledični ni več uporabljal za upodabljanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5653">User has updated a video card driver that was previously causing Office crashes and thus no longer being used to render.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5654">Obvešča Microsoft, da so uporabniki, ki so nekoč bili v neoptimalnem stanju upodabljanja, ponovno v priporočenem stanju upodabljanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5654">Informs Microsoft that users who were once in a sub-optimal rendering state are once again in the recommended rendering state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5655">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5655">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5656">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** – identifikator grafične kartice na seznamu prepovedanih</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5656">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5657">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** – različica gonilnika na seznamu prepovedanih</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5657">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5658">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** – različica posodobljenega gonilnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5658">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** - Version of the updated driver</span></span>

#### <a name="officegraphicsspritememcorrupt"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5659">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5659">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5660">Prijavi vse napake, zaznane pri telemetriji za določanje pomnilnika za slike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5660">Reports any errors detected in the sprite memory accounting telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5661">Ta dogodek je pomemben za ocenjevanje stanja telemetrije porabe grafičnega pomnilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5661">Critical for assessing health of the graphics memory usage telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5662">Ti podatki so zahtevani za preverjanje, ali je naša telemetrija pomnilnika SpriteMem pravilna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5662">This information is needed to validate the correctness of our SpriteMem telemetry.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5663">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5663">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5664">**Data\_CurrentSpriteMem** – skupna količina pomnilnika, ki je aktivno dodeljen za prikaz slik na zaslonu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5664">**Data\_CurrentSpriteMem** - Total amount of memory that is actively allocated to hold sprites (images) that result in screen content.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5665">**Data\_Function** – ime funkcije, ki poskuša sprostiti pomnilnik za slike</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5665">**Data\_Function** - The name of the function that is attempting to release sprite memory.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5666">**Data\_SpriteMemToRemove** – količina pomnilnika, ki bo odstranjena iz dodelitve za slike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5666">**Data\_SpriteMemToRemove** - Amount of memory to be removed from sprite allocation.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptsharednointernetconnectivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5667">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5667">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5668">Ti podatki so zbrani, kadar PowerPoint zazna, da ni internetne povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5668">Collected whenever PowerPoint detects there is no internet connectivity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5669">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za pridobivanje diagnostičnih informacij o internetni povezavi uporabnika, da lahko bolje razume učinek, kako to vpliva na povezljivost z Officeovimi storitvami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5669">Microsoft uses this data to get diagnostic information about the user's internet connection to be able to understand how that impacts connectivity to Office services.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5670">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5670">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5671">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** – prikaže, ali je stanje internetne povezave na voljo med klicanjem storitve Nexus (true) ali pri klicanju programskega vmesnika za splošno spletno storitev (false)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5671">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** - shows whether we got the Internet connectivity status when calling Nexus service (value true) or when calling generic web service API call (value false)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerofficesvcmgrprofile"></a><span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5672">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5672">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5673">Ta dogodek se sproži ob zagonu upravitelja za storitve v Officeu in ima ključno vlogo pri zagotavljanju natančnih vpogledov, povezanih s stanjem uvedbe in aplikacije ter zrušitvami zaradi dodatkov pri najemniku stranke ter nam omogoča, da ustvarjamo vpoglede za skrbnika za IT, ki bo lahko uvajal posodobitve za službene računalnike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5673">This event is triggered when Office Serviceability Manager starts, and is critical for providing accurate insights related to Deployment Status and Application and Add-in crashes within customer's tenant by allowing us to generate insights for the IT Admin to be able to confidently roll-out updates for their enterprise machines.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5674">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5674">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5675">**DeviceIdJoinToken** – Uporablja se za združitev podatkov telemetrije iz stanja storitve in uvedbe z drugimi funkcionalnimi podatki, zbranimi prek prodajnih lijakov storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5675">**DeviceIdJoinToken** - used to join Telemetry data from Health and Deployment Status with other Functional Data which is collected via the Services pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="2bd5f-5676">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** – Zastavica logične vrednosti, ki se uporablja za določanje števila upravljanih naprav v Officeovim ekosistemu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bd5f-5676">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** - a Boolean flag used to determine the number of Managed devices in the Office eco-system.</span></span>
